(87, 1, '2021-01-04 22:51:10', '2021-01-04 15:51:10', '<div class=\"dt-news__sapo\">\r\n<h2>C th mt mi, thiu ng, sc mt km ti, u oi nh b rt ht nng lng c th l triu chng nguy him ca bnh gan.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"dt-news__content\">\r\n\r\nAnh V Tun (37 tui, H Ni) mi y nhp vin trong tnh trng chn n, l m, mt mi, mt ng v st cao khng r nguyn nhn. Bn thn anh ch quan  li do lm vic qu sc, cn ngi nh li qu quyt do ru bia, bi trc  anh tng nhu nht tip khch c tun khng ngh.\r\n\r\nDa trn triu chng lm sng, bc s ch nh lm xt nghim tng phn tch mu. Kt qu cho thy bnh nhn gim tiu cu, ri lon ng mu, sinh ha pht hin vim gan. Nu khng cha tr sm v ngng bia ru, bc s cnh bo bnh s tin trin thnh x gan, thm ch ung th.\r\n\r\nThi gian gn y ti cm thy mt mi bt thng, phi ngh gia chng nhiu ln trong lc ang lm vic. Ti ngh do cng vic qu cng thng, khng ng li mc bnh vim gan do ru bia bao lu nay, anh Tun cho bit.\r\n\r\nGing nh anh Tun, a s mi ngi u ngh rng c th mt mi do lm vic qu sc hoc thay i thi tit. Song theo cc chuyn gia, y c th l du hiu sm ca bnh vim gan. C th mt mi, thiu ng, sc din km ti, u oi nh b rt ht nng lng, st cn bt thng u xut pht t mt l gan khng khe.\r\n\r\nTrong c th, gan l c quan ni tng ln nht vi cn nng khong 1,5kg.  ngi bnh thng, gan cha khong 100 t t bo m nhim hn 500 chc nng khc nhau nh chuyn ha dinh dng, d tr nng lng (glycogen), tng hp protein huyt tng, thi c cho c th\r\n\r\nVi khi lng cng vic  s, gan d chu tn thng khi b virus, ru bia, thuc l, thc phm bn tn cng. Lng c t tch t ngy cng nhiu s khin chc nng gan suy gim nghim trng. Trong , c chc nng d tr glycogen  chuyn ha thnh glucose, cung c nng lng cho c th.\r\n\r\nTheo chuyn gia sc khe ni ting Yuri Elkaim ca t New York Times, khi gan suy yu, khng th chuyn ha glycogen thnh glucose, c th s thiu ht nng lng trm trng.  l l do ti sao bn cm thy d mt mi, u oi, ui sc mi khi gng sc lm vic. Xt nghim thng cho kt qu men gan cao, gan nhim m hoc vim gan.\r\n\r\nTriu chng mt mi ny c th ko di m thm nhiu nm trc khi ngi bnh c du hiu nng nh vng da, vng mt, au tc h sn phi, bun nn, st cn nhanh Lc ny, bnh  chuyn sang giai on nng hoc bin chng thnh x gan, thm ch ung th. Vic iu tr lc ny thng tr nn kh khn v tn km hn nhiu\r\n\r\nBi thuc b gan, gim mt mi ca ngi Nht: 100g gan heo, 30-45g tinh ngh, 1g tiu en.\r\n\r\n phng bnh, cc bc s khuyn co nn xy dng li sng lnh mnh, thi quen khm sc khe nh k, hn ch ru bia, dng thm sn phm h tr tng cng chc nng ganTrong , ngh l mt trong nhng dc liu d tm, cha hot cht curcumin gip ti to t bo gan v chng li c t. C th xay thm ht tiu en, b vo nc m,  c th hp thu dng cht t ngh tt hn.\r\n\r\n Nht, cn c bi thuc ly 30-45g tinh ngh, 1g ht tiu en kt hp vi 100g gan heo,  tng cng chc nng gan, tng chuyn ha cc cht dinh dng, phc hi sc khe trong cc trng hp mt mi, m au. Nghin cu cho thy, gan heo thy phn cha n 18 loi acid amin, gip tng cng chc nng gan, gip gan nhanh chng phn gii c t t cn. Ung vi nc m, trc hoc sau khi nhu nht, cn c tc dng gim cc triu chng kh chu ca ru bia nh au u, bun nn, chng mt\r\n\r\nBox: Thc phm bo v sc khe Hepalyse W gip bo v t bo gan, hn ch tn thng t bo gan do ru bia, gip tng cng chc nng gan v phc hi sc khe khi mt mi, m au. Bn cnh  Hepalyse W cn h tr lm gim cc triu chng kh chu nh au u, bun nn, ni mn, mt mi.\r\n\r\nHepalyse W c thnh phn chnh c chit xut t gan heo, c dng chai lng v da d ung hoc vin nn nh gn. Ung 2 vin hoc 1 chai 100ml mt ln mi ngy, trc hoc sau khi ung ru bia.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>', 'C th mt mi cnh bo nguy c mc bnh gan', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'co-the-met-moi-canh-bao-nguy-co-mac-benh-gan', '', '', '2021-01-04 23:16:44', '2021-01-04 16:16:44', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?p=87', 0, 'post', '', 0),
