(90, 1, '2021-01-04 22:53:41', '2021-01-04 15:53:41', '<h2>5 loi thc phm gip tiu dit vi khun hp</h2>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Bong_cai_xanh\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Bng ci xanh</h3>\r\nNhc n bng ci xanh th mi ngi thng nhc n cng dng b sung canxi cho c th. p ng c lng canxi y  cho c th, nhng bng ci xanh cn tc dng khc chnh l h tr km hm s pht trin ca vi khun HP. Mt loi vi khun gy vim lot d dy.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-900 aligncenter\" src=\"https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/rau-xanh-giup-tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-hieu-qua-425x298.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" srcset=\"https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/rau-xanh-giup-tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-hieu-qua-425x298.jpg 425w, https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/rau-xanh-giup-tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-hieu-qua.jpg 592w\" alt=\"rau xanh gip tiu dit vi khun hp hiu qu\" width=\"425\" height=\"298\" />\r\n\r\nBi trong bng ci xanh c cha Sulforaphane <strong>thnh phn c kh nng c ch s nhn ln ca cc loi vi khun HP</strong>. T  c th h tr lm tng qu trnh o thi vi khun HP v s d dng  iu tr cc bnh l d dy.\r\n<h3><span id=\"Cac_loai_qua,_trai_cay_giau_vitamin_C\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Cc loi qu, tri cy giu vitamin C</h3>\r\nVitamin C c rt nhiu trong cc loi tri cy c mi nh: cam, qut, bi, chanh, du, to, i, Khng nhng c tc dng chng oxy ha mnh m cn gip<strong>c ch s pht trin ca vi khun HP</strong>chng vim hiu qu.\r\n\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;<strong>5 THC UNG LM MT GAN</strong>\r\n\r\nC mt iu bt buc bn phi nh l vitamin C cng l mt loi acid, chnh v th m bn khng nn s dng qu nhiu. Nu bn lm dng iu  th n s mang li tc dng ngc. Nh th s gy nng thm tnh trng vim lot d dy. S dng ng lng s cho bn mt kt qu tt hn.\r\n<h3><span id=\"Dung_hanh,_toi_de_tieu_diet_vi_khuan_HP\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Dng hnh, ti  tiu dit vi khun HP?</h3>\r\nTrong mi cn bp gia nh th hnh v ti l hai loi gia v khng th thiu. Hai loi gia v ny c im chung l mi kh hng, nhng y li l im cng ca chng. Mi hng ny chnh l mi ca thnh phn Allicin  khng sinh t nhin, c tc dng tng cng h min dch v phng nga cm cng. Allicin cn c chc nng<strong>c ch vi khun hp</strong>rt tt.\r\n<h3><span id=\"Gung\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Gng</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-901 aligncenter\" src=\"https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/vi-khuan-hp-la-gi-425x252.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" srcset=\"https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/vi-khuan-hp-la-gi-425x252.jpg 425w, https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/vi-khuan-hp-la-gi.jpg 592w\" alt=\"vi khun hp l g\" width=\"425\" height=\"252\" />\r\n\r\nTrong gng c cha Gingerol  thnh phn c tc dng chng oxy ha rt tt v khng vim mnh vi s pht trin ca vi khun HP. Gng cng cn l mt loi thc phm gip gim au, chng vim rt tt v hiu qu vi nhng ngi b vim hay lot d dy. Ta c th b sung gng vo thc n hng ngy  ci thin cc triu chng kh chu ca d dy.\r\n<h3><span id=\"Qua_viet_quat\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Qu vit qut</h3>\r\nProanthocyanidins  hot cht c tc dng c ch s pht trin ca vi khun hp. iu tuyt vi l n li c rt nhiu trong loi qu vit qut. Chng gip ngn cn qu trnh bm dnh ca hp trn thnh nim mc d dy v h tr y li c vi khun hp.\r\n\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;<strong>LM SAO  THANH LC GAN?</strong>\r\n<h2><span id=\"4_loai_thuoc_tieu_diet_vi_khuan_HP_tan_goc_ma_ban_nen_biet\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>4 loi thuc tiu dit vi khun HP tn gc m bn nn bit</h2>\r\n<h3><span id=\"KOFACINS_%E2%80%93_Thuoc_tieu_diet_vi_khuan_hp_hieu_qua\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>KOFACINS  Thuc tiu dit vi khun hp hiu qu</h3>\r\nVi 1 hp<strong>KOFACNS</strong>c 5 v v 10 vin nang cng/ v, v alu  alu v c ng trong ti nhm. H tr tiu dit vi khun HP rt hiu qu, gim axit dch v v bo v nim mc d dy, gim cc triu chng au d dy. Nguyn nhn l do y bng, nng rt, kh tiu,  hi,  chua, tro ngc d dy, Nu bn mun s hu loi thuc ny th c th lin h ngay vi chng ti qua s hotline:\r\n<h2><span id=\"Thuoc_khang_sinh_%E2%80%93_thuoc_ho_tro_tieu_diet_vi_khuan_hp_rat_tot\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Thuc khng sinh  thuc h tr tiu dit vi khun hp rt tt</h2>\r\nVic s dng thuc khng sinh l iu v cng cn thit  tiu dit vi khun hp tn gc. y l nhm thuc ny c kh nng c ch v tiu dit cc hi khun trong d dy thng qua vic ngn chn s nhn i, pht trin ca chng.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-902 aligncenter\" src=\"https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-425x210.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" srcset=\"https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-425x210.jpg 425w, https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-768x379.jpg 768w, https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-600x296.jpg 600w, https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp.jpg 952w\" alt=\"tiu dit vi khun hp\" width=\"425\" height=\"210\" />\r\n\r\nBn c th th tham kho 4 loi thuc khng sinh sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thuc Amoxicillin: loi thuc khng sinh c s dng  tiu dit vi khun Hp tn gc rt ph bin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc Metronidazol: Nhm thuc c tc dng cc mnh vi vi khun hp. C th dng n c hoc kt hp vi nhiu loi khng sinh khc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc Clarithromycin: y l loi thuc c ch nh <strong>tiu dit vi khun hp tn gc</strong>trong phc  iu tr 3 thuc ban u.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc Tinidazol: thuc c tc dng<strong>tiu dit vi khun hp tn gc rt tt v hiu qu</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Thuoc_bao_ve_niem_mac_da_day_giup_tieu_diet_vi_khuan_hp\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Thuc bo v nim mc d dy gip tiu dit vi khun hp</h3>\r\ny l nhm thuc c tc dng tng sinh lp nhy, h tr lm lnh cc  lot m khng gy nh hng n hot tnh ca khng sinh. Ngoi ra, thuc cn c tc dng c ch s hot ng ca vi khun hp rt tt. Mc khc n cng ngn chn chng xm nhp vo cc b phn khc.\r\n<h3><span id=\"Thuoc_nam_%E2%80%93_loai_thuoc_dan_gian_tri_vi_khuan_hp_rat_tot\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Thuc nam  loi thuc dn gian tr vi khun hp rt tt</h3>\r\nThuc Nam c mt u im ln l kh an ton, t gy ra tc dng ph. Nu s dng chng lu di cng khng gy ra tnh trng nhn thuc. Nhng bn phi kin tr s dng lin tc th mi c th thy c hiu qu ca n. Ty vo c a ca mi ngi m hiu qu ca thuc s di, ngn khc nhau.', '9 Gii Php Tiu Dit Vi Khun Hp Tn Gc Mang Li Hiu Qu Tt', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '9-giai-phap-tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-tan-goc-mang-lai-hieu-qua-tot', '', '', '2021-01-04 22:53:41', '2021-01-04 15:53:41', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?p=90', 0, 'post', '', 0),
