ion\"></span>Thuc khng sinh  thuc h tr tiu dit vi khun hp rt tt</h2>\r\nVic s dng thuc khng sinh l iu v cng cn thit  tiu dit vi khun hp tn gc. y l nhm thuc ny c kh nng c ch v tiu dit cc hi khun trong d dy thng qua vic ngn chn s nhn i, pht trin ca chng.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-902 aligncenter\" src=\"https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-425x210.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" srcset=\"https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-425x210.jpg 425w, https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-768x379.jpg 768w, https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp-600x296.jpg 600w, https://drthsaigon.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/tieu-diet-vi-khuan-hp.jpg 952w\" alt=\"tiu dit vi khun hp\" width=\"425\" height=\"210\" />\r\n\r\nBn c th th tham kho 4 loi thuc khng sinh sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thuc Amoxicillin: loi thuc khng sinh c s dng  tiu dit vi khun Hp tn gc rt ph bin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc Metronidazol: Nhm thuc c tc dng cc mnh vi vi khun hp. C th dng n c hoc kt hp vi nhiu loi khng sinh khc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc Clarithromycin: y l loi thuc c ch nh <strong>tiu dit vi khun hp tn gc</strong>trong phc  iu tr 3 thuc ban u.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc Tinidazol: thuc c tc dng<strong>tiu dit vi khun hp tn gc rt tt v hiu qu</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Thuoc_bao_ve_niem_mac_da_day_giup_tieu_diet_vi_khuan_hp\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Thuc bo v nim mc d dy gip tiu dit vi khun hp</h3>\r\ny l nhm thuc c tc dng tng sinh lp nhy, h tr lm lnh cc  lot m khng gy nh hng n hot tnh ca khng sinh. Ngoi ra, thuc cn c tc dng c ch s hot ng ca vi khun hp rt tt. Mc khc n cng ngn chn chng xm nhp vo cc b phn khc.\r\n<h3><span id=\"Thuoc_nam_%E2%80%93_loai_thuoc_dan_gian_tri_vi_khuan_hp_rat_tot\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Thuc nam  loi thuc dn gian tr vi khun hp rt tt</h3>\r\nThuc Nam c mt u im ln l kh an ton, t gy ra tc dng ph. Nu s dng chng lu di cng khng gy ra tnh trng nhn thuc. Nhng bn phi kin tr s dng lin tc th mi c th thy c hiu qu ca n. Ty vo c a ca mi ngi m hiu qu ca thuc s di, ngn khc nhau.', '9 Gii Php Tiu Dit Vi Khun Hp Tn Gc Mang Li Hiu Qu Tt', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '90-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-04 22:53:41', '2021-01-04 15:53:41', '', 90, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/index.php/2021/01/04/90-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
