(108, 1, '2021-01-04 23:13:51', '2021-01-04 16:13:51', '<strong>Khng ch c cng dng tng min dch, khe  khng, phng cm cm, cc chuyn gia cn pht hin ra vitamin C s hu nhiu li ch bt ng i vi c th khng phi ai cng bit.</strong>\r\n\r\nNm trong top u nhng hot cht chng oxy ha mnh m trong t nhin, vitamin C c mt trong hu ht t thuc mi gia nh nh mt ngi bn ng hnh, gip chng ta tng cng sc khe. Cc chuyn gia  khm ph ra nhiu cng dng cc k sng gi ca vitamin C ta khng th ng n nh:\r\n<h2><strong>Khe  khng, phng bnh t gc:</strong></h2>\r\nVitamin C khuyn khch sn xut cc t bo bch cu l lympho v phagocytes, gip bo v c th chng li nhim trng. Vitamin C gip cc t bo bch cu ny hot ng hiu qu hn, bo v chng khi b h hi bi cc phn t c kh nng gy hi, chng hn nh cc gc t do.\r\n<h2><strong>Tng cng min dch:</strong></h2>\r\nVitamin C cn thit cho cc t bo min dch (T bo T v bch cu), t  lm mnh chc nng h min dch, lm tng phn ng d ng. Khoa hc  chng minh, khi b sung vitamin C cho c th, n s lp tc h tr sn xut Interferon  loi protein chng li tc nhn gy bnh, lm suy yu cc vi khun gy hi, t  h min dch c phc hi, gip c th gim cc triu chng ho, st.\r\n<h2><strong>Gim nguy c cm lnh, cm cm:</strong></h2>\r\nVitamin C h tr gia tng hiu qu ca khng th v hot ng ca h min dch, gim bt mc  nghim trng v rt ngn thi gian c th b nhim lnh, gip hi phc sc khe nhanh sau bnh.\r\n<h2><strong>Gim stress, tng nng lng mi ngy:</strong></h2>\r\nVitamin C gip tng hp cc cht dn truyn thn kinh, ngn nga sn xut Cortisol  hoocmon c sinh ra khi ta gp p lc, t  gip c th gim ti cng thng, tng cng nng lng.\r\n<h2><strong>Kh nng chng oxy ha cao:</strong></h2>\r\nVi kh nng chng oxy ha mnh m, vitamin C gip thi c t, loi b t bo h tn ra khi c th, dn dp cc gc t do, lm gim c tnh ca thuc v chuyn ha cc phn t c thnh dng c th o thi qua nc tiu.\r\n<h2><strong>Cch b sung vitamin C p ng  nhu cu cho c th</strong></h2>\r\nC th chng ta khng th t tng hp c vitamin C, th nn thng thng mi ngi hay chn cch b sung vitamin C qua rau c, qu, tri cy. Tuy nhin, thc t vitamin C s b hao ht ng k trong qu trnh ch bin, nu nng hay thm ch tip xc di nh mt tri. Lng Vitamin C  hp th khng cn li l bao.\r\n\r\nCch thng minh v tin li  np vitamin C trn vn, khng s hao ht, m bo nhu cu cn thit cho c th mi ngy l s dng vin ung vitamin C 1000mg.Mt vin vitamin C 1000mg tng ng hn 2 k cam, gn bng 51 qu chanh, 11 qu i. Liu cao 1000mg cung cp  vitamin C hng ngy  xy dng hng ro  khng vng chc, chng li bnh tt.\r\n\r\nVitamin C 1000mg vi 2 nh dng 60% Mui Ascorbate v 40% Acid Ascorbic gip gim kch ng d dy hn so vi dng si, vin nn trn, d ung, an tm khi s dng lu di. Kt hp vi Bioflavonoids, Rutin, Hesperidin (cht chng oxy ha thin nhin) gip hp thu ti u v tng cng hiu qu vitamin C. Khng c cht lm ngt nhn to, ph hp cho c gia nh<strong>.</strong>\r\n\r\nMi ngy ung 1 vin vitamin C 1000mg lin tc trong vng 30 ngy, sau  ngng 15 ngy ri li s dng tip.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, vitamin C Yummy Gummyz l vitamin C dng ko do dnh cho tr em t 2 tui c cc ph huynh rt tin dng v nh gi cao. Vitamin C Yummy Gummyz cung cp ton b nhu cu vitamin C mi ngy cho b nhm tng cng sc  khng, phng nga cm lnh, cm cm, cc bnh v ng h hp, tng hp thu canxi &amp; st h tr xng, rng. c bit, dng ko do vui ming khin b thch th, t ngt v ch cha hng v t nhin, khng cht bo qun, gip b m thm yn tm.\r\n\r\nChng ta cng chung tay ch ng xy dng  khng min dch khe mnh, bo v sc khe gia nh ni ring v bo v sc khe cng ng ni chung, phng nga cm cm cm lnh bnh tt vi vitamin C 1000mg v vitamin C Yummy Gummyz dng ko do.', 'Mi ngy 1 vin vitamin C 1000mg hn 2kg cam', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '102-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-04 23:13:51', '2021-01-04 16:13:51', '', 102, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/index.php/2021/01/04/102-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
