(858, 1, '2021-02-19 11:49:08', '2021-02-19 04:49:08', '<h2><strong>Gii thiu h thng nh thuc t vn bn hng online I-pharmacy</strong></h2>\r\n<em>L h thng nh thuc c mt ti khp cc tnh thnh, nhng ch yu l t vn v bn thuc theo phng thc online trn c s tun th lut v cc qui nh kinh doanh ngnh Dc nhng phc v tt hn nhu cu c tip cn thuc phng v iu tr bnh ca tt c bnh nhn c nc vi cht lng tt nht, gi c hp l v giao hng min ph, nhanh chng, tin li, n tn tay ngi dng.</em>\r\n<h2><strong>Mc tiu ca nh thuc t vn bn hng online I-pharmacy</strong></h2>\r\nKhi i dch Covid p n vo u nm 2020, Chnh ph v ngi dn Vit Nam ni ring, th gii ni chung, khng c chun b. Thi gian u, nhiu ni, nhiu c quan, nhiu ngi trn th gii c phn ch quan, lng tng, cha  thc c s nguy him cht ngi ca Virus Sar-Covi 2, cha c kinh nghim trong vic phng trnh v iu tr hiu qu.\r\n\r\ni dch COVID-19 gy ra khng hong sc khe cng ng, khng hong kinh t v sinh k, hin nay nhiu nn kinh t ln ang ri vo suy thoi nghim trng. Mc  nghim trng  vt xa khng hong ti chnh 2008, thm ch vt c i suy thoi vo nhng nm 1930. Tt c cc chuyn gia kinh t th gii u thng nht rng, kinh t ton cu sau i dch s rt khc so vi trc y, khng hong kinh t x hi nghim trng s gy ra hng lot bt n trong kinh doanh v bt n trong x hi, lm tng bin i a chnh tr, gia tng i ngho, thay i thi quen ca rt nhiu ngi trn th gii. c bit l mua sm online, ngay c vi dc phm, nhu cu tip cn thuc iu tr tng cao trong i dch, nhng kh nng p ng gim i do t gy chui cung ng, do cc bin php gin cch x hi. Theo cc chuyn gia nhn nh, th gii s rt khc sau i dch.\r\n\r\nTi Vit Nam, nhiu loi thuc khng cn   cung ng cho bnh nhn, do gi c tng cao v do thiu nguyn liu cho sn xut.\r\n\r\nTrc tnh hnh , I-pharmacy ra i vi mong mun cung cp cc t vn sc khe, t vn s dng thuc an ton, hiu qu, hp l qua in thoi hoc bng phng thc online. Lm thay i thi quen mua thuc v cc sn phm tiu dng khc, gip tng kh nng tip cn thuc ca ngi bnh, gim chi ph v thi gian mua thuc, thm ch c th i tr nu mua ri m khng cn dng.\r\n\r\nVi hng trm sn phm c gii thiu v bn trn website <strong>i-pharmacy.com</strong> v hng ngn sn phm khc c bn trc tip ti h thng nh thuc cng tc vi <strong>I-pharmacy</strong>, nh thuc <strong>I-pharmacy</strong> m bo cung cp y  cc mt hng dc phm nh:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Cc loi thuc (thuc ni v thuc ngoi nhp)</li>\r\n 	<li>Thc phm chc nng: a s c nhp khu t nc ngoi nh: M, c, Php, an Mch,</li>\r\n 	<li>Sa dinh dng</li>\r\n 	<li>M phm</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng c Y Khoa</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc sn phm chm sc c th</li>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm tiu dng khc</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2><strong>Tm nhn, s mnh</strong></h2>\r\nPhc v sc khe cng ng vi cht lng tt nht v gi c hp l, giao hng tn tay ngi bnh mi lc, mi ni.\r\n<h2><strong>Phng hng pht trin</strong></h2>\r\nTrong tng lai, nh thuc <strong>I-pharmacy</strong> phn u Xy dng h thng Nh Thuc Ty vi phng thc t vn bn hng online ph khp cc vng min trn c nc, hot ng theo ng tiu chun GPP v cc qui nh mi nht trong ngnh Dc, nhm phc v tt nht cho sc khe nhn dn c nc, v hng ra cc nc xung quanh.\r\n<h2><strong>u im ni bt</strong></h2>\r\nC 6 im khc bit m ch nh thuc <strong>I-pharmacy</strong> mi mang n cho bn y  nht, c th nh sau:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>L nh thuc chnh hng</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nH thng nh thuc <strong>I-pharmacy</strong> s hu danh mc thuc chnh hng va a dng, phong ph li va chuyn su.\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n 	<li><strong>c mua l vi gi s</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nCam kt sn phm ng cht lng vi gi nim yt thp hn so vi th trng chung, tng ng vi gi bn s.\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n 	<li><strong>C dc s t vn ti ch hoc qua ng dy nng v qua cc phng tin lin lc khc nh Zalo, Facebook, Yahoo messenger 24/7, </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nChuyn nghip hn, i ng dc s <strong>I-pharmacy</strong> vi kinh nghim v chuyn mn cao lun ch trng t vn cho khch hng vi tiu ch 4 ng: ng thuc, ng liu, ng cch v ng gi.\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n 	<li><strong>i tr nguyn gi trong vng 30 ngy sau khi mua</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nCh cn c ST hoc gi li ha n mua hng, bn s c i tr sn phm hoc hon li tin  mua trong vng 30 ngy bn, k c l do thuc  mua dng khng ht hoc bc s i toa.\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Giao hng tn ni, min ph</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>I-pharmacy</strong> s giao hng tn ni trong khu vc Tp.HCM vi tc  cc nhanh v chuyn hng n tn nh ti cc tnh thnh khc.\r\n<ol start=\"6\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Thanh ton linh hot</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nKhch hng c th thanh ton trc tip ti nh thuc, thanh ton qua chuyn khon, thanh ton qua cc ng dng thanh ton in t nh: I-pay, Momo,  hoc thanh ton trc tip ti nh khi nhn hng.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nVi Nh Thuc <strong>I-pharmacy</strong>, bn hon ton c th tin tng v cht lng, gi c v tnh hp l khi s dng sn phm. i ng bc s, dc s chng ti  c nhiu nm kinh nghim trong lnh vc chm sc sc khe cho mi ngi.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Gii thiu', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '571-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-02-19 11:49:08', '2021-02-19 04:49:08', '', 571, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/571-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(110, 1, '2021-01-04 23:15:28', '2021-01-04 16:15:28', '<div class=\"dt-news__sapo\">\n<h2>C th mt mi, thiu ng, sc mt km ti, u oi nh b rt ht nng lng c th l triu chng nguy him ca bnh gan.</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dt-news__content\">\n\nAnh V Tun (37 tui, H Ni) mi y nhp vin trong tnh trng chn n, l m, mt mi, mt ng v st cao khng r nguyn nhn. Bn thn anh ch quan  li do lm vic qu sc, cn ngi nh li qu quyt do ru bia, bi trc  anh tng nhu nht tip khch c tun khng ngh.\n\nDa trn triu chng lm sng, bc s ch nh lm xt nghim tng phn tch mu. Kt qu cho thy bnh nhn gim tiu cu, ri lon ng mu, sinh ha pht hin vim gan. Nu khng cha tr sm v ngng bia ru, bc s cnh bo bnh s tin trin thnh x gan, thm ch ung th.\n\nThi gian gn y ti cm thy mt mi bt thng, phi ngh gia chng nhiu ln trong lc ang lm vic. Ti ngh do cng vic qu cng thng, khng ng li mc bnh vim gan do ru bia bao lu nay, anh Tun cho bit.\n\nGing nh anh Tun, a s mi ngi u ngh rng c th mt mi do lm vic qu sc hoc thay i thi tit. Song theo cc chuyn gia, y c th l du hiu sm ca bnh vim gan. C th mt mi, thiu ng, sc din km ti, u oi nh b rt ht nng lng, st cn bt thng u xut pht t mt l gan khng khe.\n\nTrong c th, gan l c quan ni tng ln nht vi cn nng khong 1,5kg.  ngi bnh thng, gan cha khong 100 t t bo m nhim hn 500 chc nng khc nhau nh chuyn ha dinh dng, d tr nng lng (glycogen), tng hp protein huyt tng, thi c cho c th\n\nVi khi lng cng vic  s, gan d chu tn thng khi b virus, ru bia, thuc l, thc phm bn tn cng. Lng c t tch t ngy cng nhiu s khin chc nng gan suy gim nghim trng. Trong , c chc nng d tr glycogen  chuyn ha thnh glucose, cung c nng lng cho c th.\n\nTheo chuyn gia sc khe ni ting Yuri Elkaim ca t New York Times, khi gan suy yu, khng th chuyn ha glycogen thnh glucose, c th s thiu ht nng lng trm trng.  l l do ti sao bn cm thy d mt mi, u oi, ui sc mi khi gng sc lm vic. Xt nghim thng cho kt qu men gan cao, gan nhim m hoc vim gan.\n\nTriu chng mt mi ny c th ko di m thm nhiu nm trc khi ngi bnh c du hiu nng nh vng da, vng mt, au tc h sn phi, bun nn, st cn nhanh Lc ny, bnh  chuyn sang giai on nng hoc bin chng thnh x gan, thm ch ung th. Vic iu tr lc ny thng tr nn kh khn v tn km hn nhiu\n\nBi thuc b gan, gim mt mi ca ngi Nht: 100g gan heo, 30-45g tinh ngh, 1g tiu en.\n\n phng bnh, cc bc s khuyn co nn xy dng li sng lnh mnh, thi quen khm sc khe nh k, hn ch ru bia, dng thm sn phm h tr tng cng chc nng ganTrong , ngh l mt trong nhng dc liu d tm, cha hot cht curcumin gip ti to t bo gan v chng li c t. C th xay thm ht tiu en, b vo nc m,  c th hp thu dng cht t ngh tt hn.\n\n Nht, cn c bi thuc ly 30-45g tinh ngh, 1g ht tiu en kt hp vi 100g gan heo,  tng cng chc nng gan, tng chuyn ha cc cht dinh dng, phc hi sc khe trong cc trng hp mt mi, m au. Nghin cu cho thy, gan heo thy phn cha n 18 loi acid amin, gip tng cng chc nng gan, gip gan nhanh chng phn gii c t t cn. Ung vi nc m, trc hoc sau khi nhu nht, cn c tc dng gim cc triu chng kh chu ca ru bia nh au u, bun nn, chng mt\n\nBox: Thc phm bo v sc khe Hepalyse W gip bo v t bo gan, hn ch tn thng t bo gan do ru bia, gip tng cng chc nng gan v phc hi sc khe khi mt mi, m au. Bn cnh  Hepalyse W cn h tr lm gim cc triu chng kh chu nh au u, bun nn, ni mn, mt mi.\n\nHepalyse W c thnh phn chnh c chit xut t gan heo, c dng chai lng v da d ung hoc vin nn nh gn. Ung 2 vin hoc 1 chai 100ml mt ln mi ngy, trc hoc sau khi ung ru bia.\n\nSn phm ca Cng ty Dc phm Zeria (Nht Bn), c nhp khu v phn phi chnh thc ti Vit Nam bi Cng ty C phn Dc phm 3/2.\n\ni ch: 601 Cch Mng Thng 8, P.15, Q.10, TP. HCM\n\nHotline: 0906.701232\n\nGPQC: 00968/2017/ATTP-XNQC; GPQC: 00969/2017/ATTP-XNQC do B Y t cp.\n\nThc phm ny khng phi l thuc v khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.\n\n</div>', 'C th mt mi cnh bo nguy c mc bnh gan', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '87-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-01-04 23:15:28', '2021-01-04 16:15:28', '', 87, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/index.php/2021/01/04/87-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
