(231, 1, '2021-01-19 09:25:36', '2021-01-19 02:25:36', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>Bn mt mi mi khi \"gn gi\" nng</strong></h2>\r\nMc cm, tti khin bn khng th s chia cng nng, phi lm sao y?\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/sam-nhung-bo-than-trung-uong-3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-236 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/sam-nhung-bo-than-trung-uong-3-300x227.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"875\" height=\"662\" /></a>\r\n\r\nBn lun lo lng khi khng th cng nng i ht cuc vui</div>\r\nYu sinh ll ni m nh ln nht i vi nam gii v n khng ch nh hng trc tip n bnm cn l mi e da i vi hnh phc gia nh.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>C th bn mt mi, thiu nng lng, mt hnham mun tnh dc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nng mun gn bn nhng bn li khng th tha mn nng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tti, mc cm v chuyn y khin bn ngy mt xa lnh nng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tnh cm gia nh c th m dn rn nt ri tan v lc no khng hay.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nC th sn sinh khng  lng Testosterone khin nam gii tr nn khng mn m vi chuyn chn gi, gim chc nng ham mun tnh dc lu di dn n bt lc.\r\n<blockquote>Lc ny bn cn b sung cc dng cht thit yu nhm gip b sung hormone sinh dc nam mt cch t nhin.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>thc phm chc nngBang</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Th lc sung mn, thm phn t tin</strong></h4>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/BANG-CEVRAI-60V-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-237 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/BANG-CEVRAI-60V-2-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"802\" height=\"802\" /></a>\r\n<div></div>\r\nThc phm chc nng Bang tng sinh lc cho phi mnh lun sung mn</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm c ngun gc t Php vi cc thnh phn chuyn bit ci thinsinh l nam gii.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gip b thn trng dng, tng cng sinh lc, ci thin chc nng sinh l nam gii, ko di thi gian cng dng.</li>\r\n 	<li>L mt trong nhng sn phm c nam gii a chung nht hin nay.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Bang</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCevrai Laboratoire Bang c chit xut t cc thnh phn t nhin tri qua qu trnh nghin cu v sn xut nghim ngt gm:\r\n<h4><strong>Bt r Nhn Sm 50mg</strong></h4>\r\nNgoi cc tc dng lm p da, tc, bi b sc khe, nhn sm cn c bit n l mt cht kch thch tnh dc mnh m v c th iu tr cc bnh lin quan n tnh dc nh ri lon chc nng cng dng  nam gii. Lm tng cng lu thng mu n dng vt, ci thin ham mun, gim tnh trng ri lon cng dng.\r\n<div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/tac-dung-cua-nhan-sam.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-238 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/tac-dung-cua-nhan-sam-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"905\" height=\"603\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption>Nhn sm gip tng tun hon mu, ci thin ham mun hiu qu</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4><strong>Bt r Gng 50mg</strong></h4>\r\nTheo y dc hc hin i, gng c tinh du 2% - 3%, cht nha 5%, cht bo 3% tinh bt v cc cht cay nh zingeron, shogaola. Gng v tinh du chit xut t gng cn c cho l mang li nhiu cng dng sc khe c bit Gng c ch cho sc khe nam gii bi cng dng kch thch sinh dc, hiu qu trong vic loi b bt lc v iu tr xut tinh sm. Gn y, mt nh nghin cu Trung Quc cho bit, gng cn c th iu tr hiu qu bnh vim tinh hon.\r\n<h4><strong>Bt ht Guarana 50mg</strong></h4>\r\nGuarana l mt loi cy ht vng Amazon, xut hin t lu  Venezuela v Brazil. im c bit khin Guarana c mnh danh siu ht l nng lng t Guarana c chuyn ha trong c th mt cch t t  cung cp ngun nng lng bn vng.\r\n\r\nCht x trong guarana kch thch chuyn ng ca rut nn rt c ch cho ngi b to bn, gip gii c v thanh lc ng rut, iu tr cc chng ri lon ng rut nh y hi, tiu chy. Cung cp ngun nng lng cao, kch thch qu trnh gii phng nng lng t cc t bo d tr  m m, kch thch thn kinh trung ng tng cng s tnh to v tp trung. i vi chuyn phng the, guarana gip to hng phn, tng hiu qu quan h tnh dc.\r\n<h4><strong>Km Gluconat 25mg</strong></h4>\r\nKm gluconat c tng hp theo cc phng php hin i v l mt thnh phn quan trng ca rt nhiu loi thuc, khi c hp th vo c th th km gluconat c tc dng nh vi cht km. i vi nam gii, km l thnh phn quan trng c trong tinh dch, gip ci thin v s lng v cht lng ca tinh trng.\r\n<h4><strong>Vitamin C 20mg</strong></h4>\r\nVitamin C c tc dng tng cng sc  khng cho c th, khin c th khe mnh hn. i vi chuyn y, vitamin C gip ko di thi gian giao hp, gim bt mt mi sau khi quan h.\r\n<h4><strong>Bt t 10mg</strong></h4>\r\nBt t gip tng cng lu thng mu  dng vt, lm m vn mch.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Bang</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSn phm gip b thn trng dng, tng cng sinh lc, ci thin chc nng sinh l nam gii, ko di thi gian cng dng, gim au lng, mi gi.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gip kch hot c ch sn sinh Hormone sinh dc nam ni sinh mt cch t nhin.</li>\r\n 	<li>B thn trng dng, tng cng sinh l, phc hi kh nng sinh l nam gii.</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr iu tr ri lon cng dng, xut tinh sm, di tinh, mng tinh lm chm qu trnh mn dc nam.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gip tng cng lu thng mu, tng cng ham mun, khc phc tnh trng ri lon cng dng  nam gii.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/BANG-CEVRAI-60V3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-239 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/BANG-CEVRAI-60V3-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"860\" height=\"573\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>C Bang bn nng s khng cn p lc</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>Bang gip mang n c hi mi  bn ci thin, khc phc tnh trng suy gim chc nng sinh l, mang n s do dai, cng trng v t tin th hin bn lnh n ng ch thc.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"active\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4><strong>Cch dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Liu duy tr hng ngy: 1 vin x 2 ln/ngy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>i tng s dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nam gii t tui trng thnh. (Khng dng cho tr em).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\