(240, 1, '2021-01-19 09:30:15', '2021-01-19 02:30:15', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>Bn lo lng v cc du hiu yu sinh l?</strong></h2>\r\nMun ci thin chuyn phng the, lm g y?\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/23.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-245 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/23-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"791\" height=\"527\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Du hiu yu sinh l khin i sng v chng km hnh phc</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sinh l yu khin bn lo lng, bun phin, mc cm vi nng, hnh phc gia nh dn rn nt.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tc bc sm, d rng trng tht gi nua khin bn t ti khi giao tip.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tiu m nhiu ln, tiu rt, tiu st gy mt n mt ng, c th suy nhc, mt mi, lo u, cn nng gim nhanh.</li>\r\n 	<li>au lng, t mi chn tay, mi gi dn n gim vn ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNam gii   tui sau 40, thn kh suy dn, dn ti cc triu chng thn h, thn yu nh yu sinh l, tiu m nhiu ln, au lng, mi gi...\r\n<blockquote>Cn c gii php lu thng kh huyt, phc hi tn thng  thn, t  iu tr cc triu chng thn yu, thn h.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Sm Nhung B Thn NV</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>B thn trng dng, cnggn mnh ct</strong></h4>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/24.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-246 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/24-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"763\" height=\"763\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Sm Nhung B Thn NV b thn trng dng, phc hi sinh lc cho phi mnh</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>c Cc An ton thc phm cpgiy chng nhn Sm Nhung B Thn NVph hp cc quy nh An ton thc phm.</li>\r\n 	<li>San phm ra i da trn s kt hp gia tinh hoa cua nn y hoc c truyn va ng dung cng ngh y hoc hin ai th gii.</li>\r\n 	<li>Kt hp hon ho hn 20 loi dc liu qu him trong cng 1 sn phm.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gip b thn, trng dng, mnh gn ct, tng cng sinh lc, gip gim tnh trng mn dc nam.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca thc phm chc nng Sm Nhung B Thn NV</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSm nhung b thn NV c thnh phn gm hn 20 loi dc liu qu chia thnh cc nhm tnh cht:\r\n<h4><strong>Nhm phc hi sinh lc</strong></h4>\r\nGm: Nhung hu, Cao ban long,Nhn sm.\r\n\r\nC tc dng rt tt trong vic bi b c th, tng cng sinh lc cho c nam v n, gip c th khe mnh, iu ha v tng cng h min dch.\r\n<div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/tac-dung-cua-nhan-sam.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-238 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/tac-dung-cua-nhan-sam-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"747\" height=\"498\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption>Nhn sm l dc liu qu gip phc hi sinh lc nhanh chng</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4><strong>Nhm b thn</strong></h4>\r\nBao gm: Bch trut, Cu tch,  trng, H th  , Th ty t, Tc on, Xuyn khung, Vin ch,Bch linh, Thc a, Trch T.\r\n\r\nC tc dng tr phong thp, m thn tr dng, ch huyt, mnh gn ct.\r\n<h4><strong>Nhm tng cng sinh l</strong></h4>\r\nBao gm Ba kch,Dm dng hoc, Nhc thung dung.\r\n\r\nC tc dng tng hng phn, tng bi tit tinh dch, b thn trng dng, tng cng sinh lc nam gii.\r\n<h4><strong>Nhm li tiu</strong></h4>\r\nBao gm: Bch hp, Cam tho, ng sm, ng quy, Hoi sn, Lin nhc.\r\n\r\nC tc dng b t v, ch kh, sinh tn dch, gii kht, nhun ph, thanh nhit gii c, dng tm, an thn, b huyt, iu kinh, li gan, thng huyt, tiu sng.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca thc phm chc nng Sm Nhung B Thn NV</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSm nhung b thn NV gip tng cng sinh lc cho nam giihiu qu.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>B thn, trang dng, c tinh, tng cng sinh lc, manh gn ct, an thn, ch tr cc trng hp: tiu tin nhiu ln, chn tay t mi, au lng, mi gi, tc bc sm...</li>\r\n 	<li>Giup giam tinh trang man duc nam, tngcng sinh ly.</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr iu tri va lam giam cac triu chng au lng, moi gi, chan n do thn yu.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/26.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-247 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/26-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"761\" height=\"507\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>V chng thm mn nng, hnh phc t khi bn dng Sm nhung b thn NV</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>Sm nhung b thn NV mang li cho bn sinh lc di do v mnh m, gip bn thnh cng trong mi cuc chinh phc cng nng.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4><strong>Cch dung</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngy ung 2 ln, mi ln 2 vin sng v chiu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung lc i. Mi t dng 4-6 tun.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>i tng s dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nam gii b thn h, au lng mi gi, suy gim chc nng sinh k, mn dc nam sm, di mng tinh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi suy nhc, mt mi, ngi chi th thao, vn ng nhiu, lao ng nng nhc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu </h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSn phm ny khng phi l thuc, khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Bo qun</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nBo qun sn phm  ni kh ro trnh nh nng.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 30 vin</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">HI LINH</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>', 'Thc Phm Chc Nng Sm Nhung B Thn Nv 30 Vin', '<div class=\"prd-dt-xx\">\r\n<table class=\"table-detail\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Thng hiu:</td>\r\n<td>Hi Linh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Xut x thng hiu:</td>\r\n<td>Vit Nam</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Quy cch:</td>\r\n<td>Hp 30 vin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>M sn phm:</td>\r\n<td>00011059</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"prd-dt-desc\">\r\n\r\nSm Nhung B Thn NV gip b thn, trng dng, mnh gn ct, n ng tt, tng cng sinh lc, gip gim tnh trng mn dc nam, yu sinh l, au lng, mi gi.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'thuc-pham-chuc-nang-sam-nhung-bo-than-nv-30-vien', '', '', '2021-01-19 09:30:15', '2021-01-19 02:30:15', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=product&#038;p=240', 0, 'product', '', 0),
