(248, 1, '2021-01-19 09:32:59', '2021-01-19 02:32:59', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>Lnh cm \"chuyn yu\"- ni nim ph n kh ni</strong></h2>\r\nPhi lm g gi trn vn hnh phc gia nh?\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-256 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"828\" height=\"552\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Ph n lnh cm chuyn gi chn gy nh hng hnh phc gia nh</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bn b kinh nguyt khng u, au u, kh ng dn n lo lng, mt mi, suy sp tinh thn.</li>\r\n 	<li>au lng, au c, khp, nng bng, bc ho khin bn kh chu, gp ai cng cu gt.</li>\r\n 	<li>Kh rt m o, gim hay mt ham mun tnh dc khin bn s gn chng, quan h v chng v th m dn lc c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPh n tui cng cao, qu trnh lo ha din ra cng mnh khin t l si c trn trong m o gim dn, cht nhn tit ra t i, t  gy cm gic au n, mt i khoi cm, kh khn cho vic gn gi.\r\n<blockquote>Cn c gii php tc ng nhm lm chm qu trnh lo ha trong c th n gii tui trung nin, t  ngn nga cc triu chng yu sinh l.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>thc phm chc nngOnagre</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Tng cng khoi cm, phc hisc khe ph n tin mn kinh</strong></h4>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/onagre-ho-tro-sinh-ly-nu-tien-man-kinh.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-255 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/onagre-ho-tro-sinh-ly-nu-tien-man-kinh-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"718\" height=\"718\" /></a>\r\n\r\nOnagre phc hi sinh l cho ph n tin mn kinh</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm vi cc thnh phn dng cht c ngun gc t thin nhin an ton.</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr ngn nga v lm gim cctriu chng tin mn kinh ph n.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tng khoi cm, phc hiln da mn mng, lm chm qu trnh lo ha.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Onagre</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nOnagre c bo ch t cc thnh phn dng cht c ngun gc thin nhin nc Php.\r\n<h4><strong>Du hoa Anh Tho (Onagre Oil)</strong></h4>\r\nC tc dng h tr kh nng sinh sn cho n gii bng cch tng cht nhn cho m o, ci thin cht lng cc lp lt cht nhy c t cung, gip cho tinh trng ca nam gii sng lu hn, tng kh nng th thai. Ngoi ra, tinh cht c trong du Hoa Anh Tho cn gip ngn nga lo ha da v lm chm qu trnh lo ha  ph n ngoi 30.\r\n<h4><strong>Vitamin E nguyn cht (D-Alpha tocopherol)</strong></h4>\r\nGp phn ci thin tnh dc  n gii, nng cao kt qu iu tr v sinh, lm gim tin trnh lo ha ca da v tc.\r\n<div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-254 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/3-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"845\" height=\"563\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption>Vitamin E gip ngn chn qu trnh lo ha</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4><strong>Bovin gelatin</strong></h4>\r\nBt gelatin c cha cc thnh phn axit amin, gip xy dng v ti to collagen cho c th c bit l phn da, gip da trng, mn mng. Ngoi ra, tinh cht bt Gelatin cn c tc dng gim au khp  ph n trung nin.\r\n<h4><strong>Glycerin</strong></h4>\r\nL mt loi ru a chc c to thnh bi s lin kt ca gc hyrocacbon C3H5 vi 3 nhm OH vi cng thc ha hc l C3H5(OH)3. C tc dng cp m cho ln da khin da mm mn, khe p; lm chm qu trnh lo ha da; lm sch da, h tr iu tr mn trng c, nhim trng da.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Onagre</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nOnagre gip ngn nga triu chng sm ca yu sinh l n.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>H tr iu tr cc triu chng tin kinh nguyt v mn kinh: kinh nguyt khng u, mt mi, kh ng, cu gt, nhc u, au lng, au c, khp, au bng, nng bng, bc ho, kh rt m o, gim hay mt ham mun tnh dc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lm p da:Cung cp cc axit bo khng no thc vt v vitamin E gip dng da, chng li qu trnh lo ha ca t bo, h tr duy tr v ci thin s tr trung v v p ca ln da.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-253 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/4-300x177.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"783\" height=\"463\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>c chng cng chiu s l iu bn lun cm nhn</div>\r\n<blockquote>Onagre gip bn quyn r v tr p nh thu i mi, khin chng khng th no ri mt.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4><strong>Cch dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>H trdng da, chng lo ho: Ung 1vin x 2ln/ ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr lm gim cc triu chng tin kinh nguyt, tin mn kinh v mn kinh: Ung 2 vin x 2 ln/ngy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>i tng s dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ph n t 13 tui tr ln. (Khng s dng cho tr emdi 13 tui, ph n mang thai v cho con b).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu </h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSn phm ny khng phi l thuc, khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Bo qun</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n ni kh thong, nhit  khng qu 30  C, hp v sinh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 60 vin</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Laboratoire Cevrai</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">FRANCE</div>', 'Vin Ung H Tr Sinh L N Onagre Cevrai 60 Vin', '<div class=\"prd-dt-xx\">\r\n<table class=\"table-detail\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Thng hiu:</td>\r\n<td>Cervai</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Xut x thng hiu:</td>\r\n<td>Php</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Quy cch:</td>\r\n<td>Hp 60 vin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>M sn phm:</td>\r\n<td>00345375</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"prd-dt-desc\">\r\n\r\nOnagre h tr iu tr cc triu chng tin kinh nguyt v mn kinh, ng thi dng