(284, 1, '2021-01-19 09:44:51', '2021-01-19 02:44:51', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>Chng Chn, Chng Ch V Da Sm Nm</strong></h2>\r\nKhc phc ngay thi, trc khi qu mun no cc ch em.\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/skin-care-vien-uong-giam-tham-nam.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-292 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/skin-care-vien-uong-giam-tham-nam-300x140.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1029\" height=\"480\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Da sm nm, tn nhang khin bn thiu t ti</div>\r\n</div>\r\nGng mt y nm khin ch em ph n nh phi sng chung vi l bi:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>i u cng phi trang im tht k, che ht vng nm xu x mi dm bc ra khi nh, tht bt tin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chng d chn, d ch xu, ch gi v nm chi cht trn mt, khin bn lo lng, t ti, bun chn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Da sm nm khin bn khng hong, nng sut lm vic cng gim st, stress ko di khin nm cng thm t.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNm xut hin do s gia tng qu mc ca cc hc sc t da melanin, pht trin  tng h b - tng su nht ca da. M nguyn nhn chnh khin sc t ny da tng l do tc ng ca nh nng mt tri.\r\n<blockquote>Do , cn c gii php tc ng su vo tng h b, lm gim s ph hy ca tia UV, cung cp dng cht cn thit cho ln da.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Skin Care Pigment Clear</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Chit xut vi to lc - nh bay thm nm, da trng mn mng</strong></h4>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/skin-care-vien-uong-giam-tham-nam1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-291 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/skin-care-vien-uong-giam-tham-nam1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"771\" height=\"771\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Skin Care Pigment Clear lm m thm nm, cho ln da trng sng</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>c bo ch t Astaxathin c trong chit xut vi to lc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lm m thm nm trn da, cung cp cc dng cht gip da khe mnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bo v ln da trc tc hi ca nh nng mt tri.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Skin Care Pigment Clear</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSkin Care Pigment Clear c chit xut t vi to lc, chm rut ni, qu lu giu Vitamin C v cc cht chng oxy ha.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Chit xut vi to lc cha n 2% astaxanthin</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Astaxathin trong chit xut vi to lc l mt thnh phn t nhin chng oxy ha rt mnh m, cht ny mnh hn 6.000 ln so vi vitamin Carotenoid, 800 ln so vi CoQ10 v hn 550 ln so vi Catechin tr xanh. Nh u th y m s dng Astaxanthin s gip da c mn mng v tng  n hi, lm m cc vt thm nm, vt nhn v tn nhang trn da.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ngoi ra, nu da b chy nng th Astaxanthin cn gip thm nhp tng t bo da v gim s ph hy ca tia UVA, hot ng nh mt loi kem chng nng t bn trong gip bo v da.</p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/skin-care-vien-uong-giam-tham-nam3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-290 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/skin-care-vien-uong-giam-tham-nam3-300x188.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"791\" height=\"496\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption>Astaxanthin trong to lc gip thm nhp tng t bo da v gim s ph hy ca tia UVA</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Chit xut chm rut ni</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Giu vitamin C, khong cht v axit amin, bo v cc nguyn bo si da (l t bo to ra collagen) khi qu trnh oxi ha.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Vitamin C</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Gip gim vim, bo v da chng li qu trnh oxi ha, h tr sn xut collagen cho da.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Chit xut qu lu cha n 40% ellagsyre</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">H tr qu trnh sn xut collagen v elastin, chng lo ha, chng oxi ha, gim np nhn, lm gim s hnh thnh ung th da.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Chit xut tiu en cha n 40% piperine</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cha cc cht chng oxy ha, gim np nhn v cc m tn nhang, i mi, gip tr ha da, chng ung th da do tip xc qu mc vi tia cc tm c hi, c c tnh khng vim, gip gim mn, gip da mm mi v rng r.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Niacin</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">L mt dng vitamin B3 gip dng m da, gim cc triu chng ng  da, gim np nhn, rnh nhn da, gim nm da, tng  n hi v phng chng ung th da.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Km</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">L thnh phn chnh trong cc loi kem chng nng, gip bo v da khi nh nng mt tri, lm gim au do chy nng, lm mm da nt n, gip vt thng mau lnh, gim kch ng v vim da, lm gim mn trng c.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>ng 1mg</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Gip ti to da, gip cha lnh tn thng da, kch thch sn xut collagen, gim np nhn, gip da sn chc, mn mng.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Skin Care Pigment Clear</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSkin Care Pigment Clear gip nh bay cc vt nm, gip da sng mn, rng r:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gim cc vt thm nm trn da, gip da sng mn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gim kh da v nhn da.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch lo ha.</li>\r\n 	<li>B sung cc cht dinh dng tng cng nui dng v bo v da.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/skin-care-vien-uong-giam-tham-nam-4.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-289 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/skin-care-vien-uong-giam-tham-nam-4-300x158.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"832\" height=\"438\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Khng cn sm nm, da bn trng mn nh cnh hoa ngc ng</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>Xa tan ni lo sm nm, tn nhang ch vi 2 vin Skin Care Pigment Clear mi ngy. Chng m nh iu  v trng bn lc no cng tht tr trung, rng r.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"active\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4><strong>Cch dng</strong></h4>\r\nUng 2 vin mi ngy vi nc lc.\r\n<h4><strong>i tng s dng</strong></h4>\r\nNgi trn 12 tui mun duy tr ln da p, khe mnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c thng tin v tc dng