(293, 1, '2021-01-19 09:47:17', '2021-01-19 02:47:17', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>Nu Gi Thanh Xun, Ai M Chng Mun</strong></h2>\r\nNhng thi gian li v tnh khin nhan sc ca bn xung cp ri?\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/720.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-301 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/720-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"698\" height=\"465\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Np nhn, chy x l du hiu c th thiu ht collagen</div>\r\n</div>\r\nTui 18, 20 c l l khong thi gian p nht, cng l nh cao nhan sc ca mi ngi ph n. Ai cng mun thi gian dng li  la tui   sng vi nhng iu p nht. Nhng qu tht, i khng nh l m, nhan sc ca bn c theo nm thng m xung cp.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Da d nhn nheo: Vt chn chim ni ui mt, rnh ci ngy cng su, np nhn trn trn...Mi mt np nhn nh li bo cho bn bit mnh ang gi i, da ang lo ha dn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ln da mt tnh n hi: V cng bng, mn mng ca ln da ngy y  bin mt. Gi y, bn ch cn li ln da mt tnh n hi, chy x</li>\r\n 	<li>Da sn si kh rp: T bao gi da ca bn  mt i  m t nhin vn c, nn mi tri tr lnh l b mt da li tr nn cng tc khin bn v cng kh chu.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSau 30 lng collagen trong c th b tiu hao kh nhiu nhng kh nng t sn sinh collagen trong c th li suy gim. y chnh l nguyn nhn dn n tnh trng lo ha da nhanh chng.\r\n<blockquote>B sung ngun collagen cho c th chnh l cha kha quan trng nht  bn c th lm chm li qu trnh lo ha ca da v c th,  da lun gi c nt thanh xun.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Healthy And Beauty Collagen</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Cng thc Nht Bn - B sung collagen thy phn cho ln da lun ti tr</strong></h4>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/721.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-300 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/721-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"834\" height=\"834\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Healthy and Beauty Collagen - b quyt lu gi thanh xun cho ph n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Collagen thy phn dng nc gip