(317, 1, '2021-01-19 09:52:52', '2021-01-19 02:52:52', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>Siro n Ngon Tiu Ha Khe BBear</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><b>n ung tht d dng, b vn cao tm vc</b></h3>\r\nSiro n Ngon Tiu Ha Khe BBear l gii php gip gii quyt dt im tnh trng bing ca tr, gip b n ngon ming v c h tiu ha khe mnh hn.\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Siro-an-ngon-BBear.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-322 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Siro-an-ngon-BBear-300x257.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"821\" height=\"703\" /></a></div>\r\n<div><em>Siro n Ngon Tiu Ha Khe BBear Thnh Cng 20 ng</em></div>\r\nThc n nhm chn, h tiu ha khng khehay thay i mi trng c th khin b b bing n. Nu tnh trng bing n  tr ko di s khin c th hp thu dinh dng km, suy dinh dng hay t hn l dn n suy gim h min dch.Siro n Ngon Tiu Ha Khe BBear b sungLysine, enzyme cng khong cht cn thit gip b n ngon ming, tng kh nng hp th cht dinh dng, ci thinh min dch khe mnh.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><strong>Gip n ngon ming</strong></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSiron Ngon Tiu Ha Khe Bbear cha thnh phn chnh l Lysine - mtloi axit amin m c th b khng th t tng hp. Lysine gip c th b tng hp collagen, tng cng hp th canxi, tng cng h min dch v h tr b n ngon ming.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><strong>B sung cc loi men tiu ha cn thit</strong></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTr nh c h tiu ha cn non nt. Nu h tiu ha khng khe b cng n khng ngon ming, t  d dn n bing n. Sn phm cha enzyme amylase l loi men tiu ha rt cn thit cho tr, nht l i vi nhng b b ri lon tiu ha hoc bing n. Enzyme amylase c b sung vo c th gip tiu ha nhanh chng thc n, lm trng ng tiu ha, t  gim cm gic kh chu do n khng tiu v kch thch s thm n  b.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><strong>Tng cng min dch - Pht trin ti u</strong></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTnh trng bing n s dn n c th thiu cht dinh dng. V vy, bn cnh lysine v enzym tiu ha, sn phm cn b sung cc vitamin nhm B, D, axit folic, khong cht v DHA nhm cn bng vi cht dinh dng trong c th gip bpht trin ti u, nng cao h min dch.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h4><strong>Hng v thm ngon, d dng s dng</strong></h4>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSiro n Ngon Tiu Ha Khe BBear c kt cu dngdung dch lng mang hng v thm ngon, to cm gic th v cho b khi s dng. Liu lng c phn chiachun xc trongtng ng nh ring bit, gip bn d dngcho b ung, cng m bo v sinh v cht lngcho sn phm.\r\n\r\nSiro n Ngon Tiu Ha Khe BBear l mt sn phm ca Thnh Cng Pharma.Trong sut qu trnhpht trin, Dc Thnh Cng  t c nhiu thnh tu to ln, khng nh cht lng trn th trng vi cc khu nh my ttiu chun ca T chc Y t Th gii (WHO), t chng nhn GMP. ng gp ng k chos pht trin ca nghnh cng nghip Dc Vit Nam.\r\n<blockquote>Siron Ngon Tiu Ha Khe BBear -gip b n ngon ming v hp th dng cht ti u t mn ngon m nu.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Bbear</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n 	<li>L-Lysin: 120mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Enzym Amylase: 250IU</li>\r\n 	<li>Enzym Protease: 50IU</li>\r\n 	<li>Vitamin B1: 1.2mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Vitamin B2: 0.5mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Vitamin B6: 0.5mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Vitamin D3: 100IU</li>\r\n 	<li>Acid folic: 30mcg</li>\r\n 	<li>Magnesi (Magnesi gluconat): 15mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Calci (Calci gluconat): 11.2mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Km (Km gluconat): 1mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Inulin: 100mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Thymomodulin: 20mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Sa ong cha: 5mg</li>\r\n 	<li>DHA: 50mcg</li>\r\n 	<li>Ph liu: ng knh trng, nc tinh khit, natri benzoat, hng da va  10ml.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Bbear</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSn phmn Ngon Tiu Ha Khe Bbear b sung lysin, mt s vitamin, enzym v khong cht gip n ngon ming, h tr kh nng tiu ho v hp thu cht dinh dng.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"active\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nUng sau ba n.\r\n\r\nTr em 2 - 5 tui: Ngy dng 1 ng.\r\n\r\nTr em t 6 - 12 tui: Ung 1 ng/ ln, ngy 1 - 2 ln.\r\n\r\nTr em trn 12 tui v ngi ln: Ung 1 ng/ln, ngy dng t 2-3 ln.\r\n\r\nTham kho  kin bc s khi dng cho tr em di 2 tui hoc dng liu ln hn.\r\n\r\n<strong>i tng s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nSn phm n Ngon Tiu Ha Khe Bbear thch hp s dng cho ngi ln v tr em t 2 tui tr ln.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c thng tin v tc dng ph ca sn phm.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu </h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSn phm ny khng phi l thuc v khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.\r\n\r\nc k hng dn s dng trc khi dng.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Bo qun</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nBo qun ni kh ro, thong mt, trnh nh sng, nhit  di 30  C.\r\n\r\n xa tm tay tr em.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 4 v x 5 ng</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">THNH CNG</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>', 'Siro n Ngon Tiu Ha Khe Bbear Thnh Cng 20 ng', '<div class=\"prd-dt-xx\">\r\n<table class=\"table-detail\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Thng hiu:</td>\r\n<td>Thnh Cng</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Xut x thng hiu:</td>\r\n<td>Vit Nam</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Quy cch:</td>\r\n<td>Hp 4 v x 5 ng</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>M sn phm:</td>\r\n<td>00019020</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"prd-dt-desc\">\r\n\r\nSn phmn Ngon Tiu Ha Khe Bbear b sung lysin, mt s vitamin, enzym v khong cht gip n ngon ming, h tr kh nng tiu ho v hp thu cht dinh dng.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'siro-an-ngon-tieu-hoa-khoe-bbear-thanh-cong-20-ong', '', '', '2021-01-19 09:52:52', '2021-01-19 02:52:52', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=product&#038;p=317', 0, 'product', '', 0),
