(323, 1, '2021-01-19 09:55:09', '2021-01-19 02:55:09', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>M C C t, B Th C Ngm</strong></h2>\r\nCuc chin mi ba n gia m v b vn ko di bt tn mi thi.\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/siro-an-ngon-healthy-new-kid.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-331 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/siro-an-ngon-healthy-new-kid-300x169.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"807\" height=\"455\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Tr vn khng chu n d m c c d dnh bng mn n b thch</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNgoi vic phi ngh mn no tt cho con, mn no y  dinh dng. M cn au u v phi ngh 36 k  d b n. B khng n c l nguyn nhn ca mi lo lng  m.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>B s chm pht trin: Vic n ung nh hng trc tip n kh nng pht trin ca tr. Tr khng n c ng ngha vi vic c th khng  cht dn n chm pht trin.</li>\r\n 	<li>D dng mc bnh: Tr khng n ung c s lm sc  khng yu i, khin vi khun, virus d dng tn cng v gy bnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Km pht trin v tr tu: Khi cc yu cu dinh dng khng c p ng, tr tu v kh nng nhn bit ca tr cng chm pht trin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>Nguyn nhn ca s bing n bt ngun t vic c th tr thiu ht cc vitamin, khong cht cn thit. B sung ngun vitamin, khong cht y ch chnh l cha kha  gii quyt tnh trng tr li n.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Siro n Ngon Healthy New Kids</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>B sung vitamin, gip tr n ngon ming</strong></h4>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/siro-an-ngon-healthy-new-kid1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-330 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/siro-an-ngon-healthy-new-kid1-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"848\" height=\"848\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Siro Healthy New Kids kch thch tr n ngon</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>c chit xut da trn cc thnh phn vitamin v khong cht thit yu.</li>\r\n 	<li>c B Y T cpgiy chng nhnl sn phm an ton.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gip tr n ngon ming, hp th tt, tng sc  khng v pht trin ton din.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Healthy New Kids</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSiro Healthy New Kid c chit xut da trn cc thnh phn acid amin, cc vitamin v khong cht thit yu.\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Vitamin D3</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Vai tr ca Vitamin D3 Vitamin D3 c vai tr rt quan trng trong qu trnh to xng nh tc dng ln chuyn ha cc cht v c m ch yu l Canxi v phosphat.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Vitamin B</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">C tc dng lm gim vim thn kinh v gim au. Kch thch gan bi tit cht c lm gim phn ng vim ca da.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Vitamin B2</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Vitamin B2 tt cho mt, da, h thn kinh, ng thi gii phng nng lng c th t thc phm bn tiu th.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Vitamin B6</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tt cho tr no ca tr, gip tr pht trin h thn kinh, thng minh, nhanh nhn.</p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/siro-an-ngon-healthy-new-kid2.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-329 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/siro-an-ngon-healthy-new-kid2-300x222.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"801\" height=\"593\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption>Siro Healthy New Kids b sung y  vitamin cho b</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Vitamin B5</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tng cng h thng thn kinh, gip no b hot ng tt, tr ng ngon su gic.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>DHA</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> tr em, DHA rt quan trng cho s pht trin no, h thn kinh v vng mc. Thiu ht DHA tc ng trc tip n  thng minh, kh nng c, ghi nh v cc hnh vi.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Men bia</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Kch thch s hp th thc n, li tiu ho, chng thiu mu, cn bng v bo v h thn kinh</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cc vi cht khc</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Lysine HCl, Taurin, Calcium Lactate, Km Gluconat, Selen,Thymomodulin.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Healthy New Kids</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nNhng vitamin, khong cht c trong Siro n Ngon Healthy New Kids s gip b ci thin ton din v sc khe.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gip tr n ngon ming: Cc vitamin, khong cht s gip tr n ngon ming hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hp th tt: Kch thch tiu ha, tr hp th dinh dng tt hn</li>\r\n 	<li>Tng sc  khng: Gip tr c c ch khng sinh t nhin khi cc vi khun, virus gy bnh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/siro-an-ngon-healthy-new-kid3.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-328 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/siro-an-ngon-healthy-new-kid3-300x168.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"848\" height=\"475\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Mt mung siro mi ngy, b mau n chng ln</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>M tht yn tm khi b nh mnh n ngon, hp thu tt, chng pht trin v th cht v tr tu. Thi gian dnh cho nhng trn chin ko di mi ba n  chm dt, m c th cng b tham gia nhiu hot ng b ch hn cho tng lai ca b.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4><strong>Cch dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tr t 2-6 tui: 5ml/ln x 2 ln/ngy</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr t 7-10 tui: 10ml/ln x 2 ln/ngy</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr trn 10 tui v ngi ln: 15ml/ln x 2 ln/ngy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>i tng s dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tr em gy g, m yu, suy dinh dng, sc  khng yu, tr b bnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi suy nhc c th, mt mi, chn n, ngi thiu vitamin nhm B.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu </h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSn phm ny khng phi l thuc v khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Bo qun</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nNi kh ro, thong mt, trnh nh sng trc tip\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\"