(423, 1, '2021-01-19 10:29:13', '2021-01-19 03:29:13', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>Khng phi b m no cng may mn c  sa cho con b</strong></h2>\r\nNu m b mt sa - Lm th no  kch thch tit sa di do cho con?\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/20170412_025236_502527_khoc-dem-1.max-800x800-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-431 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/20170412_025236_502527_khoc-dem-1.max-800x800-1-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"704\" height=\"469\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">M thiu sa, con nh thit thi</div>\r\nKhoa hc  chng minh, sa m l ngun dinh dng hon ho nht dnh cho tr. c bit trong nhng ngy thng u i, nu cho tr b sa m y  s cung cp cc dng cht thit yu, khng th t nhin, l nn tng cho s pht trin ton din ca b v sau.\r\n\r\nNu m khng  sa cho b trong giai on u i, b d mc cc triu chng sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bb suy dinh dng: Tr chm tng cn, khng ln cn thm ch l st cn, gim cn trong 2-3 thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>B chm pht trin: t vn ng, chm i ng, b ngi, t vui chi, km linh hot so vi cng la tui.</li>\r\n 	<li>B hay quy khc: Tr bun bc, bing n, n t, hay khc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sc  khng ca b yu: Tr hay b ri lon tiu ha, thng xuyn mc cc bnh nhim trng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNguyn nhn khin cho m b mt sa l do ch  dinh dng khng  cht, tinh thn cng thng, lo u, trm cm, cho con b, vt sa khng ng cch, mc cc bnh lin quan n ni tit...\r\n<blockquote>  sa cho con, cn c bin php kch thch c th tit hc mn Prolactin tit sa, tng hp th dinh dng v tng cng chuyn ha trong c th m, gip tng s lng v cht lng sa m.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Tasuamum</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Tng tit sa - Cho b yu bng lun cng trn</strong></h4>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/giai-ma-hien-tuong-co-cari-goi-sua-ve-dat-dao-bau-bau-1-1509331224-width569height492.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-430 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/giai-ma-hien-tuong-co-cari-goi-sua-ve-dat-dao-bau-bau-1-1509331224-width569height492-300x259.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"795\" height=\"686\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Tasuamum gip tng tit sa</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>C ngun gc t tho dc v gip tng c s lng, cht lng sa m.</li>\r\n 	<li>L sn phm u tin c cha Tinh cht c cari vi Thnh phn Galactagogues kch thch tuyn sa v tng sn lng sa m vt tri.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thnh phn cao Thin Mn Chm gip tng 3,5 ln Prolactin (hooc-mn tit sa m) gip sa m nhiu hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm c kim nh cht lng bi Vin y dc c truyn Tu Tnh.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Cm Li Sa Tasuamum</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCm li sa Tasuamum l sn phm chit xut thin nhin, cng thc hon ho v khoa hc c cng thc  cho m, khe cho b.\r\n<h4><strong>Tinh cht C Cari</strong></h4>\r\nC tc dng tng kh nng tit sa, tng cht lng sa, h tr tiu ha, nng cao kh nng chng ung th, c bit l ung th v. Ngoi ra, hm lng ln cht flavonoid trong loi c ny gip gia tng estrogen t nhin, gip y nhanh qu trnh hnh thnh t bo mi  ngc, gii quyt trit  vn  t sa, thiu sa  m sau sinh.\r\n<h4><strong>B sung Beta - Glucan</strong></h4>\r\nGip kch thch h min dch t nhin, tng cng hot ng ca cc i thc bo v kch thch tng cht hot ho t bo min dch. c bit Beta - Glucan phng chng nhim trng do vi khun, virus...\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Untitled-6-01-600x600-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-429 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Untitled-6-01-600x600-1-300x257.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"664\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption>Tasuamum s kt hp cc dc liu thin nhin</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4><strong>B sung thm thnh phn Canxi Nano</strong></h4>\r\nGip c th b bu hp thu canxi tt nht, c th ln 99%. Canxi Nano tham gia vo qu trnh hnh thnh pht trin h xng, rng  thai nhi, d dng hp thu vo c th.\r\n<h4><strong>DHA</strong></h4>\r\nDng cht cn thit cho s pht trin t bo vng mc mt v l nn tng khng th thiu cho s pht trin tr tu ca tr.\r\n<h4><strong>L-Lysin, taurin v cc thnh phn khc</strong></h4>\r\nL-Lysin, taurin v cc thnh phn khc<strong></strong>bao gm y  cc loi vitamin, khong cht thit yu nh magie, photpho, km gip cho c th m v b pht trin khe mnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Cm Li Sa Tasuamum</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCm li sa PQA l s kt hp tinh ty t nhng bi thuc t ngun tho dc hon ton thin nhin, an ton cho b, hiu qu cho m.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Li sa, tng tit sa, kch thch tng tit sa  ph n sau sinh, ang trong thi k cho con b.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tng cht lng sa  b m ang trong thi k cho con b:Gip m tng cng hp thu dng cht v tng chuyn ha nng lng, dng cht gip sa m nhiu dinh dng hn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/phai-lam-sao-khi-be-ngung-bu-me-dot-ngot-nguyen-nhan-khien-tre-bo-bu-me-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-428 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/phai-lam-sao-khi-be-ngung-bu-me-dot-ngot-nguyen-nhan-khien-tre-bo-bu-me-2-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"789\" height=\"789\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Tasuamum m nhiu sa, b pht trin nhanh</div>\r\n<blockquote>S dng cm li sa Tasuamum bu sa m cng trn. M c nhiu sa, sa c  cht dinh dng cho em b b tha thch, b bm v khe mnh, b n nhanh chng ln, pht trin ton din.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4><strong>Cch dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngy ung: 2-3 ln, mi ln 2 gi.</li>\r\n 	<li>t ung lin tc 4  6 tun.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>i tng s dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dng cho ph n cho con b.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu </h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Hiu qu iu tr ph t