(438, 1, '2021-01-19 10:33:30', '2021-01-19 03:33:30', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>Ly chng  lu m vn cha th th thai</strong></h2>\r\nD  chy cha khp ni nhng kt qu ch lm bn thm chn nn?\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/ovumcare-capsule-3x10-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-446 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/ovumcare-capsule-3x10-1-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"795\" height=\"530\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Bn ang lng g cha c em b</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPh n sau khi kt hn tht s phi chu kh nhiu p lc, nht l khi ly nhau  lu m bn vn cha c \"tin vui\".\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>p lc t 2 bn gia nh: ng b ni ngoi u trng chu, c nhc mi khng thi, thm ch l trch mng.</li>\r\n 	<li>p lc trong i sng v chng: d chng khng ai ni ra nhngr rng 2 v chng ngycng xa cch.</li>\r\n 	<li>p lc trong chnh bn thn bn: mt mi, b tc, thm ch l tuyt vng vi chnh mnh v  th nhiu cch m khng thay i c g.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThu hiu c ni lng v tht s ng cm vi bn. C th bn cha bit nguyn nhn ca chng him mun l do ri lon bung trng v hi chng bung trng a nang. Hi chng nydn n thiu ht cc cht dinh dng, ri lon cc cht chng oxy ha lm gim kh nng rng trng hoc trng gp tinh trng gy ra tnh trng him mun  ph n.\r\n<blockquote> tng kh nng c thai, cn b sung thiu ht cc vi cht dinh dng, cn bng ni tit, lm dy nim mc,  kch thch rng trng, tng kh nng trng gp tinh trng.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Vin ung</strong><strong>O</strong><strong>vumcare</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Cng Thc Ton Din - Tng Kh Nng Mang Thai Cho Ph N</strong></h4>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/ovumcare-capsule-3x101-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-445 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/ovumcare-capsule-3x101-1-300x100.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"846\" height=\"282\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Ovumcare Tng kh nang mang thai cho ph n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Cng thc ton din vi a dng cht, c kim nghim lm sng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tng kh nng th thai  ph n v sinh do cc hi chng bung trng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sn xut trn dy chuyn hin i ca Nht,t tiu chun GMP-WHO.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Ovumcare</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nVin ung b trng Ovumcare Capsules vi cc l s kt hp hon ho ca cc thnh phn dng cht thit yu cho sc khe sinh sn ph n.\r\n<h4><strong>Inositol</strong></h4>\r\nto p ng Insulin  ph n bo ph v nh cn b bung trng a nang, lm tng kh nng rng trng v gim androgen. ng vai tr l tin cht trong s tng hp phosphoinositides, l cc cht dn truyn tn hiu lin quan n cc chc nng ca t bo, trong  c s sinh trng ca t bo. Inositol lm tng t l rng trng  ph n c kinh nguyt khng u hoc bung trng a nang.\r\n<h4><strong>Chromium</strong></h4>\r\nL mt cht cn cho s iu ho hot ng ca Insulin, thc y  nhy ca Insulin\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/ovumcare-capsule-3x102-1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-444\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/ovumcare-capsule-3x102-1-212x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"746\" height=\"1056\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption>Ovumcare Capsules cng thc ton din gip tng kh nng th thai  ph n</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4><strong>Magnesium - Km - ng</strong></h4>\r\nL cc nguyn t vi lng rt quan trng trong chuyn ha, lu gi, s dng nng lng, iu ha v tng hp  300 h thng enzym, iu ha chuyn ha trung gian, tng hp DNA v RNA, tng hp cu trc t bo pht trin sinh sn v cu trc mng t bo. S thiu ht ca cc khong cht ny l nguyn nhn gy ra v sinh, sy thai,bt thng thai nghn hoc cao huyt p do thai , sy thai,  non, cht lu.\r\n<h4><strong>L- Arginine</strong></h4>\r\nCi thin to dch  c t cung, to trng, cc mch mu  ni mc t cung v h tr qu trnh bm ca bo thai\r\n<h4><strong>Cc cht chng oxy ha nh Vitamin A, C, E, Selenium</strong></h4>\r\nCc cht chng oxy ha nh Vitamin A, C, E, Selenium.l gim s mt cn bng v cc cht chng oxy ha.l gim s mt cn bng v cc cht chng oxy ha\r\n<h4><strong>Vitamin nhm B v cc cht dinh dng</strong></h4>\r\nVi mt s lng thch hp lm gim s tng nng  homocysteine trong mu, do  ngn nga v sinh do thiu cc cht dinh dng.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Ovumcare</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nVin ungOVUMCARE l la chn tt nht cho bnh nhn bung trng a nang.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tng t l c thai trn ph n v sinh do cc ri lon v bung trng v hi chng bung trng a nang (PCOS).</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr iu trthiu ht cc cht dinh dng v cc ri lon cc cht chng oxy ha lin quan n v sinh.</li>\r\n 	<li>S dng phi hp vi cc thuc khc kch thch rng trng v h tr cc k thut sinh n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/ovumcare-capsule-3x103-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-443 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/ovumcare-capsule-3x103-1-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"726\" height=\"484\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Ovumcare Capsules gip tng kh nng c thai  ph n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>S dng Ovumcare Capsules gip tng kh nng c thai  ph n him mun. a thin chc lm m n gn hn vi bn.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4><strong>Cch dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ung 1 vin/ ln x 2 ln/ ngy trong hoc ngay sau ba n chnh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>i tngs dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dng cho ph n him mun do cc ri lon v bung trng v hi chng v bung trng a nang.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng cho ph n thiu ht cc vi cht dinh dng v ph n b ri lon cc cht chng oxy ha lin quan n him mun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng kt hp vi cc thuc khc  kch thch rng trng v h tr cc k thut sinh .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nMt vi bnh nhn c th c ri lon d dy rut nh khi mi bt u dng Ovumcare. Tuy nhin, cc ri 