(447, 1, '2021-01-19 10:39:31', '2021-01-19 03:39:31', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>Tiu ng phi n ung king khem kh s</strong></h2>\r\nTt c cng ch v bn s ch s ng huyt ca mnh tng ln\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/news-1476694024.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-455 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/news-1476694024-300x204.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"821\" height=\"558\" /></a>\r\n\r\nng huyt tng cao lun l ni m nh ca bn?</div>\r\nBnh i tho ng l th, d khng c biu hin g qu c bit nhng mt khi bn mc phi chng bnh ny u phi king khem ht mc. Nu khng king c ng cch, chng bnh i tho ng s gy ra nhng hu qu khng ng.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bin chng cp tnh: Bn c th hn m, thm ch t vong mt khi lng ng ln qu cao m khng c cp cu kp thi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tn thng thn kinh thc vt s dn n cc biu hin lon nhp tim, tiu chy, to bn, i tin khng kim sot c,...</li>\r\n 	<li>Tn thng thn do hm lng ng trong mu cao, gy tn thng hng triu vi mch ti thn dn n suy gim cc chc nng lc, bi tit ca thn v suy thn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nbnh tiu ngbt ngun khi ch s ng huyt trong c th tng cao, nguyn nhn c th do chnh ch  n ung v sinh hot hng ngy ca bn.\r\n<blockquote>Cch hiu qu nht  n nh lng ng huyt chnh l c mt ch  n ung hp l, kt hp cc thc phm gip kim sot ng.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Vin ung Blood Sugar Control</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Kim sot ng huyt, ngn nga tiu ng</strong></h4>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/00015043-blood-sugar-control-60v-1472-5b18_large.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-454 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/00015043-blood-sugar-control-60v-1472-5b18_large-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"756\" height=\"756\" /></a>\r\n\r\nBlood Sugar Control cng thc ca cc bc s khuyn dng</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>c nghin cu v sn xut ti M.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chit xut t tho dc thin nhin an ton cho sc khe.</li>\r\n 	<li>Kim s