(470, 1, '2021-01-19 10:45:32', '2021-01-19 03:45:32', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><b>i tho ng - k git ngi thm lng</b></h2>\r\nGii php no gipbnngn nga bnh i tho ng ph hy ni tng?\r\n<div><img src=\"https://hellobacsi.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/trieu-chung-benh-tieu-duong-o-nam-gioi.jpg\" alt=\"i tho ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" />Bnh i tho ng ang dn ph hy c th bn?</div>\r\nTiu ng l bnh khng ly nhim nhng c mc  ph bin trn ton cu. Theo bc s ti bnh vin Bch Mai, ring ti Vit Nam nm 2015 c ti 3,5 triu bnh nhn. V con s ny s tng ln hong 6.1 triu ngi vo nm 2040.\r\n\r\nBan u bnh khng c biu hin g r rng nhng lu dn n s lm tn thng nhiu c quan ni tng trong c th bn.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Kht nc v i tiu nhiu: Khi b tiu ng bn lin tc cm thy kht nc. Nhng khi ung nc vo li i tiu nhiu ln.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt mi: bn thy c th nh cn kit nng lng, hay bun ng, u oi, mt b m nhe, tay chn t b.</li>\r\n 	<li>Stcn: bn s thy cn nng ca mnh st gim r rt d khng n king hoc tp th dc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vt thng lu lnh: nu chng may bn b t tay th vt thng s rt lu lnh thm ch l lot trong thi gian di.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNguyn nhn chnh ca cc vn  m bn gp phi nh trn c th gii thch bi l do duy nht l lng glucose trong mu b tng mn tnh.\r\n<blockquote> iu tr bnh i tho ng hiu qu, cna lng glucose trong mu (ng huyt) tr v ch s an ton.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><b>thc phm chc nngBoniDiabet</b></h3>\r\n<h4><b>Cn bng glucose, khnglo bin chng</b></h4>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/boniet.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-477 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/boniet-300x173.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"865\" height=\"499\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\"Tr th\" BoniDiabet h tr iu tr tiu ng hiu qu</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm ngoi nhp c sn xut ti Canada.</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr iu trbnh tiu nghiu qu.</li>\r\n 	<li>B sung vi dng cht, phng nga bin chng tiu ng.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca BoniDiab