(478, 1, '2021-01-19 10:50:38', '2021-01-19 03:50:38', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><b>Kht nc, mc tiu nhiu, st cn</b></h2>\r\nB quyt no  bn thot khibnh tiu ng?\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/77.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-486 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/77-300x185.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"756\" height=\"466\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Bnh tiu ng, mi lo sc khe ca ngi gi</div>\r\nTheo thng k ca B y t, Vit Nam c khong 3,5 triu ngi mc bnh tiu ng. y l cn bnh mang n nhiu phin toi v h ly cho sc khe ngi bnh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bn kht nc nhiu: dng nh bn kht nc lin tc, va ung xong  kht, lc no cng phi k k theo chai nc bn mnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tiu nhiu: v kht nc nn bn ung nc nhiu, dn n hin tng tiu nhiu. ang lm vic cng mc tiu, ang n cng mc tiu, ang ng cng mc tiu khin mi cng vic ca bn d b gin on,...</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt mi, kit sc v st cn: l nhng biu hin thy r khi bn mc bnh tiu ng. Bn lun c cm gic u oi trong ngi, cm thy kh chu v khng lc no khe mnh  tn hng cuc sng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNguyn nhn gy ra bnh tiu ng l do ri lon chuyn ha insulin trong c th, dn n lng ng trong mu cao.\r\n<blockquote> gim cc triu chng ca bnh tiu ng, bn cn b sung cho c th nhng hot cht c tc dng iu tit chuyn ha insulin trong c th, gi lng ng  mc n nh v cn bng.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Vin Tha Canh - Gio C Lam</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>n nh ng huyt, chia xa tiu ng</strong></h4>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/78.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-485 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/78-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"907\" height=\"907\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Vin Tha Canh - Gio C Lam gip h ng huyt cho bnh nhn tiu ng</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Chit xut t cc thnh phn thin nhin qu him nh dy tha canh, gio c lam.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gip n nh ng huyt  mc cn bng.</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr gim cholesterol v lipid trong mu  ngi mc bnh tiu ng hiu qu.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca vin tha canh gio c lam</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nVin tha canh - Gio c lam c chit xut t cc thnh phn tho dc thin nhin qu him.\r\n<h4><strong>Dy tha canh</strong></h4>\r\ngip hm v ngt v gip iu chnh lng ng trong mu bng cch ngn s hp th ng  rut v kch thch tuyn ty tit ra insulin. Ngoi ra, dy tha canh cn c s dng  gim cn v lm gim lng cholesterol.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/79.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-484\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/79-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"830\" height=\"553\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption>Dy tha canh gip iu chnh lng ng trong mu</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4><strong>Gio C Lam</strong></h4>\r\nc thnh phn chnh l Saponin rt ging nhn sm. Gio c lam c nhng cng dng chnh nh gip bnh n p huyt, chng kt t tiu cu, lm tan huyt khi, phng nga x va mch, cc tai bin v tim, mch, no.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra cn c cc thnh phn nh: Lactose, tinh bt, magne stearat.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca vin tha canh gio c lam</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nS kt hp ca dy tha canh, gio c lam v cc thnh phn khc gip cho sn phm ny mang li nhiu cng dng tuyt vi cho ngi mc bnh tiu ng:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gip n nh ng huyt</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr gim cholesterol v lipid trong mu  ngi mc bnh tiu ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_483\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"770\"]<a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/80.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-483\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/80-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"770\" height=\"513\" /></a> Senior woman eats lunch at retirement home[/caption]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">ng huyt n nh, cuc sng vui ti</div>\r\n<blockquote><b></b>C Vin tha canh - gio c lam, n