(487, 1, '2021-01-19 10:52:12', '2021-01-19 03:52:12', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nc k tha v pht huy nn y hc c truyn Vit Nam, Vin Tha Canh Gio C Lam i c Mnh gip phng nga v h tr iu tr bnh tiu ng, gim cholesterol v lipid trong mu cao.\r\n\r\nSn phm c chit xut t dy tha canh v cy gio c lam kt hp thnh cng, sn xut theo tiu chun ISO 22000 v GMP - WHO (t chc Y t th gii), c vinh danh 2 gii thng nm 2013, top 10 thng hiu nhn hiu Vit Nam (do Vin s hu tr tu v sng to chng nhn).\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/vien-thia-canh-giao-co-lam-60v.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-492 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/vien-thia-canh-giao-co-lam-60v-300x257.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"723\" height=\"619\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Vin Tha Canh Gio C Lam i c Mnh 60 vin</em></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nTrong mt vin:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cao mm Dy tha canh: 400mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Cao mm Gio c lam: 100mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Ph liu: ng Lactose, tinh bt, magnesi stearat.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nVin Tha Canh Gio C Lam gip h ng huyt  ngi mc bnh tiu ng.\r\n\r\nGip duy tr ng huyt  mc n nh.\r\n\r\nGim cholesterol v lipid trong mu  ngi mc bnh tiu ng.\r\n\r\nPhng nga bin chng bnh tiu ng.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"active\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nUng 1 - 2 vin/ln, ngy 2 - 3 ln.\r\n\r\nUng trc hoc sau ba n 30 pht.\r\n\r\nt dng ti thiu t 1 - 3 thng\r\n\r\n<strong>i tng s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nVin Tha Canh Gio C Lam dng trong cc trng hp:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi mc bnh tiu ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi c hm lng cholesterol v lipid trong mu cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi cao huyt p.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng 