(499, 1, '2021-01-19 10:57:23', '2021-01-19 03:57:23', '<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h2><strong>M</strong><strong>cbnh tiu ngl mang theo ngn ni lo</strong></h2>\r\nBnh tiu ng c th gy ra cho bn nhng bin chng ht sc nguy him\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1002.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-507 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1002-300x201.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"928\" height=\"622\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">ng huyt tng cao</div>\r\nKhi mc bnh tiu ng, ngoi vic lo lng v cc phng php tr bnh, lch ung thuc cho ng gi gic, king c hp l Th bn cn mang thm gnh nng v nhng bin chng khn lng ca bnh nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>t qu: ng tng qu cao trong c th dn n tnh trng t qu v cng nguy him. Nu khng c cu cha kp thi, nguy c mt mng l rt cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tn thng thn kinh thc vt: Bn s thy nhp tim ca mnh b ri lon, da kh, tiu chy hoc to bn khng kim sot c.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tn thng thn kinh ngoi: Dn n mt vng trn c th bn nh bn chn, bn tay c du hiu l lot v hoi t. Vic ct b b phn  l iu khng th trnh khi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNguyn nhn chnh gy ra bnh tiu ng l do lng ng huyt trong c th tng cao v khng kim sot c.\r\n<blockquote>V th vic n nh ng huyt chnh l cha kha quan trng gip bn y li bnh tiu ng v hn ch ti a nhng bin chng ca bnh.</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Vin Ung T Care</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>n nh ng huyt, ngn nga bin chng bnh tiu ng</strong></h4>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1003.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-506 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1003-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"838\" height=\"838\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Vin Ung T Care -<strong></strong>h tr iu tr bnh tiu ng</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm 100% ngun gc tho dc c tc dng h tr iu tr bnh tiu ng</li>\r\n 	<li>Gip ngn nga cc bin chng nguy him do bnh tiu ng gy ra</li>\r\n 	<li>Dnh cho ngi b tiu ng, m trong mu cao</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca T Care</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nSn phm c kt hp t 7 tho dc qu, gip h ng huyt, h tr lm gim cholesterol trong mu nh:\r\n<h4><strong>Kh qua 3g</strong></h4>\r\nGip iu tr cc trng hp iu tr tiu ng; ci thin ng huyt v ci thin dung np glucose; gim cholesterol, hn ch tin trnh bnh vng mc (do bin chng t bnh tiu ng). Kh qua cn c tc dng khng khun, chng u bu v c th c ch tng hp protein.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1004.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-505\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1004-300x225.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"853\" height=\"640\" /></a><figcaption>Kh qua gip iu tr cc trng hp iu tr tiu ng</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4><strong>Dy tha canh 1g</strong></h4>\r\nDy tha canh c cha cht lm gim s hp thu ng t rut. Dy tha canh cng c th lm tng lng insulin trong c th v tng s pht trin ca cc t bo trong ty, l ni insulin trong c th c to ra.\r\n<h4><strong>Thng trut 1g</strong></h4>\r\nTc dng h ng huyt, kch thch tiu ha\r\n<h4><strong>Hoi sn 0.2g</strong></h4>\r\nHoi sn v ngt hi ng, tnh bnh; vo kinh t, ph, thn v v. C tc dng ch kh dng m, kin t, b ph thn, sinh tn.\r\n<h4><strong>To Spirulina 0.3g</strong></h4>\r\nGip duy tr n nh ng huyt, ngn nga cc bin chng v mt v vim lot chn tay, cung cp y  dinh dng thit yu cho ngi tiu ng.\r\n<h4><strong>Linh chi 0.3g</strong></h4>\r\nTc dng nng cao tng cng sc khe, gip thn th cng trng, khe mnh.\r\n<h4><strong>Sinh a 0.3g</strong></h4>\r\nDng tt cho cc bnh mang tnh nhit nh st cao, i khi pht cung, m sng... hoc cc chng bnh tiu kht, ban chn, to tr, xut huyt...\r\n\r\nPh liu va : 1 vin.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca T Care</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nVin ung tiu ng T Care l sn phm 100% ngun gc tho dc s mang n nhng tc dng cho ngi bnh tiu ng nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gip h ng huyt v cholesterol, lipid trong mu. H tr iu tr bnh tiu ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gip ngn nga bin chng v tim mch, thn kinh ngoi bin do bnh tiu ng gy ra.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1005.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-504 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/1005-300x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"828\" height=\"414\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">ng huyt n nh, cuc sng vui ti</div>\r\n<blockquote>Bnh tiu ng ca bn  c ngn nga v kim sot hiu qu. Khng cn gnh nng v tm l v sc khe, cuc sng ca bn cng ngy cng vui ti, hnh phc hn.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4><strong>Cch dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngy ung 2 ln, mi ln 2  3 vin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung trc ba n 30 pht hoc sau n 1 gi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng trong thi gian t nht 3 thng, nn dng thng xuyn  c kt qu tt nht.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>i tng s dng</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dng cho ngi b bnh tiu ng, ngi cholesterol v lipid trong mu cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng cho ngi c nguy c cao mc bnh tiu ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu </h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khi ung sn phm nn kim tra ng huyt thng xuyn, nn thc hin ch  n gim cht ngt, hn ch tinh bt v tng cng th dc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm ny khng phi l thuc v khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Bo qun</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nBo qun ni kh ro, thong mt, trnh nh sng, nhit  di 30  C.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 60 vin</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">CT CP DC PHM GIA NGUYN</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>', 'Vin Ung n nh ng Huyt T Care 60 Vin', '<div class=\"prd-dt-xx\">\r\n<table class=\"table-detail\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Thng hiu:</td>\r\n<td>Vit c</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Xut x thng hiu:</td>\r\n<td>Vit Nam</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Quy cch:</td>\r\n<td>Hp 60 vin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>M sn phm:</td>\r\n<td>00007209</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"prd-dt-desc\">\r\n\r\nT Care gip h ng huyt v cholesterol, lipid trong mu. Ngn nga bin chng v tim mch, thn kinh ngoi bin do bnh tiu ng gy ra.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'vien-uong-on-dinh-duong-huyet-td-care-60-vien', '', '', '2021-03-14 03:49:17', '2021-03-13 20:49:17', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=product&#038;p=499', 0, 'product', '', 0),
