nh Amidon, aerosol, PER 6000, tween 80, talc, magnesi, stearate, kali sorbat.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Diabetna</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nDiabetna chit xut hon ton t thin nhin trn dy chuyn hin i  c chun ha, gip h tr iu tr tiu ng, ngi bnh an tm khi s dng.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>H tr sinh tn, ch kht, lm h ng huyt: h tr phng nga cc triu chng h ng huyt nh i tiu nhiu, mt m, ming kh, ming hi...</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr ngi bnh tiu ng, n nh ng huyt v ngn nga cc bin chng ca bnh tiu ng nh au nhc, nga, t b  chn, lot bn chn, lit dng  nam gii, suy thn, nhi mu c tim, nhi mu no, mt nhn m, m mt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/diabetna-2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-513 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i-pharmacy.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/diabetna-2-300x171.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"811\" height=\"462\" /></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Diabetna mang n 4 cng dng gip y nhanh bin chng tiu ng</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>Diabetna gip bn tm bit tnh trng i tiu nhiu ln, ming hi, mt kh, xua tan ni lo bin chng tiu ng, gip bn an tm hng th cuc sng.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"active\">Liu dng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4>Cch dng</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ung ngy 2 ln, mi ln 2 vin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung vo bui sng v bui ti trc ba n 30 pht.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>i tng s dng</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dng cho ngi b tiu ng typ I v typ II.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi c ng huyt cao, tin i tho ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi cn n nh ng huyt v ngn nga cc bin chng bnh tiu ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Tc dng ph</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu </h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Kt qu khc nhau ty c a mi ngi</li>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm ny khng phi l thuc v khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n