(635, 1, '2021-01-25 16:39:24', '2021-01-25 09:39:24', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Bonlutin L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nGim au: nhc c, au lng, vim dy thn kinh ta v vim x, au khp mn tnh, vim khp xng mn tnh, thp khp, vim khp dng thp.\r\nGim vim au khp, tng kh nng vn ng khp b vim hay gt.\r\nDuy tr &amp; ci thin tnh trng sc khe chung\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Bonlutin</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">EICOSAPENTAENOIC ACID (EPA)</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Bonlutin</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nGim au: nhc c, au lng, vim dy thn kinh ta v vim x, au khp mn tnh, vim khp xng mn tnh, thp khp, vim khp dng thp.\r\nGim vim au khp, tng kh nng vn ng khp b vim hay gt.\r\nDuy tr &amp; ci thin tnh trng sc khe chung\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Bonlutin</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n1-3 vin/ngy.\r\nTc dng ca thuc c th bt u sau 1 tun, nu au nhiu c th dng thuc gim au chng vim trong nhng ngy u.\r\nThuc khng gy ri lon d dy-rut nn c th iu tr lu di.\r\niu tr nhc li sau 6 thng hoc ngn hn ty tnh trng bnh nhn, t iu tr 1-6 thng ty vo tin trin bnh.\r\nCch dng:\r\n\r\nUng trong hoc sau ba n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Bonlutin</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc ny ch dng theo n ca bc s.\r\nc k hng dn s dng trc khi dng.\r\nNu cn thm thng tin, xin hi  kin bc s.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 4 v x 15 vin</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">CATALENT</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">AUSTRALIA</div>', 'Bonlutin', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bonlutin', '', '', '2021-01-25 16:39:24', '2021-01-25 09:39:24', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=6