(636, 1, '2021-01-25 16:45:50', '2021-01-25 09:45:50', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Amiyu Granules 2.5g L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc cm ung Amiyu Granules 2.5G cung cp cc acid amin trong suy thn mn tnh\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Amiyu Granules 2.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: L-Histidine hydrochloride hydrat</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Tuyn tin lit</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Hp 210 gi x 2,5g thuc cm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Amiyu Granules 2.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCung cp cc acid amin trong suy thn mn tnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Amiyu Granules 2.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc dng ng ung. Nn dng cng vi thc n hoc ung sau ba n.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n\r\nNgi ln: 1 gi x 3 ln/ngy. Chnh liu theo tui,  nng cc triu chng &amp; th trng.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Amiyu Granules 2.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Amiyu Granules 2.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nNn s dng duy tr cho bnh nhn suy thn mn tnh. Ngi cao tui: gim liu. Ph n c thai. Ngng cho con b nu cn thit dng.  an ton i vi tr em cha c xc nh. Vo thi im s dng: cung cp cho bnh nhn ch  n t protein theo chc nng thn &amp; lng calo hp th nn l  1800kCal.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 30 gi</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">NHN KHC</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">JAPAN</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Amiyu Granules 2.5G', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'amiyu-granules-2-5g', '', '', '2021-01-25 16:45:50', '2021-01-25 09:45:50', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=636', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(637, 1, '2021-01-25 16:47:44', '2021-01-25 09:47:44', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Apitim 5Mg L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nAPITIM 5mg c thnh phn chnh lAmlodipine dng iu tr tng huyt p ( ngi bnh c nhng bin chng chuyn ha nh i tho ng) v iu tr d phng  ngi bnh au tht ngc n nh, thiu mau c tim.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Apitim 5Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Amlodipine</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Tim mch huyt p</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Hp 3 v x 10 vin nang</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Apitim 5Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\niu tr tng huyt p ( ngi bnh c nhng bin chng chuyn ha nh i tho ng) v iu tr d phng  ngi bnh au tht ngc n nh, thiu mau c tim.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Apitim 5Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li> iu tr tng huyt p v au tht ngc, liu phi ph hp cho tng ngi bnh. Ni chung, khi u vi liu bnh thng l 5mg, 1 ln cho 24 gi. Liu c th tng n 10mg cho 1 ln trong 1 ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nu tc dng khng hiu qu sau 4 tun iu tr c th tng liu. Khng cn iu chnh liu khi phi hp cc thuc li tiu thiazid.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNgi ln: 5 mg x 1 ln/ngy, c th tng liu 10 mg/ngy nu khng p ng iu tr sau 2 tun.\r\nNgi gi &amp; bnh nhn x gan: cn chnh liu.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nCc triu chng ca qu liu c th bao gm: hoa mt, ngt xu, nhp tim nhanh. Nu nn nhn hn m hoc khng th c, cn gi cp cu ngay lp tc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nB sung liu ngay khi nh ra. Tuy nhin, nu thi gian gin cch vi liu tip theo qu ngn th b qua liu  qun v tip tc lch dng thuc. Khng dng liu gp i  b cho liu  b b l.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Apitim 5Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tc dng an thn t mc  bun ng cho n ng su c th xy ra nhng s gim bt sau vi ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon nh ng tiu ha v thn kinh trung ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThng bo cho bc s nhng tc dng khng mong mun gp phi khi s dng thuc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Apitim 5Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>Thn trng khi dng cho ngi suy gim chc nng gan, hp ng mch ch, suy tim sau nhi mu c tim cp.</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ph n c thai: Cc thuc chn knh canxi c th c ch cn co t cung sm. Tuy nhin, thuc khng c tc dng bt li cho qu trnh sinh . Phi tnh n nguy c thiu oxy cho thai nhi nu gy h huyt p  ngi m, v c nguy c lm gim ti mu nhau thai. y l nguy c chung khi dng cc thuc iu tr tng huyt p, chng c th lm thay i lu lng mu do gin mch ngoi bin.  ng vt thc nghim, thuc chn knh canxi c th gy qui thai  dng d tt xng. V vy, trnh dng amlodipin cho ngi mang thai, c bit trong 3 thng u thai k</li>\r\n 	<li>B m cho con b: Cha c thng bo no nh gi s tch ly ca amlodipin trong sa m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Cc thuc c th xy ra tng tc:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cc thuc gy m lm tng tc dng chng tng huyt p ca amlodipin v c th lm huyt p gim mnh hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lithi: Khi dng cng vi amlodipin, c th gy c thn kinh, bun nn, nn, a chy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc chng vim khng steroid, c bit l indomethacin c th lm gim tc dng chng tng huyt p ca amlodipin do c ch tng hp prostaglandin v/hoc gi natri v dch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc thuc lin kt cao vi protein (nh dn cht coumarin, hydantoin...) phi dng thn trng vi amlodipin, v amlodipin cng lin kt cao vi protein nn nng  ca cc thuc ni trn  dng t do (khng lin kt), c th thay i trong huyt thanh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Cc loi thc phm,  ung c th tng tc:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nu bc s k ch  n t mui hoc t natri, lm theo cc hng dn cn thn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ru v thuc l cng c th tng tc vi vi loi thuc nht nh. Hy tham kho  kin chuyn gia sc khe ca bn v vic ung thuc cng thc n, ru v thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tnh trng sc khe no nh hng n thuc?</li>\r\n 	<li>Tnh trng sc khe ca bn c th nh hng n vic s dng thuc ny. Bo cho bc s bit nu bn c bt k vn  sc khe no.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 3 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">DHG</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Apitim 5Mg 3X10 Vin', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'apitim-5mg-3x10-vien', '', '', '2021-01-25 16:47:44', '2021-01-25 09:47:44', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=637', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(638, 1, '2021-01-25 16:48:49', '2021-01-25 09:48:49', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc ALCHYSIN 2X10 BVPHARMA L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nChng ph n khng vim dng men v iu tr cc trng hp ph n sau chn thng hay sau phu thut.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca ALCHYSIN 2X10 BVPHARMA</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Chymotrypsin</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Khng vim</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nn dng bao phim</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca ALCHYSIN 2X10 BVPHARMA</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chng ph n khng vim dng men.</li>\r\n 	<li>iu tr cc trng hp ph n sau chn thng hay sau phu thut.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca ALCHYSIN 2X10 BVPHARMA</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc dng ng ung hoc ngm di li.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>ng ung: 2 vin/ln, 3 hoc 4 ln trong ngy (ung).</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngm di li : 4 n 6 vin chia u ra trong ngy ( thuc tan t t di li)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g nu qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"active\">Tc dng ph ca ALCHYSIN 2X10 BVPHARMA</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nTrong mt vi trng hp, c th c cc biu hin d ng vi thuc, khi  nn trnh hay ngng s dng.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu  ca ALCHYSIN 2X10 BVPHARMA</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nV kh nng gy mt dch kch, nn khng khuyn co dng chymotrypsin trong phu thut c thu tinh th  ly b nhn mt  ngi bnh di 20 tui.\r\n\r\nKhng dng chymotrypsin cho ngi bnh tng p sut dch knh v c vt thng h hoc ngi bnh c nhn mt bm sinh.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 2 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">CNG TY C PHN BV PHARMA</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Alchysin 2X10 Bvpharma', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'alchysin-2x10-bvpharma', '', '', '2021-01-25 16:48:49', '2021-01-25 09:48:49', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=638', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
