(641, 1, '2021-01-25 16:53:36', '2021-01-25 09:53:36', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Atorlip 10mg L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nAtorlip c s dng trong cc trng hp: tng cholesterol ton phn, tng LDL-cholesterol, tng triglycerid. Lm chm s tin trin ca x va mch vnh. D phng tin pht bin c mch vnh  ngi tng cholesterol mu: lm gim nguy c nhi mu c tim, gim nguy c phi lm cc th thut ti to mch vnh, gim nguy c t vong dobnh timm\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Atorlip 10mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Atorvastatin</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Gim cholesterol</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nn 10mg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Atorlip 10mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Atorlip c s dng trong cc trng hp: tng cholesterol ton phn, tng LDL-cholesterol, tng triglycerid.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lm chm s tin trin ca x va mch vnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>D phng tin pht bin c mch vnh  ngi tng cholesterol mu: lm gim nguy c nhi mu c tim, gim nguy c phi lm cc th thut ti to mch vnh, gim nguy c t vong do bnh tim mch.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Atorlip 10mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc dng ng ung. Thuc c th ung vo bt k thi im no trong ngy v khng ty thuc vo ba n.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n\r\nBnh nhn cn c ch  n king hp l trc khi iu tr bng Atorlip v nn duy tr ch  n ny trong sut qu trnh iu tr.\r\n\r\nLiu khi u: ung 10 - 20mg x 1 ln/ngy.\r\n\r\nNhng bnh nhn cn lm gim LDL- cholesterol nhiu (trn 45%) c th khi u bng liu 40mg x 1 ln/ngy.\r\n\r\nLiu iu tr: ung 10 - 80mg x 1 ln/ngy, liu dng c iu chnh theo kt qu xt nghim cc ch s lipid mu.\r\n\r\nHoc theo ch dn ca thy thuc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu nn nhn hn m hoc khng th c, cn gi cp cu ngay lp tc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nB sung liu ngay khi nh ra. Tuy 