iu tr h tr v iu tr triu chng, khng c thuc gii c c hiu. Cc d liu hn ch cho thy bisoprolol kh thm phn c.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhp tim chm: tim tnh mch atropine.</li>\r\n 	<li>H huyt p: dng isoproterenol hoc mt thuc ch vn alpha- adrenergic. Trong trng hp khng p ng c th dng norepinephrine 4 mg/L tim truyn tnh mch chm hay dopamine vi liu ban u 5 mcg/kg/pht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Blc tim ( 2 hoc 3): theo di cn thn, tim truyn isoproterenol hoc my to nhp tim.</li>\r\n 	<li>Suy tim sung huyt: dng digitalis, thuc li tiu, thuc lm tng lc co c, thuc gin mch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Co tht ph qun: dng mt thuc gin ph qun nh isoproterenol v/ hoc aminophylin.</li>\r\n 	<li>H glucose huyt: tim tnh mch glucose.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chng kim ho mu: dng amoni chloride tr khi ngi mc bnh gan.</li>\r\n 	<li>B li nhanh chng lng nc v in gii  mt.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu qun khng dng thuc ng gi, khng nn dng liu b vo lc mun trong ngy, nn tip tc dng liu bnh thng vo ngy hm sau trong liu trnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"active\">Tc dng ph ca Bisoloc Plus 2.5/6.25</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nLnh chi, bun nn, nn, tiu chy, to bn, mt mi, chng mt, au u, gim kali huyt, tng acid uric huyt, tng glucose mu, tng lipid mu (liu cao)\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Bisoloc Plus 2.5/6.25</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Chng ch nh</strong>\r\n\r\nSuy tim khng kim sot c bng thuc; nhp tim &lt; 50 nhp/pht; huyt p thp; hen ph qun nng, COPD mn tnh nng; tc nghn ng mch ngoi vi giai on mun, hi chng Raynaud; u tuyn thng thn cha iu tr; cn au tht ngc Prinzmetal; suy gan/thn nng; mn cm vi thnh phn thuc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>BISOLOC Plus nn c dng cn trng vi cc bnh nhn: b bnh tim, b bnh ng mch (c bit l hi chng Raynaud), c tin s bnh hen ph qun, b bnh i tho ng, ri lon tuyn gip, bnh thng phong, bnh vy nn, suy gim chc nng gan v thn, ang iu tr cc chng d ng, bnh nhn c gy m hay tin hnh i phu, bnh nhn ct b thn kinh giao cm.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tt c bnh nhn nn c theo di cc du hiu ca ri lon nc in gii v cn thc hin theo nh k xt nghim in gii .</li>\r\n 	<li>Li xe v vn hnh my mc: BISOLOC Plus c th nh hng n kh nng li xe v vn hnh my mc v gy nguy c h huyt p v chng mt.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc chn beta khc. Thuc chn calci. Clonidine. Thuc chng lon nhp tim nhm I-III. Thuc kch thch giao cm/ph giao cm. Thuc iu tr i tho ng. Thuc gy m. Digitalis glycoside. Thuc chng trm cm 3 vng, barbiturate, phenothiazine, thuc iu tr cao huyt p khc. Mefloquine. Rifampicin. Corticosreroid, ACTH. Amin tng huyt p. Thuc gin c. Lithium. NSAID. Quinidine. Thuc chng ng, thuc cha gout. Thuc gy m, glycoside, vit D. Cholestyramin, colestipol.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 3 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">UNITED</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Bisoloc Plus 2.5/6.25', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bisoloc-plus-2-5-6-25', '', '', '2021-01-25 16:57:33', '2021-01-25 09:57:33', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=644', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(645, 1, '2021-01-25 16:58:43', '2021-01-25 09:58:43', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Biafine 46.5g L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nBiafine iu tr phng  1 &amp; 2, tt c vt thng, vt lot ngoi da khng nhim trng,  da th pht do x tr.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\">Thnh phn ca Biafine 46.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Trolamine</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc iu tr bnh da liu</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc v hm lng: Hp 1 tup 46;5g; Nh tng bi da</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Biafine 46.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nBiafine iu tr phng  1 &amp; 2, tt c vt thng, vt lot ngoi da khng nhim trng,  da th pht do x tr.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Biafine 46.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc c dng bi ngoi da\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n\r\nPhng  1: Bi &amp; xoa nh 1 lp dy n khi khng cn c hp thu na. Lp li 2-4 ln/ngy.\r\nPhng  2 &amp; vt thng ngoi da khc: Sau khi ra vt thng, bi 1 lp dy ph b mt tn thng &amp; bi lp li  duy tr 1 lp tha trn tn thng. Nu cn ph 1 ming gc m &amp; bng li. Khng dng bng hp thu kh.\r\n da do t laser hay x tr: bi &amp; xoa nh, 2-3 ln/ngy, khong cch gia cc ln bi u nhau.\r\n\r\nLiu dng thuc Biafine cho tr em liu tng t nh ngi ln.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp hoc qu liu, gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun liu?</strong>\r\nNu bn qun dng mt liu thuc, bn hy b sung cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, bn hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Khng dng gp i liu  quy nh\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Biafine 46.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nau (kim chm) va phi &amp; thong qua (15-30 pht). Him: d ng do tip xc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Biafine 46.5g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc ny khng dng  chng nng. Ph n c thai &amp; cho con b.\r\n\r\nD ng vi thnh phn thuc. Vt thng c chy mu. Vt thng c nhim trng.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc ny c th tng tc vi cc thuc khc, hi bc s ca bn  bit thm thng tin.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Tup 46,5 gram</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">JANSSEN</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">THAILAND</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Biafine 46.5G', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'biafine-46-5g', '', '', '2021-01-25 22:59:43', '2021-01-25 15:59:43', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=645', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0);
