(646, 1, '2021-01-25 16:59:56', '2021-01-25 09:59:56', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc BACTAMOX 375 12 GI L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc Bactamox 375 12 Gi c thnh phn Amoxicillin, Sulbactam c tc dng iu tr nhim khun do cc vi khun nhy cm gy ra, bao gm: nhim khun tai mi hng: vim amidan, vim xoang, vim tai gia; nhim khun ng h hp di: vim ph qun cp v mn, vim phi  ph qun; nhim khun ng tit niu  sinh dc: vim bng quang, vim niu o, vim b thn, nhim khun ng sinh dc n; nhim khun da v m mm\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca BACTAMOX 375 12 GI</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Amoxicillin, Sulbactam</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc chng nhim khun</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Hp 12 gi x 1,2 gam.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca BACTAMOX 375 12 GI</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\niu tr nhim khun do cc vi khun nhy cm gy ra, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun tai mi hng: vim amidan, vim xoang, vim tai gia.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng h hp di: vim ph qun cp v mn, vim phi  ph qun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng tit niu  sinh dc: vim bng quang, vim niu o, vim b thn, nhim khun ng sinh dc n.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun da v m mm: mn nht, p xe, nhim khun vt thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun xng v khp.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun nha khoa: p xe  rng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun khc: nhim khun do no thai, nhim khun mu trong giai on hu sn, nhim khun trong  bng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca BACTAMOX 375 12 GI</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nUng thuc trc hay sau ba n u c. Phn tn thuc trong mt t nc, sa, hay nc hoa qu v ung ngay sau khi pha.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ln, tr em trn 40kg: 1 gi x 3 ln/ngy .\r\nTr em di 40kg:</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun nh v va: 20mg/kg cn nng/ngy, chia thnh 3 ln/ngy .</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun nng: 40mg/kg cn nng/ngy, chia thnh 3 ln/ngy, ung trong 5 ngy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc t gy ra tai bin, v c dung np tt ngay c  liu cao. Nhng phn ng cp xy ra ph thuc vo tnh trng qu mn ca tng c th. Trong trng hp dng qu liu, ngng dng thuc ngay v s dng cc bin php h tr, c th gy nn, ra d dy nu mi qu liu. Khng c thuc gii c c hiu. Amoxicillin v Sulbactam c th c loi b bng thm phn mu.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g nu qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca BACTAMOX 375 12 GI</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thng gp: tiu chy, nga, ngoi ban.</li>\r\n 	<li>t gp: bun nn, nn, tng bch cu i toan, pht ban, vim gan v vng da  mt, tng transaminase.</li>\r\n 	<li>Him gp: phn ng phn v, ph Quincke, gim nh tiu cu, gim bch cu, thiu mu tan huyt, vim i trng gi mc, hi chng Stevens -Johnson, ban  a dng, vim da bong, hoi t biu b do ng c, vim thn k.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thng bo cho bc s nhng tc dng khng mong mun gp phi khi s dng thuc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Lu  ca BACTAMOX 375 12 GI</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cc du hiu v triu chng vng da  mt tuy t xy ra khi dng thuc nhng c th nng. Tuy nhin nhng triu chng  thng hi phc v s ht sau 6 tun ngng iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc phn ng qu mn trm trng v i khi dn n t vong (dng phn v)  c bo co xy ra trn bnh nhn dng cc khng sinh penicillin.\r\n c xut hin ban  (a dng) i km vi st ni hch (tng bch cu n nhn nhim khun)  nhng bnh nhn dng Amoxicillin. Nn trnh s dng thuc nu nghi ng c tng bch cu n nhn nhim khun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc ko di i khi lm pht trin cc vi khun khng thuc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ph n mang thai: nghin cu thc nghim trn qu trnh sinh sn ca ng vt (chut)  chng minh khi dng ch phm theo ng ung khng gy d dng. Tuy nhin, v cn t kinh nghim v dng ch phm cho ngi mang thai, nn cn trnh s dng thuc  ngi mang thai nht l trong 3 thng u ca thai k, tr trng hp cn thit do thy thuc ch nh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ph n cho con b: amoxicillin v sulbactam c bi tit vo sa m, phi thn trng khi dng thuc cho ngi m ang cho con b.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tc ng ca thuc ln kh nng li xe v vn hnh my mc: Thuc khng gy nh hng n kh nng li xe hoc vn hnh my mc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thuc c th gy ko di thi gian chy mu v ng mu.\r\nThuc c th lm gim hiu qu ca cc thuc trnh thai ung, do  nn cnh bo cho bnh nhn bit iu ny.</li>\r\n 	<li>Probenecid lm gim s o thi ca thuc qua ng thn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nifedipin lm tng s hp thu Amoxicillin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Amoxicillin lm gim s bi tit Methotrexat, lm tng c tnh trn ng tiu ha v h to mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng ng thi vi Allopurinol: lm tng nguy c cc phn ng d ng da.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chloramphenicol, macrolid, sulfonamid v tetracyclin c th cn tr tc dng dit khun ca amoxicillin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 12 gi</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">CNG TY C PHN DC PHM IMEXPHARM</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Bactamox 375 12 Gi', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bactamox-375-12-goi', '', '', '2021-01-25 16:59:56', '2021-01-25 09:59:56', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=646', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(647, 1, '2021-01-25 17:01:00', '2021-01-25 10:01:00', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Bavegan LADOPHAR 60V (L) L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc Bavegan Ladophar 60V (L) c thnh phn l cao Actiso, cao bin sc, bm bm, t dc c tc dng iu tr cc chng bnh v gan nh mn nht, nga, n m ay, vim gan cp v mn tnh, vng da, gip thng tiu, nhun trng (chng to bn), gip n ngon.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Bavegan LADOPHAR 60V (L)</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: cao Actiso, cao bin sc, bm bm, t dc</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc c ngun gc Tho dc, ng vt</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nn bao ng-l 60 vin</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Bavegan LADOPHAR 60V (L)</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\niu tr cc chng bnh v gan nh mn nht, nga, ni m ay, vim gan cp v mn tnh, vng da, gip thng tiu, nhun trng (chng to bn), gip n ngon.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Bavegan LADOPHAR 60V (L)</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc dng ng ung.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n\r\nNgi ln : Ung 2 -4 vin/ln x 3 ln/ngy.\r\nTr em: Ung 1  2 vin/ln x 3 ln/ngy, tu theo tui.\r\nHoc theo s ch dn ca thy thuc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp hy gi cho trung tm cp cu 115 hoc trm y t gn nht\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g nu qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Bavegan LADOPHAR 60V (L)</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Bavegan LADOPHAR 60V (L)</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nCha c bo co.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 60 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">LADOPHAR</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Bavegan Ladophar 60V (L)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bavegan-ladophar-60v-lo', '', '', '2021-01-29 23:19:51', '2021-01-29 16:19:51', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=647', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
