(648, 1, '2021-01-25 17:02:31', '2021-01-25 10:02:31', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc BESTRIP 50MG 3X10 L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nChng say tu xe. Phng v iu tr cc chng bun nn do nhiu nguyn nhn khc nhau (tr do ho tr liu ung th).\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca BESTRIP 50MG 3X10</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Dimenhydrinate</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc hng tm thn</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Hp 3 v x10 vin, hp 10 v x 10 vin bao phim</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca BESTRIP 50MG 3X10</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chng say tu xe.</li>\r\n 	<li>Phng v iu tr cc chng bun nn do nhiu nguyn nhn khc nhau (tr do ho tr liu ung th).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca BESTRIP 50MG 3X10</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nDng ng ung, ung na gi trc khi i xe\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Say tu xe:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n+ Ngi ln: 50 - 100 mg ung na gi trc khi i, sau  50 mg/4 gi.\r\n\r\n+ Tr 8 - 15 tui: 25 - 50 mg.\r\n\r\n+ Tr 2 - 7 tui: 12,5 - 25 mg.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nn v bun nn:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n+ Ngi ln: 50 - 100 mg.\r\n\r\n+ Tr em: gim liu theo tui nh trn.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca BESTRIP 50MG 3X10</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nTng tnh nhy nht cht tit ph qun, ri lon iu tit, kh ming, to bn, b tiu, l ln.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca BESTRIP 50MG 3X10</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nKhng nn dng cho ph n c thai v cho con b, ngi li xe v vn hnh my mc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nTrnh dng thc ung c cn, thuc khng sinh c kh nng gy c tnh  tai, thuc c ch TKTW, thuc khng cholinergic.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 3 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">PHARMEDIC</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Bestrip 50Mg 3X10', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bestrip-50mg-3x10', '', '', '2021-01-29 23:17:21', '2021-01-29 16:17:21', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=648', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(649, 1, '2021-01-25 17:03:48', '2021-01-25 10:03:48', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Cao Sao Vng 4g L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCao sao vng 4g h tr iu tr cm cm, nhc u, s mi, bun nn, au bng, say tu xe; b mui v cc cn trng khc t.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Cao Sao Vng 4g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Camphor 849,20 mg;Menthol 425,20 mg;Tinh du Bc h 525,20 mg;Tinh du Trm 210,80 mg;Tinh du Hng nhu 130,80 mg;Tinh du Qu 53,20 mg ;T dc va  4g(Du parafin, sp ong vng, lanolin, vaselin, parafin rn).</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc bi ngoi</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Cao xoa, Hp x 4g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Cao Sao Vng 4g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCm cm, nhc u, s mi, bun nn, au bng, say tu xe; b mui v cc cn trng khc t.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Cao Sao Vng 4g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nDu bi ngoi da hoc xng\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhc u, chng mt, cm cm, say tu xe: Xoa du cao vo hai bn thi dng v gy, xoa vo l mi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khi b mui v cc cn trng khc t: Xoa du cao vo ch b t.</li>\r\n 	<li>C th xng: Cho khong 1  2 u a du cao vo nc si  xng khi b cm cm.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Cao Sao Vng 4g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cha c bo co</strong>\r\n\r\nThng bo cho Bc s nhng tc dng khng mong mun gp phi khi s dng thuc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Cao Sao Vng 4g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khng dng cho tr em di 2 tui. Khng bi vo mt.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng dng cho ngi mn cm vi bt k thnh phn no ca thuc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 10 gi</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">OPC</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Cao Sao Vng 4G', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cao-sao-vang-4g', '', '', '2021-01-29 23:13:09', '2021-01-29 16:13:09', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=649', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(650, 1, '2021-01-25 17:05:06', '2021-01-25 10:05:06', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Cali Lactylase L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc Cali lactylase c thnh phn chnh lLactobacillus acidophilus c dng  d phng v iu tr cc ri lon tiu ha nh a chy, y bng kh tiu v h tr nng cao sc  khng ca c th.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Cali Lactylase</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Lactobacillus acidophilus</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Tiu ha</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Dng bt 1 g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Cali Lactylase</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCali lactylase c dng  d phng v iu tr cc ri lon tiu ha nh a chy, y bng kh tiu v h tr nng cao sc  khng ca c th. c bit, thuc cn dng  d phng v iu tr cc ri lon tiu ha do dng khng sinh. Bn cnh , cn c tc dng gip tr s sinh c th tiu ha sa d dng.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Cali Lactylase</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nHa tan gi thuc cng vi mt cc nc lc. Lu  rng thuc ch c dng vi nc un si  ngui, tuyt i khng dng nc nng  pha thuc. Mi ngy ung 2 ln theo ch nh ca bc s.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n\r\ni vi ngi ln, mi ngy nn ung t 2 ti 4 gi, mi ngy ung 2 ln.\r\n\r\ni vi tr em, ung t 1 n 2 gi trong ngy, ung 2 ln mt ngy.\r\n\r\nNgi dng c th dng thuc trong khong thi gian t 1 n 2 tun, nu mun ko di hn cn phi xin  kin v thc hin theo ch nh ca bc s.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nHin nay, cha c trng hp c hu qu nghim trng khi s dng thuc qu liu. Tuy nhin, nu ngi dng s dng qu liu v xut hin cc hin tng l th nn lin h vi cc c s y t gn nht  theo di v iu tr.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy nhanh chng s dng li thuc cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu st gi vi liu thuc tip theo, ngi dng c th b qua liu thuc  qun, v s dng thuc theo ng lch trnh ban u. Lu  rng, trong ln s dng tip theo tuyt i khng c s dng gp i lng thuc, hy tun theo liu lng trong ch nh ca bc s.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Cali Lactylase</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co no v vic ngi dng c cc phn ng ph vi thuc. Tuy nhin, nu cm thy trong qu trnh s dng thuc khin c th xut hin nhng biu hin khng bnh thng, nh hng ti sc khe, ngi dng nn tm ngng s dng v c gng lin h vi bc s hoc dc s  a ra chn on v phng php khc phc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Cali Lactylase</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nTrc khi s dng thuc, ngi dng nn thng bo trc vi bc s tnh trng sc khe ca bn thn, cng nh cc loi thuc  v ang s dng trong thi gian gn y  bc s c th a ra ch nh ph hp.\r\n\r\ni vi ph n c bu hoc ang cho con b, thuc cali khng gy nh hng, nhng  m bo an ton, nn hi  kin bc s, dc s trc khi dng.\r\n\r\nThuc ch c s dng theo n ca bc s, ngi dng nn c v kim tra k hng dn s dng trc khi dng. Nu cn bit thm thng tin hoc c thc mc v thuc, vui lng lin h vi bc s hoc dc s  c t vn v b sung nhng thng tin cn thit.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong qu trnh s dng Cali lactylase, ngi dng tuyt i khng s dng song song vi thuc Tetracylin, v nh th s lm hn ch tc dng ca Cali lactylase.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">BIOPHARCO</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Cali Lactylase', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cali-lactylase', '', '', '2021-01-29 23:06:10', '2021-01-29 16:06:10', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=650', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(651, 1, '2021-01-25 17:07:12', '2021-01-25 10:07:12', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Cebraton - Tng cng tr nh L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>B</strong><strong>n ang mc chng nh nh qun qun</strong>\r\n\r\nV mun mau chng chm dt tnh trng trn?\r\n<div>Chng d qun khin cuc sng tr nn ri rm</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bn c i c li 1 trang giy thi nhng khng th nh ni.</li>\r\n 	<li>i ch qun nhng th cn mua.</li>\r\n 	<li> qun cha kha, in thoi, v tin l chuyn nh cm ba.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thm ch, bn qun lun c cng vic cn lm.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThiu mu ln no l mt trong nhng nguyn nhn hng u khin suy gim tr no v gy ra cc biu hin nh au u, chng mt, mt mi, lm trc qun sau...\r\n<blockquote>Do , tng cng lu lng tun hon mu no s gip nhanh chng ci thin cc triu chng hoa mt, au u, chng mt, suy gim tr nh...</blockquote>\r\n<h3><strong>Ce</strong><strong>braton - gii php cho b no thi hin i</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Tng tun hon no - Tng cng tr nh - Gii ta Stress</strong></h4>\r\n<div>Cebraton tng cng tr nh, gip bn tp trung hn</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm dng no cao cp, s dng cng ngh cao trong bo ch v sn xut.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nguyn liu c chun ha theo tiu chun GACP - WHO (thc hnh tt trng trt v thu hi cy thuc theo khuyn co ca T chc Y t Th gii).</li>\r\n 	<li>Sn phm lt top 100 sn phm, dch v c tin v dng nm 2012.</li>\r\n 	<li>Top 10 nhn hiu ni ting nht Vit Nam nm 2016.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Cebraton - Tng cng tr nh</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc Cebraton kt hp hon ho 2 thnh phn dc liu t thin nhin l inh lng v Bch qu.\r\n<h4><strong>Cao inh lng</strong></h4>\r\nCao inh lng tn ting anh l Panax fruticosum L Extract c hot cht chnh l Saponin triterpenic. Cao dc liu c dng bt mn vi cc mu nu, nu sm v nu sng. Trong c inh lng c cha nhiu Saponin c tc dng nh Nhn sm, Vitamin B1, B2, B6 v C. Ngoi ra r cn cha khong 13 loi axit amin quan trng, rt cn thit cho c th con ngi. Cc hot cht ny c tc dng tng cng tr nh cho no b, gii ta stress rt hiu qu. Ngoi ra, Cao inh lng cn c cng dng:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bi b kh huyt, tiu ha km, gii c thc n, chng d ng, chng ho ra mu, ni m ay.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cha lit dng, di tinh, au lng mi gi, chn tay t thp.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gii c gan, vim gan mn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr tc tia sa, ho ra mu, thp khp, au lng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>Cao inh lng tc dng b dng ging nh nhn sm</div>\r\n<h4><strong>Cao Bch qu (Gingko)</strong></h4>\r\nL mt loi thuc qu, c trng  Trung Quc cch y 3000 nm. Trong nhng nm 1700 Bch qu  c bit n  chu u, v khong 60 nm sau  l  Bc M. Bch qu c dng lm thuc cha bnh  phng Ty t nhng nm 1900.\r\n\r\nChit xut t l Bch qu gm Terpenoid, Flavonoid v mt s thnh phn khc nh Catechin, cc hp cht Phenol, cc Polysaccharid, cc Sterol, tinh du, Brom, sp c tc dng lm gin cc mao mch, t  ci thin lu thng tun hon mu, c bit l cc mch mu no v t chi.\r\n\r\nNgy nay, Bch qu c s dng ph bin trong iu tr bnh sa st tr tu, thiu nng tun hon mu no, thoi ha im vng, hi chng tin nh,  tai, trm cm, lo u, cng thng, vim tc mch mu chi, hi chng Raynaud. N cng gip ci thin suy ngh, nhn thc v tr nh  nhng ngi mc bnh Alzheimer.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Cebraton - Tng cng tr nh</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc Cebraton gip b kh huyt, hot huyt dng no hiu qu.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Lm tng chc nng h thn kinh trung ng, tng hot ha v no, tng lu lng tun hon no, tng tr nh v  minh mn; lm gim au u, hoa mt, chng mt, mt mi, ri lon tin nh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lm gim triu chng run, tng lc bp tay, sc ko v kh nng phi hp ng tc chnh xc ca bnh nhn Parkinson.</li>\r\n 	<li>C tc dng b kh huyt, hot huyt, ngn chn s hnh thnh cc mu ng, tng cng lu thng mu ca cc mch ngoi vi, do  gip lm gim au mi vai gy, au cng c, t b chn tay.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>Cebraton gip bn tp trung, ci thin tr nh</div>\r\n<blockquote><strong></strong>Ch vi 2 vin mi ngy, Cebraton mang li tc dng nhanh, mnh trong vic iu tr suy gim tr nh, au u mt ng, hoa mt chng mt.</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Cebraton - Tng cng tr nh</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<h4><strong>Cch dng</strong><strong>thuc Cebraton</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ln: ung 1 vin/ln x 2 ln/ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr em trn 8 tui: ung 1 vin/ngy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>i tng s dngthuc Cebraton</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi hot ng tr c nhiu: doanh nhn, cc nh nghin cu, hc sinh, sinh vin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi trung - cao tui, ph n b thiu mu no: au u, hoa mt, chng mt, mt ng, hay qun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi au mi vai gy, au cng c, t b chn tay.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi b bnh Parkinson.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"active\">Tc dng ph ca Cebraton - Tng cng tr nh</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Cebraton - Tng cng tr nh</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Chng ch nh</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mn cm vi cc thnh phn ca thuc.</li>\r\n 	<li>c k hng dn s dng trc khi dng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 5 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">TRAPHACO</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Cebraton - Tng Cng Tr Nh', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cebraton-tang-cuong-tri-nho', '', '', '2021-01-29 23:01:47', '2021-01-29 16:01:47', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=651', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(710, 1, '2021-01-25 23:17:55', '2021-01-25 16:17:55', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Efferalgan 500mg L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThucefferalgan 500mgc thnh phn chnh l Paracetamol dng iu tr cc chng au v/hoc st nh au u, tnh trng nh cm, au rng, nhc mi c.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Efferalgan 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Paracetamol</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc gim au, h st, Nhm chng vim khng Steroid, Thuc iu tr Gt v cc bnh xng khp</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc v hm lng: Hp 4 v x 4 vin, Vin si, 500mg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Efferalgan 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc Efferalgan 500Mg dng iu tr cc chng au v/hoc st nh au u, tnh trng nh cm, au rng, nhc mi c.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Efferalgan 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\"><b>Cch dng</b>\r\nEfferalgan 500Mg dng ng ung. Ha tan hon ton vin ung trong 1 ly nc ln v ung\r\n<b>Liu dng</b>\r\nNu tr st trn 38,5  C, hy lm nhng bc sau y  tng hiu qu ca thuc Efferalgan 500Mg\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ci b bt qun o ca tr em</li>\r\n 	<li>Cho tr ung thm cht lng</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng  tr  ni qu nng</li>\r\n 	<li>Nu cn , tm cho tr bng nc m, c nhit  thp hn 2  C so vi thn nhit ca tr</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Mi ln dng thuc Efferalgan 500Mg cch nhau 4 gi, dng khng qu 4g/ngy.</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khng c dng paracetamol  t iu tr gim au qu 10 ngy  ngi ln hoc qu 5 ngy  tr em, tr khi do thy thuc hng dn, v au nhiu v ko di nh vy c th l du hiu ca mt tnh trng bnh l cn thy thuc chn on v iu tr c gim st.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng dng Efferalgan 500Mg cho ngi ln v tr em  t iu tr st cao trn 39,5  C, st ko di trn 3 ngy hoc st ti pht, tr khi do thy thuc hng dn, v st nh vy c th l du hiu ca mt bnh nng cn c thy thuc chn on nhanh chng.</li>\r\n 	<li> gim thiu nguy c qu liu, khng nn cho tr em qu 5 liu Efferalgan 500Mg gim au hoc h st trong vng 24 gi, tr khi do thy thuc hng dn.</li>\r\n 	<li> gim au hoc h st cho ngi ln v tr em trn 11 tui, liu Efferalgan 500Mg thng dng hoc a vo trc trng l 325 - 650 mg, c 4 - 6 gi mt ln khi cn thit nhng khng qu 4 g mt ngy, liu mt ln ln hn 1g c th hu ch  gim au  mt s ngi bnh.</li>\r\n 	<li> gim au hoc h st, tr em c th ung hoc a vo trc trng c 4 - 6 gi mt ln khi cn: tr em 1 - 2 tui, 120 mg, tr em 4 - 11 thng tui, 80 mg; v tr em ti 3 thng tui, 40 mg.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Liu trc trng cho tr em di 2 tui dng tu theo mi bnh nhi.</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Liu ung thng dng Efferalgan 500Mg, di dng vin nn gii phng ko di 650 mg,  gim au  ngi ln v tr em 12 tui tr ln l 1,3 g c 8 gi mt ln khi cn thit, khng qu 3,9 g mi ngy. Vin nn paracetamol gii phng ko di, khng c nghin nt, nhai hoc ho tan trong cht lng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</b>\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n<b>Lm g khi qun liu?</b>\r\nNu bn qun s dng mt liu thuc Efferalgan 500Mg, bn hy b sung cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, bn hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu Efferalgan 500Mg k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Khng dng gp i liu Efferalgan 500Mg  quy nh\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Efferalgan 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Vui lng xem thng tin chi tit trn t hng dn s dng trong hp thuc hoc tham kho  kin dc s, bc s.</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Efferalgan 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\"><b>Thn trng khi s dng</b>\r\n trnh tnh trng qu liu Efferalgan 500Mg, cn ch  cc thnh phn ca thuc s dng km theo khng cha Paracetamol.\r\n<b>Tng tc thuc</b>\r\nTrnh ung ru khi dng thuc Efferalgan 500Mg, khng dng chung vi cc thuc khc c cha Paracetamol.</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 4 v x 4 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">BRISTOL</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">FRANCE</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Efferalgan 500Mg', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'efferalgan-500mg', '', '', '2021-01-29 21:52:29', '2021-01-29 14:52:29', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=710', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(652, 1, '2021-01-25 17:08:49', '2021-01-25 10:08:49', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Cephalexin 500Mg L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCephalexin 500Mg iu tr nhim trng do mt s vi khun Gr(-) &amp; Gr(+) k c Staphylococcus sn xut men penicillinase, nhim trng ng tit niu, h hp, da &amp; m mm.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh:Cephalexin 500mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc khng sinh</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nang, 500mg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nNhim trng do mt s vi khun Gr(-) &amp; Gr(+) k c Staphylococcus sn xut men penicillinase, nhim trng ng tit niu, h hp, da &amp; m mm.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nDng ng ung.Ung thuc trc ba n 1 gi.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ln: 0.5 g- 1 g/ ln, ung cch khong 6 gi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr em: 25 - 50mg/ kg/ngy, chia 4 ln. Trng hp nhim khun nng, phi tng gp i liu dng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim hng v vim bng quang cp: liu hng ngy c th chia lm 2 ln.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim tai gia: 75 - 100mg/ngy/kg, chia 4 ln.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun Beta-tan huyt, thi gian iu tr ti thiu  10 ngy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Qu liu v x tr</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Triu chng:bun nn, nn, kh chu thng v, tiu chy v huyt niu</li>\r\n 	<li>iu tr: Nn ch nh than hot thay cho hoc cng vi vic ra d dy</li>\r\n 	<li>Bi niu, lc mu hu nh khng c tc dng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu qun khng dng thuc ng gi, khng nn dng liu b vo lc mun trong ngy, nn tip tc dng liu bnh thng vo ngy hm sau trong liu trnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon tiu ha, phn ng d ng, tng bch cu i toan, ph mch, phn ng phn v, gim bch cu trung tnh, bi nhim, vim i trng gi mc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tiu chy, bun nn, nn, chng kh tiu, chn n, au bng, kh chu thng v. Ban da, my ay, au u, bnh candida sinh dc, vim m o, nga m h.</li>\r\n 	<li> c xy ra chng mt,  tai, ic tai v thay i hnh vi tp tnh  tr nh khi dng Cefalexin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Chng ch nh</strong>\r\n\r\nQu mn vi cephalosporin.\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>S dng thuc di ngy c th gy bi nhim chng vi khun khng nhy cm.</li>\r\n 	<li>Suy thn: phi gim liu v theo di cht ch bnh nhn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Kim tra chc nng to mu, thn v gan, trong iu tr di ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh nhn c tin s bnh d dy - rut nht l bnh vim i trng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tnh an ton ca Cefalexin trong thi k thai nghn cha c thit lp.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nghim php Coomb (+) gi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Glucoza niu (+) gi trong th nghim vi Benedict,Fehling hoc vi vin Clinitest , nhng khng xy ra vi Test  Tape (Glucose Enzymatic Test Strip, USP).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 10 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIDIPHAR</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Cephalexin 500Mg', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cephalexin-500mg', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:52:15', '2021-01-29 15:52:15', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=652', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(653, 1, '2021-01-25 17:11:32', '2021-01-25 10:11:32', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Cefadroxil 500mg L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCefadroxil h tr iu trnhim khun ng tit niu: Vim thn - b thn cp v mn tnh, vim bng quang, vim niu o, nhim khun ph khoa, nhim khun ng h hp: vim amidan, vim hng, vim ph qunphi v vim phi thy, vim ph qun cp v mn tnh, p xe phi, vim m mng phi,...\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Cefadroxil 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Cefadroxil</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc khng sinh nhm cephalosporin th h th nht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nang cng, 500mg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Cefadroxil 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCefadroxil c ch nh trong iu tr cc nhim khun th nh v trung bnh do cc vi khun nhy cm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng tit niu: Vim thn - b thn cp v mn tnh, vim bng quang, vim niu o, nhim khun ph khoa.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng h hp: Vim amidan, vim hng, vim ph qun - phi v vim phi thy, vim ph qun cp v mn tnh, p xe phi, vim m mng phi, vim mng phi, vim xoang, vim thanh qun, vim tai gia.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun da v m mm: Vim hch bch huyt, p xe, vim t bo, lot do nm lu, vim v, bnh nht, vim qung.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc nhim khun khc: Vim xng ty, vim khp nhim khun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vi nhng trng hp nhim khun do vi khun Gram dng, penicilin vn l thuc u tin c chn, cc khng sinh cephalosporin th h 1 ch l thuc c chn th hai  s dng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Cefadroxil 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nCefadroxil c dng theo ng ung. C th gim bt tc dng ph ng tiu ha nu ung thuc cng vi thc n.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cefadroxil c dng theo ng ung. C th gim bt tc dng ph ng tiu ha nu ung thuc cng vi thc n.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ln v tr em (&gt; 40 kg): 500 mg - 1 g, 2 ln mi ngy ty theo mc  nhim khun. Hoc l 1 g mt ln/ngy trong cc nhim khun da v m mm v nhim khun ng tit niu khng bin chng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Tr em (&lt; 40 kg):</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Di 1 tui: 25 - 50 mg/kg th trng/24 gi, chia lm 2 - 3 ln. Th d: Dng 125 mg mi ngy, chia lm 2 ln cho tr 6 thng tui cn nng 5 kg, hoc dng 500 mg mi ngy chia lm hai ln, cho tr 1 nm tui cn nng 10 kg.</li>\r\n 	<li>T 1 - 6 tui: 250 mg, 2 ln mi ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trn 6 tui: 500 mg, 2 ln mi ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi cao tui: Cefadroxil o thi qua ng thn, cn kim tra chc nng thn v iu chnh liu dng nh  ngi bnh suy thn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Ngi bnh suy thn:</em>i vi ngi bnh suy thn, c th iu tr vi liu khi u 500 mg n 1000 mg cefadroxil. Nhng liu tip theo c th iu chnh theo bng sau:\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Thanh thi creatinin</td>\r\n<td>Liu</td>\r\n<td>Khong thi gian gia 2 liu</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>0 - 10 ml/pht</td>\r\n<td>500 - 1000mg</td>\r\n<td>36 gi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>11 - 25 ml/pht</td>\r\n<td>500 - 1000mg</td>\r\n<td>24 gi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>26 - 50 ml /pht</td>\r\n<td>500 - 1000mg</td>\r\n<td>12 gi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nCh : Thi gian iu tr phi duy tr ti thiu t 5 - 10 ngy.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu nn nhn hn m hoc khng th c, cn gi cp cu ngay lp tc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g nu qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nB sung liu ngay khi nh ra. Tuy nhin, nu thi gian gin cch vi liu tip theo qu ngn th b qua liu  qun v tip tc lch dng thuc. Khng dng liu gp i  b cho liu  b b l.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"active\">Tc dng ph ca Cefadroxil 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nau d dy, tiu chy, nn, pht ban da nh n nng, nga, ni m ay, kh th hoc kh nut, th kh kh, chy mu bt thng hoc bm tm, vim hng, au ming hoc l lot c hng, nhim trng m o. Cn gp bc s nu cc triu chng tr nn nghim trng.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Cefadroxil 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>V  thy c phn ng qu mn cho (bao gm phn ng sc phn v) xy ra gia ngi bnh d ng vi khng sinh nhm beta - lactam, nn phi c s thn trng thch ng v sn sng c mi phng tin  iu tr phn ng chong phn v khi dng cefadroxil cho ngi bnh trc y  b d ng vi penicilin. Tuy nhin, vi cefadroxil, phn ng qu mn cho vi penicilin c t l thp.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thn trng khi dng cefadroxil cho ngi bnh b suy gim chc nng thn r rt. Trc v trong khi iu tr, cn theo di lm sng cn thn v tin hnh cc xt nghim thch hp  ngi bnh suy thn hoc nghi b suy thn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng cefadroxil di ngy c th lm pht trin qu mc cc chng khng nhy cm. Cn theo di ngi bnh cn thn, nu b bi nhim, phi ngng s dng thuc.</li>\r\n 	<li> c bo co vim i trng gi mc khi s dng cc khng sinh ph rng, v vy cn phi quan tm ti chn on ny trn nhng ngi bnh b a chy nng c lin quan ti vic s dng khng sinh. Nn thn trng khi k n khng sinh ph rng cho nhng ngi c bnh ng tiu ha, c bit l bnh vim i trng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cha c  s liu tin cy chng t dng phi hp cefadroxil vi cc thuc c vi thn nh cc aminoglycosid c th lm thay i c tnh vi thn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Kinh nghim s dng cefadroxil cho tr s sinh v  non cn hn ch. Cn thn trng khi dng cho nhng ngi bnh ny.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Ph n c thai v ang cho con b:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ph n c thai: Mc d cho ti nay cha c thng bo no v tc dng c hi cho thai nhi, vic s dng an ton cephalosporin trong thi k mang thai cha c xc nh dt khot. Ch dng thuc ny trong thi k mang thai khi tht cn thit.</li>\r\n 	<li>B m cho con b: Cefadroxil bi tit trong sa m vi nng  thp, khng c tc ng trn tr ang b sa m, nhng nn quan tm khi thy tr b a chy, ta v ni ban.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>Thuc c th tng tc vi thuc no?</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cholestyramin gn kt vi cefadroxil  rut lm chm s hp th ca thuc ny.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gim tc dng: Probenecid c th lm gim bi tit cephalosporin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tng c tnh: Furosemid, aminoglycosid c th hip ng tng c tnh vi thn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 2 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">DOMESCO</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Cefadroxil 500Mg', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cefadroxil-500mg', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:46:56', '2021-01-29 15:46:56', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=653', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0);
