(654, 1, '2021-01-25 17:13:08', '2021-01-25 10:13:08', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Celecoxib 200HV USP L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc Celecoxib 200Hv Usp c thnh phn chnh l Celecoxib c tc dngiu tr triu chng thoi ha khp v vim khp dng thp  ngi ln. iu tr b tr  lm gim s lng polyp trong liu php thng thng iu tr bnh polyp dng tuyn i - trc trng c tnh gia nh. iu tr au cp, au sau phu thut, nh rng, thng kinh nguyn pht.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Celecoxib 200HV USP</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Celecoxib</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc gim au, h st; chng vim khng steroid</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc v hm lng: Vin nang, 200mg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Celecoxib 200HV USP</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>iu tr triu chng thoi ha khp v vim khp dng thp  ngi ln.</li>\r\n 	<li>iu tr b tr  lm gim s lng polyp trong liu php thng thng iu tr bnh polyp dng tuyn i - trc trng c tnh gia nh.</li>\r\n 	<li>iu tr au cp, au sau phu thut, nh rng, thng kinh nguyn pht.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Celecoxib 200HV USP</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<b>Cch dng</b>\r\n\r\nThuc dng ng ung. Nn ung trong ba n  hp thu tt hn.\r\n\r\n<b>Liu dng</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vim xng khp: liu duy nht 1 vin / ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim khp dng thp: 1 vin x 2 ln / ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>au bng kinh  ph n: liu duy nht 2 vin / ngy u. Tip theo 1 vin x 2 ln / ngy, nu cn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trng hp suy gan nh  trung bnh: Gim na liu. Khng nn dng cho bnh nhn suy gan, suy thn nng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</b>\r\n\r\nCc triu chng ca qu liu c th bao gm: thiu nng lng, bun ng, bun nn, nn, au bng, cht nn c mu hoc ging nh b c ph, phn c mu hoc en, mt  thc, ni m ay, pht ban, sng mt, mt, li, mi, c hng, cnh tay, bn tay, bn chn, mt c chn hoc cng chn, kh th hoc kh nut. Nu nn nhn hn m hoc khng th c, cn gi cp cu ngay lp tc.\r\n\r\n<b>Lm g khi qun liu?</b>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun s dng mt liu thuc, bn hy b sung cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, bn hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Khng dng gp i liu  quy nh\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"active\">Tc dng ph ca Celecoxib 200HV USP</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nTiu chy, y hi, vim hng, triu chng cm lnh, tng cn khng r nguyn nhn, bun nn, mt mi qu mc, chy mu bt thng hoc bm tm, nga, thiu nng lng, n mt ngon, au  phn trn bn phi d dy, vng da hoc mt, triu chng ging cm, rp da, cm st, pht ban, ni m ay, sng mt, c hng, li, mi, mt, tay, chn, mt c chn hoc cng chn, khn ting, kh nut hoc kh th, da nht nht, nhp tim nhanh, nc tiu c, mt mu hoc c mu, au lng, tiu kh hoc au n, i tiu thng xuyn, c bit l vo ban m. Celecoxib c th gy ra cc tc dng ph khc. Gi cho bc s nu bn c bt k vn  bt thng no khi dng thuc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Celecoxib 200HV USP</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<b>Thn trng:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tin s lot, xut huyt tiu ha.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi gi, suy kit.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ph n c thai v cho con b.</li>\r\n 	<li>Suy gan- suy thn nng, ph, tng HA, suy tim.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCnh bo\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc ny lu di c th tng nguy c tim mch bao gm au tim, ng mu, au ngc, ngng tim v t qu.</li>\r\n 	<li>V tai bin ng tiu ha: lot, xut huyt, thng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Tng tc thuc</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chung: Chuyn ho ca celecoxib qua trung gian cytochrom P450 2C9 trong gan. S dng ng thi celecoxib vi cc thuc c tc dng c ch enzym ny c th nh hng n dc ng hc ca celecoxib, nn phi thn trng khi dng ng thi cc thuc ny . Ngoi ra, celecoxib cng c ch cytochrom P450 2D6. Do  c kh nng tng tc gia celecoxib v cc thuc c chuyn ho bi P450 2D6.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc c ch men chuyn angiotensin: Cc thuc chng vim khng steroid c th lm gim tc dng chng tng huyt p ca cc thuc c ch enzym chuyn angiotensin. Cn ch  n tng tc ny khi dng celecoxib ng thi vi cc thuc c ch enzym chuyn angiotensin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc li tiu : Cc thuc chng vim khng steroid c th lm gim tc dng tng bi tit natri-niu ca furosemid v thiazid  mt s bnh nhn, c th do c ch tng hp prostaglandin v nguy c suy thn c th gia tng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Aspirin : Mc d c th dng celecoxib cng vi liu thp aspirin, vic s dng ng thi hai thuc chng vim khng steroid ny c th dn n tng t l lot ng tiu ho hoc cc bin chng khc, so vi vic dng celecoxib ring r. V khng c tc dng khng tiu cu, celecoxib khng phi l cht thay th aspirin i vi vic d phngbnh timmch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Fluconazol : Dng ng thi celecoxib vi fluconazol c th dn n tng ng k nng  huyt tng ca celecoxib. Tng tc dc ng hc ny c v do fluconazol c ch isoenzym P450 2C9 c lin quan vi s chuyn ho celecoxib. Nn bt u iu tr celecoxib vi liu khuyn dng thp nht  ngi bnh dng fluconazol ng thi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lithi: Celecoxib c th lm gim s thanh thi thn ca lithi, iu ny dn n tng nng  lithi trong huyt tng. Cn theo di cht ch bnh nhn dng ng thi lithi v celecoxib v cc du hiu c ca lithi v cn iu chnh liu cho ph hp khi bt u hoc ngng dng celecoxib.</li>\r\n 	<li>Warfarin: Cc bin chng chy mu kt hp vi tng thi gian prothrombin  xy ra  mt s bnh nhn (ch yu ngi cao tui) khi dng celecoxib ng thi vi warfarin. Do , cn theo di cc xt nghim v ng mu nh thi gian prothrombin, c bit trong my ngy u sau khi bt u hoc thay i liu php, v cc bnh nhn ny c nguy c bin chng chy mu cao.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 10 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">USP</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Celecoxib 200Hv Usp', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'celecoxib-200hv-usp', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:42:57', '2021-01-29 15:42:57', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=654', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(655, 1, '2021-01-25 17:14:19', '2021-01-25 10:14:19', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Clocardigel 75mg L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc Clocardigel 75mg c thnh phn l Clopidogrel c tc dng gim cc bin c huyt khi do x va  bnh nhn c tin s x va ng mch biu hin bi t qu thiu mu cc b (t 7 ngy n t hn 6 thng), nhi mu c tim (t vi ngy n t hn 35 ngy) hoc bnh l ng mch ngoi bin  c xc nh; kt hp vi a-xt acetyl salicylic  iu tr cho bnh nhn b hi chng mch vnh cp tnh m khng c on ST chnh ln (au tht ngc khng n nh hoc nhi mu c tim khng c sng Q).\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Clocardigel 75mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Clopidogrel 75mg (tng ng vi Clopidogrel bisulphat 97,857mg)</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc chng kt tp tiu cu, thuc nhm thuc thienopyridine.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Hp 4 v x 7 vin nn bao phim</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Clocardigel 75mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gim cc bin c huyt khi do x va  bnh nhn c tin s x va ng mch biu hin bi t qu thiu mu cc b (t 7 ngy n t hn 6 thng), nhi mu c tim (t vi ngy n t hn 35 ngy) hoc bnh l ng mch ngoi bin  c xc nh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Kt hp vi a-xt acetyl salicylic  iu tr cho bnh nhn b hi chng mch vnh cp tnh m khng c on ST chnh ln (au tht ngc khng n nh hoc nhi mu c tim khng c sng Q).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Clocardigel 75mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc dng ng ung.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ln: Liu khuyn co 75mg/ x 1 ln/ ngy. Khng cn gim liu  ngi gi v bnh nhn c bnh thn.Kt hp vi a-xt acetyl salicylic  iu tr cho ngi c hi chng mch vnh cp khng c on ST chnh: ngy u tin 300mg clopidogrel. Nhng ngy tip theo 75mg clopidogrel/ ngy, kt hp vi liu a-xt acetyl salicylic 75  325mg/ ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cha c y  d liu v hng dn dng thuc cho tr em.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nCc triu chng ca qu liu c th bao gm bm tm hoc chy mu bt thng. Nu nn nhn hn m hoc khng th c, cn gi cp cu ngay lp tc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g nu qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Clocardigel 75mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nMt mi qu mc, au u, hoa mt, bun nn, nn, au bng, tiu chy, chy mu mi, ni m ay, pht ban, nga, kh th hoc kh nut, sng mt, c hng, li, mi, mt, tay, chn, mt c chn hoc cng chn, khn ting, phn c mu en, c mu  trong phn, nn ra mu, cht nn ging b c ph, chy mu bt thng hoc bm tm, ni chm hoc kh khn, yu hoc t mt cnh tay hoc mt chn, thay i trong tm nhn, cm st, kh th, nhp tim nhanh, da nht nht, xut hin vt mu tm hoc chy mu di da, nhm ln, vng da hoc mt, co git. Clopidogrel c th gy ra cc tc dng ph khc. Gi cho bc s nu bn c bt k vn  bt thng no khi dng thuc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Clocardigel 75mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Trc khi dng clopidogrel, cho bc s v dc s bit nu bn b d ng vi clopidogrel, bt k loi thuc hoc bt k thnh phn no ca thuc clopidogrel v cc thuc bn ang dng hoc d nh dng. Ni vi bc s nu bn b chy mu vt lot trong nim mc d dy hoc rut non, chy mu no hoc bt k yu t no gy chy mu nghim trng, mi b thng, c hoc  tng c bnh gan hoc bnh thn, vim lot d dy v cc vn  v mt. Nu bn ang c phu thut, k c phu thut nha khoa, cho bc s hoc nha s bit bn ang dng clopidogrel. Clopidogrel lm tng nguy c chy mu, cn thn khng ct hoc lm tn thng c th trong qu trnh iu tr vi clopidogrel. Khng nn bt u iu tr vi clopidogrel trong vi ngy u sau khi b nhi mu c tim cp tnh. Thn trng khi kt hp clopidogrel vi cc thuc: wafarin, NSAID, heparin, a-xt acetyl salicylic v c kh nng tng nguy c chy mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ph n c thai v cho con b: Khng dng Clopidogrel cho cc i tng ny.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A-xt acetyl salicylic: Tng nguy c chy mu khi kt hp a-xt acetyl salicylic 500mg x 2 ln/ ngy vi clopidogrel 75mg/ ngy. Thn trng khi kt hp hai thuc trn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Heparin: Dng kt hp Heparin vi Clopidogrel c th gia tng nguy c chy mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thuc khng vim khng steroid (NSAID): c hin tng gia tng xut huyt d dy n khi dng phi hp naloxon vi clopidogrel cho ngi khe mnh, cha c kt qu nghin cu v s phi hp gia clopidogrel vi cc NSAID khc. Cn thn trng khi phi hp clopidogrel vi NSAID.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nClopidogrel c chuyn ha bi cytochrom P450 isoenzyme CYP2C9, CYP2B6 nn c th tng tc vi cc thuc c chuyn ha bi enzyme ny:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thuc khng nm: Ketoconazole lm gim nng  trong huyt tng ca cht chuyn ha c hot tnh ca clopidogrel, lm gim tc dng c ch tiu cu ca clopidogrel.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bupropion: Clopidogrel lm gim s chuyn ha bupropion thnh cht chuyn ha c hot tnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhm statin: gia tng nguy c tiu c vn khi ung clopidogrel cng vi ciclosporin v nhm statin (atorvastatin, lovastatin, simvastatin).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 4 v x 7 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">OPV</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Clocardigel 75Mg', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'clocardigel-75mg', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:32:27', '2021-01-29 15:32:27', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=655', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(656, 1, '2021-01-25 17:16:14', '2021-01-25 10:16:14', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Cefimvid 200Mg 10V L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCefimvid 200Mg 10V iu tr vim tai gia, vim hng, vim amidan, vim ph qun, vim phi cp &amp; mn tnh.Nhim trng tit niu - sinh dc, bnh lu, da &amp; m mm.iu tr thng hn.D phng nhim trng phu thut.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Cefimvid 200Mg 10V</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh:cefiximtrihydrat</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc khng sinh</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nn di bao phim, 200mg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Cefimvid 200Mg 10V</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vim tai gia, vim hng, vim amidan, vim ph qun, vim phi cp &amp; mn tnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim trng tit niu</li>\r\n 	<li>sinh dc, bnh lu, da &amp; m mm.</li>\r\n 	<li>iu tr thng hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>D phng nhim trng phu thut.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Cefimvid 200Mg 10V</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCch dng\r\n\r\nDng ng ung\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ln &amp; tr &gt; 12 tui: 50</li>\r\n 	<li>100 mg x 2 ln/ngy, c th tng ln 200 mg x 2 ln/ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng tiu do lu liu duy nht 400 mg. Suy thn: gim liu.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu qun khng dng thuc ng gi, khng nn dng liu b vo lc mun trong ngy, nn tip tc dng liu bnh thng vo ngy hm sau trong liu trnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Cefimvid 200Mg 10V</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nRi lon tiu ho, nhc u, ni mn, m ay, nga, st, au khp. gim tiu cu, gim bch cu, tng bch cu i toan, thay i chc nng gan, thn.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Cefimvid 200Mg 10V</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Chng ch nh</strong>\r\n\r\nQu mn vi cephalosporin.\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Qu mn vi penicillin, ngi suy thn, tin s bnh d dy - rut, bnh i trng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ph n c thai &amp; cho con b, tr di 6 thng tui khng dng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nWarfarin\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 1 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIDIPHAR</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Cefimvid 200Mg 10V', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cefimvid-200mg-10v', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:23:52', '2021-01-29 15:23:52', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=656', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
