(657, 1, '2021-01-25 17:17:35', '2021-01-25 10:17:35', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Cefalexin 500mg L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCefalexin 500mg iu tr nhim trng do mt s vi khun Gr(-) &amp; Gr(+) k c Staphylococcus sn xut men penicillinase, nhim trng ng tit niu, h hp, da &amp; m mm.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Cefalexin 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh:Cefalexin 500mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc khng sinh</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nang, 500mg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Cefalexin 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng h hp: Vim ph qun cp v mn tnh v gin ph qun nhim khun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun tai, mi, hng: Vim tai gia, vim xng chm, vim xoang, vim amian hc v vim hng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim ng tit niu: Vim bng quang v vim tuyn tin lit. iu tr d phng nhim khun ng niu ti pht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun sn v ph khoa.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun da, m mm v xng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh lu (khi penicilin khng ph hp).</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim khun rng.</li>\r\n 	<li>iu tr d phng thay penicilin cho ngi mcbnh timphi iu tr rng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Cefalexin 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nDng ung\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ln: Ung 250  500 mg cch 6 gi/1 ln, ty theo mc  nhim khun. Liu c th ln ti 4 g/ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lu : Thi gian iu tr nn ko di t nht t 7 n 10 ngy. Trong cc nhim khun ng niu phc tp, ti pht, mn tnh, nn iu tr 2 tun (1 g/ln x 2 ln/ngy). Vi bnh lu, thng dng liu duy nht 3 g vi 1 g probenecid cho nam hay 2 g vi 0,5 g probenecid cho n. Dng kt hp vi probenecid s ko di thi gian o thi ca cefalexin v lm tng nng  trong huyt thanh t 50  100%.</li>\r\n 	<li>iu chnh liu khi c suy thn</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu qun khng dng thuc ng gi, khng nn dng liu b vo lc mun trong ngy, nn tip tc dng liu bnh thng vo ngy hm sau trong liu trnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"active\">Tc dng ph ca Cefalexin 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mt vi trng hp c th xy ra: y bng, tiu chy, bun nn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thng bo cho bc s nhng tc dng khng mong mun gp phi khi s dng thuc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Cefalexin 500mg</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Chng ch nh</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mn cm vi cc cephalosporin.</li>\r\n 	<li>D ng vi penicilin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr s sinh di 1 thng tui</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thn trong khi phi hp vi khng sinh khc c vi thn, c bit nhm Aminozit, thuc li tiu, nhm Furosemid, Acid Etacrylic .</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi suy thn trnh dng liu cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cephalexin qua sa m, khuyn nn ngng cho con b trong thi gian iu tr.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>V cc khng sinh nhm Cephalosporin nh Cephalexin ch tc ng ln cc vi khun tng sinh, khng nn kt hp chng vi khng sinh km khun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khi kt hp vi thuc li tiu mnh (Etacrynic acid, Furosemid) hay cc khng sinh c kh nng gy c thn (Aminoglycosid, Polymixin, Colistin), Cephalexin c th gy c tnh thn nhiu hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Probenecid lm tng nng  huyt thanh v thi gian bn thi ca Cephalexin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nh cc khng sinh khc, Cephalexin lm gim tc dng thuc nga</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 10 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">DOMESCO</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Cefalexin 500Mg', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cefalexin-500mg', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:22:03', '2021-01-29 15:22:03', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=657', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(658, 1, '2021-01-25 17:19:27', '2021-01-25 10:19:27', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc BIHASAL 5 L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nBihasal 5 mg, cha thnh phn chnhBisoprolol hemifumarate, c tc dng iu tr trong cc trng hp sau: tng huyt p t nh n va. C th dng n tr liu hoc phi hp vi cc thuc chng tng huyt p khc, c bit l thuc li tiu, cn au tht ngc...\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca BIHASAL 5</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Bisoprolol hemifumarate</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc tim mch</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nn bao phim 5 mg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca BIHASAL 5</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc c ch nh  iu tr trong cc trng hp sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tng huyt p t nh n va. C th dng n tr liu hoc phi hp vi cc thuc chng tng huyt p khc, c bit l thuc li tiu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cn au tht ngc.</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr trong iu tr bnh suy tim mn tnh n nh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca BIHASAL 5</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nUng thuc vi nhiu nc, nn dng thuc vo bui sng khi i hoc lc im tm.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mc liu lng nn c xc nh ty theo tng c th ph hp vi nhp tim v kt qu iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trong iu tr tng huyt p v au tht ngc:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Liu thng thng: ung liu duy nht t 5  10 mg/ ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Liu ti a: 20 mg/ ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng cn thit phi iu chnh liu  bnh nhn ri lon chc nng gan v thn t nh n va. Liu khi u c th l 2,5 mg/ ngy v lu  iu chnh liu cho ph hp. Liu ca Bisoprolol fumarate khng c vt qu 10 mg/ ngy i vi bnh nhn suy thn nng ( thanh thi creatinine di 20 ml/ min) hoc ri lon chc nng gan nghim trng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Trong iu tr suy tim:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Liu khi u: ung liu duy nht 1,25 mg/ ngy. Nu dung np thuc, c th tng liu ln gp i sau 1 tun, v tng liu dn dn trong khong t 1-4 tun n liu ti a m bnh nhn c th dung np c nhng khng nn vt qu 10 mg/ ngy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khng cn thit iu chnh liu  bnh nhn ln tui tr trng hp b ri lon chc nng gan v thn ng k.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi b qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nThng gp nht l chm nhp v h huyt p. Phi ngng s dng Bisoprolol ngay v iu tr bng cch tim tnh mch atropine (1 -2 mg), nu cn c th theo - sau bi mt liu truyn tnh mch 25 mcg isoprenaline, glucagon cng c th c dng vi liu t 1-5 mg.\r\n\r\nC th xy ra co tht ph qun v suy tim. iu tr co tht ph qun bng cch tim tnh mch aminophylline v iu tr suy tim bng thuc tr tim mch (digitalis) v thuc li tiu.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi thiu 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nDng liu  ngay khi nh ra. Tuy nhin nu  gn ti gi ung liu tip theo th hy b qua liu  v tip tc lch trnh dng thuc theo ch dn. Khng dng liu gp i  b cho liu  b l.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca BIHASAL 5</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thng gp: Mt mi, chng mt, hoa mt, nhc u,  m hi, ri lon gic ng, c nhng gic m mnh, lo lng, mt tp trung v trm cm. Cc triu chng ny thng t nghim trng v thng bin mt trong vng t 1 n 2 tun sau khi bt u iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thnh thong: Ri lon tiu ho (tiu chy, to bn, bun nn, nn ma, au bng, d dy, au vng thng v, lot d dy...), h huyt p, mch chm, hoc ri lon dn truyn nh tht, tnh trng t rn v cm gic lnh  u chi. - Him gp: phn ng ngoi da (nh ban , sng ty, nga, rng tc...), nhc c, vp b v gim tit nc mt (nu c mang knh st trng), tng  khng ng h hp (kh th trn bnh nhn c khuynh hng b phn ng co tht ph qun).</li>\r\n 	<li>Trn bnh nhn c dng i khp khing v hin tng Raynaud, lc bt u iu tr cc triu chng ny c th tr nn nghim trng hn v suy c tim c th nng hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trn bnh nhn ln tui b tiu ng, nhng du hiu h ng huyt nh tim p nhanh c th b che lp.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCc bt thng xt nghim:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thng c s tng triglycerid huyt thanh nhng khng chc do thuc gy ra.</li>\r\n 	<li>C s tng nh acid uric, creatinine, BUN, kali huyt thanh, glucose v phospho, s gim nh t bo bch cu v tiu cu. Nhng s thay i ny khng c  ngha lm sng quan trng v him khi phi ngng dng Bisoprolol fumarate.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca BIHASAL 5</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thn trng:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSuy tim: Khng s dng cc thuc chn bta cho bnh nhn c triu chng ca bnh suy tim sung huyt. Tuy nhin,  mt s bnh nhn suy tim phi b, nu cn thit s dng thuc th phi tht thn trng.\r\n\r\nNgng iu tr t ngt: Ngng iu tr t ngt cc thuc chn bta c th lm trm trng thm cn au tht ngc, nhi mu c tim hoc lon nhp tm tht  nhng bnh nhn mc bnh ng mch vnh. Nn thn trng khi ngng iu tr nu khng c hng dn ca bc s.\r\n\r\nBnh co tht ph qun: V tnh chn lc bta1 tng i nn c th dng Bisoprolol vi mc thn trng cn thit  ngi bnh co tht ph qun khng p ng hoc khng dung np liu php chng tng huyt p khc. Chnh v tnh chn lc bta1 khng tuyt i nn c th dng Bisoprolol  liu thp nht c th c vi liu khi u l 2,5 mg/ ngy. Cng c th dng ng thi vi mt thuc kch thch bta2 (cht gy gin ph qun).\r\n\r\nGii phu v gy m: Nn ngng s dng Bisoprolol t nht 48 gi trc khi bnh nhn c phu thut. Nu phi s dng thuc trong sut qu trnh phu thut, nn thn trng i vi cc tc nhn gy m nh ether, cyclopropan v trichloroethylen. Nu qu liu, x l vi atropin 1-2 mg I.V.\r\n\r\nTiu ng v h glucose mu: Bisoprolol che du biu hin h ng huyt (c bit l nhp tim nhanh). Tuy nhin,  bnh nhn tiu ng c ch nh insulin hoc cc thuc h ng huyt dng ung, nn s dng Bisoprolol mt cch thn trng.\r\n\r\nNhim c tuyn gip: Bisoprolol c th che du cc du hiu lm sng cng tuyn gip (nh nhp tim nhanh). S ngng t ngt thuc chn bta c th thc y cn nhim c tuyn gip.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>S dng cho ph n c thai v cho con b:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKhng nn s dng thuc cho ph n ang c thai hoc cho con b.\r\n\r\nDo c kh nng gy nhp tim chm, h huyt p v h ng huyt trn tr s sinh, trc thi hn sinh l 72 gi, phi c chm dt iu tr vi Bisoprolol. Nu vic iu tr khng th chm dt c, tr s sinh phi c theo di trong vng 48-72 gi sau khi sinh.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tc ng ca thuc khi li xe, vn hnh my mc:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDo thuc c tc dng h huyt p nn ty theo c th c th nh hng n kh nng li xe v vn hnh my mc. c bit l tnh trng ny thng xy ra vo lc u iu tr v khi c thay i s dng thuc cng nh khi c s tng tc vi ru.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\n- Cc loi thuc c th xy ra tng tc:\r\n\r\nKhng nn phi hp vi cc thuc chn beta khc.\r\n\r\niu tr ng thi Bisoprolol vi cc thuc lm cn kit catecholamine (reserpin, alpha-methyldopa, clonidin v guanethidine) c th lm gim ng k nhp tim.  bnh nhn c iu tr ng thi vi clonidine, nu mun ngng thuc, khuyn co nn ngng s dng Bisoprolol trong vi ngy trc khi ngng clonidine.\r\n\r\nS dng ng thi Bisoprolol vi thuc lm gin c tim hay c ch dn truyn nh tht nh mt s thuc i vn calci (c bit l nhm phenylalkylamine [verapamil] v nhm benzothiazepine [diltiazem]), hoc tc nhn chng lon nhp (disopyramide) c th xy ra h huyt p, nhp chm, lon nhp tim hoc suy tim.\r\n\r\nKhi dng ng thi vi reserpin, alpha-methyldopa, guanfacine, clonidine hoc cc glycoside c th lm gim ng k nhp tim.\r\n\r\nRifampin lm tng chuyn ho thi tr Bisoprolol fumarate do  rt ngn thi gian bn thi ca thuc. Tuy nhin, vic iu chnh liu ca Bisoprolol l khng cn thit.\r\n\r\nS dng Bisoprolol cng lc vi insulin v thuc lm gim ng huyt ng ung, c th lm tng kh nng tc dng ca chng. Cc triu chng h ng huyt (c bit l nhp tim nhanh) b che lp i hoc b gim nh. Hm lng ng huyt phi c kim tra theo di mt cch u n.\r\n\r\n- Cc loi thc phm,  ung c th xy ra tng tc:\r\n\r\nThc n, ru v thuc l c th tng tc vi vi loi thuc nht nh. Hy tham kho  kin bc s v vic ung thuc cng thc n, ru v thuc l.\r\n\r\n- Tnh trng sc khe no nh hng n thuc:\r\n\r\nBisoprolol chng ch nh  ngi bnh c sc do tim, suy tim cp, suy tim cha kim sot c bng iu tr nn, suy tim  III nng hoc  IV, blc nh - tht  hai hoc ba, v nhp tim chm xoang (di 60/pht trc khi iu tr), bnh nt xoang, hen nng, hoc bnh phi - ph qun mn tnh tc nghn nng, Hi chng Reynaud nng. Mn cm vi bisoprolol, u tu thng thn (u t bo a crm) khi cha c iu tr.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 3 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">HASAN</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Bihasal 5', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bihasal-5', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:14:38', '2021-01-29 15:14:38', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=658', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(659, 1, '2021-01-25 17:21:17', '2021-01-25 10:21:17', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc BISILKON BIDIPHAR 10G L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nBisilkon Bidiphar 10G iu tr cc bnh l da p ng vi corticosteroid khi c bin chng nhim trng do vi khun (nhy cm vi gentamicin) v nm (nhy cm vi clotrimazol) hoc khi nghi ng do nhim trng. BISILKON thch hp  iu tr eczema c r dch.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca BISILKON BIDIPHAR 10G</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dc cht chnh:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nClotrimazol ................................................ 100 mg\r\n\r\nBetamethason dipropionat .......................... 6,4 mg\r\n\r\nGentamicin (di dng Gentamicin sulfat) ..10 mg\r\n\r\nT dc va .............................................1 tup\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Loi thuc:</strong>Thuc iu tr bnh da liu</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dng thuc, hm lng:</strong>Kem bi ngoi da.<strong></strong>Hp 1 tup 10 g.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca BISILKON BIDIPHAR 10G</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\niu tr cc bnh l da p ng vi corticosteroid khi c bin chng nhim trng do vi khun (nhy cm vi gentamicin) v nm (nhy cm vi clotrimazol) hoc khi nghi ng do nhim trng. BISILKON thch hp  iu tr eczema c r dch.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca BISILKON BIDIPHAR 10G</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng - Liu dng:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ra sch vng da b nhim bnh, thm kh ri thoa lp thuc mng va  ln vng da b nh hng 2 ln/ngy, vo bui sng v bui ti.  iu tr hiu qu, BISILKON nn c bi thng xuyn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thi gian iu tr khc nhau ty thuc vo mc , v tr ca bnh v p ng ca bnh nhn. Tuy nhin, khi bi thuc trong 3  4 tun m khng thy c du hiu ci thin th nn ngng thuc v khm li.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em><strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong></em>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong></em>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca BISILKON BIDIPHAR 10G</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nCha c bo co.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca BISILKON BIDIPHAR 10G</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Chng ch nh</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi c tin s mn cm vi cc thnh phn ca thuc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vt thng h hoc mng nhy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi nhim trng da do nhim vi khun (lao da, giang mai,), nm (nhim Candida,), virus (gii leo, rp da, thy u, u ma,) v cn trng (gh nga, ch rn,) (triu chng c th xu i).</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim da quanh ming, mn ni chung v mn trng c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Corticoid dng ti ch hp thu ton thn c th gy c ch vng di i - tuyn yn  thng thn (HPA) c hi phc, hi chng Cushing, tng ng huyt, tiu ng v long xng  mt s bnh nhn.  mt s ngi dng corticoid ngoi da thoa vi din tch rng hoc trong tnh trng bng kn, s c ch trc vng di i  tuyn yn  thng thn phi c kim tra thng xuyn qua nng  cortisol trong mu, cortisol t do trong nc tiu hoc th nghim s kch thch ACTH.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nn trnh  dng iu tr lu di, c bit l bng kn v thuc c th gy ra tc dng ph ging nh dng corticoid ng ung.</li>\r\n 	<li>S dng ng thi vi khng sinh aminoglycosid ton thn c th gy c t vic tch ly thuc khng sinh. Tr nhng trng hp c bit, trnh dng lin tc trong di ngy v trong tnh trng bng kn. c bit lu  nhng thng tin trn i vi tr s sinh v tr em.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng dng  iu tr nhim nm ton thn; nu c kch ng hoc mn cm, phi ngng thuc v iu tr thch hp; phi iu tr thuc  thi gian theo ch nh mc d cc triu chng c thuyn gim; bo vi thy thuc nu c biu hin tng kch ng  vng bi thuc (, nga, bng, mn nc, sng), du hiu ca s qu mn. Trnh cc ngun gy nhim khun hoc ti nhim.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nCha c bo co.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Tup 10g</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">CNG TY CP DC - TTBYT BNH NH</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Bisilkon Bidiphar 10G', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bisilkon-bidiphar-10g', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:11:52', '2021-01-29 15:11:52', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=659', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
