(660, 1, '2021-01-25 17:22:25', '2021-01-25 10:22:25', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc APFU L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nApfu c s dng  iu tr nm hoc nm men nhim trng nghim trng, chng hn nh nm Candida m o, Candida hu hng, nm Candida thc qun, nhim candida khc, hoc nm (Cryptococcus) vim mng no.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca APFU</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Cefpodoxim.............200mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc tr k sinh trng, chng nhim khun, khng virus, khng nm</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nang</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca APFU</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhim nm Candida nim mc: mi, ming, hu hng, k c bnh nhn suy gim min dch. Nm Candida m o cp tnh hay ti pht, nm chn, thn, bn.</li>\r\n 	<li>iu tr v phng nga nhim nm Candida  bnh nhn b bnh c tnh, AIDS.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim mng no do Cryptococcus hoc phng nga ti pht vim mng no do Cryptococcus  bnh nhn AIDS.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca APFU</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nDng bng ng ung.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhim nm Candida hu hng: 50-100mg/ngy trong 1-2 tun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim nm Candida m o: liu duy nht 150mg.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim nm chn, thn, bn: 150 mg/ln/tun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim mng no do Cryptococcus: liu khi u 400mg/ngy u tin. Sau  200 mg/ngy, dng t nht 6-8 tun. Trng hp phng nga ti pht do Cryptococcus: 100-200mg/ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ln tui: nu khng c du hiu suy thn c th dng liu thng thng. Nu c du hiu suy thn ( thanh thi creatinin &lt; 40 ml/pht), nn iu chnh liu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh nhn suy thn: pht  iu tr liu n khng cn chnh liu. Vi pht  iu tr nhiu ln/ngy dng liu thng thng trong 1-2 ngy, sau  cn iu chnh khong cch gia cc liu.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca APFU</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nNhc u, bun nn, au bng, tiu chy, y hi, ni mn da.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca APFU</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nHy cho bc s ca bn bit nu bn  tng c bt k phn ng bt thng hoc d ng vi thnh phn ca thuc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nNghin cu trn lm sng, fluconazol gy tng nng  huyt tng ca phenytoin. Thi gian bn hy ca fluconazol trong huyt tng ko di khi dng chung vi sulphonylurea. Cn theo di v iu chnh liu ca phenytoin v sulphonylurea.\r\n\r\nRifampicin lm gim  hp thu v thi gian bn hy ca fluconazol. Do  khi dng ng thi vi rifampicin, cn tng liu ca fluconazol.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 1 v x 10 vin</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">USP</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Apfu', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'apfu', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:10:13', '2021-01-29 15:10:13', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=660', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
