(661, 1, '2021-01-25 17:23:32', '2021-01-25 10:23:32', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Azopt 5ml L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nHuyn dch nh mt Azopt 1%c tc dng iu tr chng tng p lc ni nhn trn bnh nhn tng nhn p hay Glaucoma  gc m.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Azopt 5ml</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Brinzolamide 1%</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc nh mt</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Hn dch nh mt, 5ml</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Azopt 5ml</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\niu tr chng tng p lc ni nhn trn bnh nhn tng nhn p hay Glaucoma  gc m\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Azopt 5ml</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc nh mt.\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\r\n\r\nNh 1 git x 3 ln/ngy, mi ln nh cch nhau t nht 10 pht.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Azopt 5ml</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhn m v c v ng, v chay hay v bt thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Him gp: vim kt mc m mt, vim da, kh mt, cm mt, nhc u, xung huyt, xut tit nhn cu, kh chu  mt, vim gic mc, vim nhn cu, nga mt, vim mi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rt him: phn ng d ng, hi u, au ngc, vim kt mc, tiu chy, nhn i, chng mt, kh ming, kh th, kh tiu, mi mt, tng trng lc, au thn, ng vy hay cm gic dnh  mi mt, bun nn, vim hng, chy nc mt, m ay.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Azopt 5ml</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Chng ch nh</strong>\r\n\r\nQu mn vi thnh phn thuc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n\r\nPh n c thai, cho con b, tr em di 3 tui.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nCha c bo co.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Chai 5ml</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">ALCON</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">UNITED STATES</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Azopt 5Ml', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'azopt-5ml', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:07:42', '2021-01-29 15:07:42', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=661', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
(662, 1, '2021-01-25 17:24:29', '2021-01-25 10:24:29', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Benita L g?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\nThuc Benita iu trvim mi d ngquanh nm, vim mi d ng theo ma, vim mi vn mch. D phng ti pht polyp mi sau phu thut ct polyp. iu tr triu chng polyp mi.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Benita</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Budesonid 1,28mg</li>\r\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc ng h hp</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Hn dch xt mi, chai 120 liu (liu 64 mcg).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Benita</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vim mi d ng quanh nm, vim mi d ng theo ma, vim mi vn mch.</li>\r\n 	<li>D phng ti pht polyp mi sau phu thut ct polyp. iu tr triu chng polyp mi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Benita</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\r\n\r\nThuc xt mi\r\n\r\n<strong>Liu dng thuc Benita</strong>\r\n\r\nNgi ln v tr em &gt; 6t: Khi u 256 mcg/ngy. S dng 1 ln vo bui sng (128 mcg mi bn mi) hoc chia u sng v ti (64 mcg mi bn mi vo bui sng v ti). Khi t c hiu qu, gim liu xung thp nht m vn kim sot c triu chng.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\r\n\r\nNu bn qun mt liu thuc, hy dng cng sm cng tt. Tuy nhin, nu gn vi liu k tip, hy b qua liu  qun v dng liu k tip vo thi im nh k hoch. Lu  rng khng nn dng gp i liu  quy nh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Benita</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Kch ng ti ch, xut huyt ng mi nh, chy mu cam.</li>\r\n 	<li>t gp: Ph mch, ni m ay, vim da, ni mn, nga.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rt him gp: Thng vch ngn mi, lot nim mc, phn ng phn v</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lu  ca Benita</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bnh nhn nhim nm, nhim Herpes ng mi; s dng corticosteroid ng ton thn chuyn sang dng Benita khi c nghi ng ri lon trc h i-tuyn yn-thng thn; lao phi, suy gan.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trnh tip xc mt.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr em.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ph n c thai (ch dng khi tht s cn), cho con b</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\r\n\r\nKetoconazole v cht c ch CYP3A4 mnh khc\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Chai</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">MERAP</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\r\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Benita', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'benita', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:06:20', '2021-01-29 15:06:20', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=thuoc&#038;p=662', 0, 'thuoc', '', 0),
