(707, 1, '2021-01-25 22:52:45', '2021-01-25 15:52:45', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Amoxicillin 250mg VDP L g?</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n\nThuc iu tr nhim khun ng h hp trn, nhim khun ng h hp di do lin cu khun, ph cu khun, t cu khun khng tit penicilinase v H. influenzae, nhim khun ng tit niu khng bin chng, bnh lu.\n\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Amoxicillin 250mg VDP</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n<ul>\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh: Amoxicillin</li>\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc tr k sinh trng, chng nhim khun, khng virus,khng nm</li>\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Hp 10 v x 10 vin nang</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Amoxicillin 250mg VDP</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n<ul>\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng h hp trn.</li>\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng h hp di do lin cu khun, ph cu khun, t cu khun khng tit penicilinase v H. influenzae.</li>\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng tit niu khng bin chng.</li>\n 	<li>Bnh lu.</li>\n 	<li>Nhim khun ng mt.</li>\n 	<li>Nhim khun da, c do lin cu khun, t cu khun, E. coli nhy cm vi amoxicilin.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Amoxicillin 250mg VDP</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\n\nThuc dng ng ung\n\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Liu thng dng l 250 - 500 mg, cch 8 gi mt ln.</li>\n 	<li>Tr em n 10 tui c th dng liu 125 - 250 mg, cch 8 gi mt ln.</li>\n 	<li>Tr em di 20 kg thng dng liu 20 - 40 mg/kg th trng/ngy.</li>\n 	<li>Liu 3g, nhc li sau 8 gi  iu tr p-xe quanh rng, hoc nhc li sau 10 - 12 gi  iu tr nhim khun cp ng tit niu khng bin chng.</li>\n 	<li> d phng vim mng trong tim  ngi d mc, cho liu duy nht 3 g cch 1 gi trc khi lm th thut nh nh rng.</li>\n 	<li>Dng phc  liu cao 3 g x 2 ln/ngy cho ngi bnh nhim khun ng h hp nng hoc ti pht.</li>\n 	<li>Nu cn, tr em 3 - 10 tui b vim tai gia c th dng liu 750 mg x 2 ln/ngy trong 2 ngy.</li>\n 	<li>i vi ngi suy thn, phi gim liu theo h s thanh thi creatinin:</li>\n 	<li>Cl creatinin &lt; 10 ml/pht: 500 mg/24 gi.</li>\n 	<li>Cl creatinin &gt; 10 ml/pht: 500 mg/12 gi.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Lm g khi dng qu liu?</strong>\n\nNu nn nhn hn m hoc khng th c, cn gi cp cu ngay lp tc.\n\nTrong trng hp khn cp, hy gi ngay cho Trung tm cp cu 115 hoc n trm Y t a phng gn nht.\n\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\n\nB sung liu ngay khi nh ra. Tuy nhin, nu thi gian gin cch vi liu tip theo qu ngn th b qua liu  qun v tip tc lch dng thuc. Khng dng liu gp i  b cho liu  b b l.\n\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Amoxicillin 250mg VDP</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n<ul>\n 	<li>Thng gp: Ngoi ban (3-10%), thng xut hin chm sau 7 ngy iu tr.</li>\n 	<li>t gp:</li>\n</ul>\n+ Tiu ho: Bun nn, nn, a chy.\n+ Phn ng qu mn: Ban , ban dt sn v my ay, c bit l hi chng Stevens-Johnson.\n<ul>\n 	<li>Him gp:</li>\n</ul>\n+ Gan: Tng nh SGOT.\n+ Thn kinh trung ng: Kch ng, vt v, lo lng, mt ng, l ln, thay i ng x v/hoc chng mt.\n+ Mu: Thiu mu, gim tiu cu, ban xut huyt gim tiu cu, tng bch cu a eosin, gim bch cu, mt bch cu ht.\n\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2>Lu  ca Amoxicillin 250mg VDP</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Phi nh k kim tra cc chc nng gan, thn trong sut qu trnh iu tr di ngy.</li>\n 	<li>C th xy ra phn ng qu mn trm trng  nhng bnh nhn c tin s d ng vi penicillin hoc cc d nguyn khc, nn cn phi iu tra k tin s d ng vi penicillin, cephalosporin v cc d nguyn khc.</li>\n 	<li>Nu phn ng d ng xy ra nh ban , ph Quincke, sc phn v, hi chng Stevens-Johnson, phi ngng dng amoxicillin v ngay lp tc iu tr cp cu bng adrenalin, th oxy, liu php corticoid tim tnh mch v thng kh, k c t ni kh qun v khng bao gi c iu tr bng penicillin hoc cephalosporin na.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>S hp thu amoxicillin khng b nh hng bi thc n trong d dy, do  c th ung trc hay sau ba n. Nifedipin lm tng hp thu amoxicillin.</li>\n 	<li>Khi dng alopurinol cng vi amoxicillin s lm tng kh nng pht ban ca amoxicillin.</li>\n 	<li>C th c s i khng gia cht dit khun amoxicillin v cc cht km khun nh cloramphenicol, tetracyclin.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 10 v x 10 vin</div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"\">Nh sn xut</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIDIPHAR</div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\n</ul>', 'Amoxicillin 250Mg Vdp', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '705-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-01-25 22:52:45', '2021-01-25 15:52:45', '', 705, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/705-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
