(739, 1, '2021-01-29 22:47:53', '2021-01-29 15:47:53', '<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Thuc Cephalexin 500Mg L g?</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n\nCephalexin 500Mg iu tr nhim trng do mt s vi khun Gr(-) &amp; Gr(+) k c Staphylococcus sn xut men penicillinase, nhim trng ng tit niu, h hp, da &amp; m mm.\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Thnh phn ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n<ul>\n 	<li>Dc cht chnh:Cephalexin 500mg</li>\n 	<li>Loi thuc: Thuc khng sinh</li>\n 	<li>Dng thuc, hm lng: Vin nang, 500mg</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Cng dng ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n\nNhim trng do mt s vi khun Gr(-) &amp; Gr(+) k c Staphylococcus sn xut men penicillinase, nhim trng ng tit niu, h hp, da &amp; m mm.\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Liu dng ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n\n<strong>Cch dng</strong>\n\nDng ng ung.Ung thuc trc ba n 1 gi.\n\n<strong>Liu dng</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Ngi ln: 0.5 g- 1 g/ ln, ung cch khong 6 gi.</li>\n 	<li>Tr em: 25 - 50mg/ kg/ngy, chia 4 ln. Trng hp nhim khun nng, phi tng gp i liu dng.</li>\n 	<li>Vim hng v vim bng quang cp: liu hng ngy c th chia lm 2 ln.</li>\n 	<li>Vim tai gia: 75 - 100mg/ngy/kg, chia 4 ln.</li>\n 	<li>Nhim khun Beta-tan huyt, thi gian iu tr ti thiu  10 ngy.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Qu liu v x tr</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Triu chng:bun nn, nn, kh chu thng v, tiu chy v huyt niu</li>\n 	<li>iu tr: Nn ch nh than hot thay cho hoc cng vi vic ra d dy</li>\n 	<li>Bi niu, lc mu hu nh khng c tc dng.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Lm g khi qun 1 liu?</strong>\n\nNu qun khng dng thuc ng gi, khng nn dng liu b vo lc mun trong ngy, nn tip tc dng liu bnh thng vo ngy hm sau trong liu trnh.\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"section-7\" class=\"\">Tc dng ph ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n<ul>\n 	<li>Ri lon tiu ha, phn ng d ng, tng bch cu i toan, ph mch, phn ng phn v, gim bch cu trung tnh, bi nhim, vim i trng gi mc.</li>\n 	<li>Tiu chy, bun nn, nn, chng kh tiu, chn n, au bng, kh chu thng v. Ban da, my ay, au u, bnh candida sinh dc, vim m o, nga m h.</li>\n 	<li> c xy ra chng mt,  tai, ic tai v thay i hnh vi tp tnh  tr nh khi dng Cefalexin.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2>Lu  ca Cephalexin 500Mg</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">\n\n<strong>Chng ch nh</strong>\n\nQu mn vi cephalosporin.\n\n<strong>Thn trng khi s dng</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>S dng thuc di ngy c th gy bi nhim chng vi khun khng nhy cm.</li>\n 	<li>Suy thn: phi gim liu v theo di cht ch bnh nhn.</li>\n 	<li>Kim tra chc nng to mu, thn v gan, trong iu tr di ngy.</li>\n 	<li>Bnh nhn c tin s bnh d dy - rut nht l bnh vim i trng.</li>\n 	<li>Tnh an ton ca Cefalexin trong thi k thai nghn cha c thit lp.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Tng tc thuc</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Nghim php Coomb (+) gi.</li>\n 	<li>Glucoza niu (+) gi trong th nghim vi Benedict,Fehling hoc vi vin Clinitest , nhng khng xy ra vi Test  Tape (Glucose Enzymatic Test Strip, USP).</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"active\">Quy cch</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">Hp 10 v x 10 vin</div>\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nh sn xut</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIDIPHAR</div>\n<h2 id=\"section-6\">Nc sn xut</h2>\n<div class=\"lc-content-cover\">VIET NAM</div>\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\n</ul>', 'Cephalexin 500Mg', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '652-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-01-29 22:47:53', '2021-01-29 15:47:53', '', 652, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/652-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
