(781, 1, '2021-01-30 22:03:35', '2021-01-30 15:03:35', '<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\"><strong>Bi no tr em l tn thng no b ca tr khin n khng tin trin c v gy nh hng n s pht trin chc nng vn ng, ngn ng, cm gic</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Bi no tr em l g?</strong></h3>\r\nBi no tr em l tn thng no b ca tr khin n khng tin trin c v gy nh hng n s pht trin chc nng vn ng, ngn ng, cm gic Biu hin thng thy ca bnh nhi l ri lon vn ng, c th km cc ri lon khc v tr tu, gic quan v hnh vi. Nguyn nhn gy bnh bt ngun t cc yu t tc ng  giai on trc sinh, trong khi sinh v sau sinh n 5 tui. Hin vn cha c phng pho cha tr hon ton chng bi no, nhng ph huynh c th gip tr ci thin kh nng tip cn th gii thng qua s n lc, kin tr v cc hot ng cng tr.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/6/2018/05/6-bai-nao-tre-em-5128-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"Bi no tr em\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-next icon-next\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Next slide\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/6/2018/05/6-bai-nao-tre-em-2045-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"Bi no tr em\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca bi no tr em</strong></h3>\r\nNgi nh bnh nhi cn quan st v nm bt cc triu chng di y sm  kp thi can thip, th c hi phc hi s rt cao.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon vn ng: Tay chn di chuyn khng nhp nhng, di chuyn b lch hai bn. C th mm ot, t c vn ng t pht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon sinh l: C th tr cng , nut khng tt, ng di gic, vng u hnh dng bt thng, vi tr s sinh b khng c lc, thng tr sa, c ming cng, cn nng t tng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon ngn ng: Phn ln cc bnh nhn u c biu hin ny. Cc tr b din t kh khn, ngng v ni lp, cng c khi mt ngn ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon tr tu: tr mc bi no tr tu khong bng  ngi bnh thng, nu bnh trng va v nh th  mc , nng mc .</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon th gic: Cc bnh l thng gp nh mt lc, c tt khc x nh cn th, nhc th, Hn 50% bnh nhn b ri lon th gic 1 bn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon tinh thn: Khng nhn thng vo b m, thng co git. Tr cng d git mnh, co rm ngi, khng ci v hay cu knh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon thnh gic: Mt s bnh nhi c triu chng gim dn th gic n ic.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nBt c khi no tr c triu chng ri lon vn ng hoc chm pht trin vn ng hy tm n bc s t vn ngay  gii p thc mc v trng lc c, vn ng v phi hp vn ng c. Mi ngi c mt c a khc nhau, bn cn tham kho  kin bc s  c phng n iu tr thch hp. Chn on v iu tr sm s gim nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn nbi no tr em</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>M b nhim trng trong thi k mang thai: Mt s nhim trng thng gp: rubella, virus c bo (nhim trng do siu vi trng nh) v toxoplasmosis (nhim trng do k sinh trng nh). Dn n nguy c gy tn thng no ca bo thai v gy bi no sau ny.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bo thai b thiu kh no: C th do chc nng nhau thai b gim st hoc b bc tch khi thnh t cung trc khi sinh, lm gim lng -xy cung cp cho bo thai.</li>\r\n 	<li>Do sinh non: Nhng a tr sinh non c nguy c xut huyt no rt cao gy tn thng cc t chc ang pht trin ca no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc bin chng trong qu trnh chuyn d v sinh n.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh bt ng nhm mu Rh: L s bt tng hp nhm mu gia m v bo thai c th gy tn thng no dn n bi no. Nhng bnh bt ng nhm mu Rh c th ngn nga trc c bng cch tim vo ngi m mang Rh-m (Rh-negative) mt sn phm mu c gi l Rh immune globulin vo tun th 28 trong thi k mang thai v tim nhc li mt ln na sau khi sinh cho a tr mang Rh-dng (Rh-positive).</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhng d tt bm sinh khc: Bt thng v cu trc no, bnh di truyn, nhim sc th bt thng, v nhng d tt c th khc cng lm tng nguy c mc bnh bi no.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><b>Nhng ai c nguy c</b><strong>b bi no tr em?</strong></h3>\r\nTr d mc bnh bi no khi:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Trong thi k mang thai m b nhim trng hoc mc mt s bnh nh: Rubella; thy u; Cytomegalovirus (virus c bo); Toxoplasmosis; giang mai; bnh v tuyn gip, thiu nng tr tu hoc co git; tip xc vi cht c nh menthyl thy ngn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr mc bnh nh vim mng no do vi khun/ virus; vng da nng hoc vng da lu ngy khng c iu tr vo thi k s sinh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBn c th lm gim kh nng mc bnh bng vic hn ch cc yu t nguy c.\r\n\r\nYu t lm tng nguy cbi no tr em, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sinh non.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr c cn nng khi sinh thp.</li>\r\n 	<li>a thai.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr b chn thng u hoc b nhim trng trong nhng nm u i.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn onbi no tr em</strong></h3>\r\nCc bc s chuyn khoa thng nhn bit c tr b bi no tm sau 6 thng tui, cha m cn lu  tnh trng ca tr v a tr i phc hi sm.\r\n\r\nDo hin nay cha c phng php no chn on chnh xc bnh bi no nn cc bc s phi quan st tr trong thi gian di v thc hin cc xt nghim nh siu m no qua thp, chp CT, o in no , v c bit chp cng hng t MRI cho bit c thng tin v tn thng no.\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr bi no tr em hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nCc tn thng ca no mun c cha lnh hon ton dng nh l iu khng th, nhng chng ta c th gip tr nng cao kh nng tip xc vi th gii thng qua vic phc hi chc nng nh s h tr t gia nh v nhng ngi xung quanh.\r\n\r\nPhc hi chc nng gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vn ng tr liu theo mc vn ng ca tr vi trnh t: Kim sot u c - ly - ngi - qu - b - ng - i - chy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vt l tr liu gip tng sc co c,  linh hot cn bng trong vn ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Luyn giao tip v ngn ng thng qua vic xy dng mi quan h vi ngi khc, bit chi a v giao tip bng c ch, c k nng x hi cn thit, ng thi ph huynh cng cn quan tm n con em mnh nhiu hn, cng ni chuyn vi tr, gip tr ci thin v sm ha nhp.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hun luyn cc k nng cn cho hot ng sng hng ngy nh dng hai tay, n ung, mc , i giy, v sinh c nhn,</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngoi ra tr cng c th c phu thut  gim s cng c v iu chnh bt thng ca xng do lit cng nh phu thut chnh hnh hoc phu thut ct dy thn kinh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMc d y l bnh ko di sut i nhng cng khng din tin tng nng, cng khng lm suy gim tui th ca tr. iu quan trng nht l ph huynh cn lun  bn cnh tr, sn sng h tr v ng vin tr vt qua cc tr ngi. Nu iu tr tt, tr vn c kh nng hc tp v sinh hot vi cng ng.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php phng ngahiu qu</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khng kt hn cn huyt.</li>\r\n 	<li>B m trn 35 tui khng nn sinh thm con v s c nhiu yu t gy tn thng bo thai.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sn ph hn ch nguy c mc cc bnh nhim khun, ng thi khng nn dng cc cht gy nghin hoc kch thch nh ru, thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>B sung vitamin K gn ngy sinh  hn ch mt mu v phng xut huyt no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Quan st tnh hnh vng da ca tr  tr c iu tr sm nu c bt thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr bi no cng cn b sung y  cc cht nh mi tr bnh thng khc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Bi no tr em', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bai-nao-tre-em', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:07:37', '2021-01-30 15:07:37', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=781', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
(782, 1, '2021-01-30 22:06:55', '2021-01-30 15:06:55', '<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\n<div class=\"description\"><strong>Bi no tr em l tn thng no b ca tr khin n khng tin trin c v gy nh hng n s pht trin chc nng vn ng, ngn ng, cm gic</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\n<h3><strong>Bi no tr em l g?</strong></h3>\nBi no tr em l tn thng no b ca tr khin n khng tin trin c v gy nh hng n s pht trin chc nng vn ng, ngn ng, cm gic Biu hin thng thy ca bnh nhi l ri lon vn ng, c th km cc ri lon khc v tr tu, gic quan v hnh vi. Nguyn nhn gy bnh bt ngun t cc yu t tc ng  giai on trc sinh, trong khi sinh v sau sinh n 5 tui. Hin vn cha c phng pho cha tr hon ton chng bi no, nhng ph huynh c th gip tr ci thin kh nng tip cn th gii thng qua s n lc, kin tr v cc hot ng cng tr.\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/6/2018/05/6-bai-nao-tre-em-5128-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"Bi no tr em\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-button-next icon-next\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Next slide\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></div>\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/6/2018/05/6-bai-nao-tre-em-2045-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"Bi no tr em\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca bi no tr em</strong></h3>\nNgi nh bnh nhi cn quan st v nm bt cc triu chng di y sm  kp thi can thip, th c hi phc hi s rt cao.\n<ul>\n 	<li>Ri lon vn ng: Tay chn di chuyn khng nhp nhng, di chuyn b lch hai bn. C th mm ot, t c vn ng t pht.</li>\n 	<li>Ri lon sinh l: C th tr cng , nut khng tt, ng di gic, vng u hnh dng bt thng, vi tr s sinh b khng c lc, thng tr sa, c ming cng, cn nng t tng.</li>\n 	<li>Ri lon ngn ng: Phn ln cc bnh nhn u c biu hin ny. Cc tr b din t kh khn, ngng v ni lp, cng c khi mt ngn ng.</li>\n 	<li>Ri lon tr tu: tr mc bi no tr tu khong bng  ngi bnh thng, nu bnh trng va v nh th  mc , nng mc .</li>\n 	<li>Ri lon th gic: Cc bnh l thng gp nh mt lc, c tt khc x nh cn th, nhc th, Hn 50% bnh nhn b ri lon th gic 1 bn.</li>\n 	<li>Ri lon tinh thn: Khng nhn thng vo b m, thng co git. Tr cng d git mnh, co rm ngi, khng ci v hay cu knh.</li>\n 	<li>Ri lon thnh gic: Mt s bnh nhi c triu chng gim dn th gic n ic.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\nBt c khi no tr c triu chng ri lon vn ng hoc chm pht trin vn ng hy tm n bc s t vn ngay  gii p thc mc v trng lc c, vn ng v phi hp vn ng c. Mi ngi c mt c a khc nhau, bn cn tham kho  kin bc s  c phng n iu tr thch hp. Chn on v iu tr sm s gim nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn nbi no tr em</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>M b nhim trng trong thi k mang thai: Mt s nhim trng thng gp: rubella, virus c bo (nhim trng do siu vi trng nh) v toxoplasmosis (nhim trng do k sinh trng nh). Dn n nguy c gy tn thng no ca bo thai v gy bi no sau ny.</li>\n 	<li>Bo thai b thiu kh no: C th do chc nng nhau thai b gim st hoc b bc tch khi thnh t cung trc khi sinh, lm gim lng -xy cung cp cho bo thai.</li>\n 	<li>Do sinh non: Nhng a tr sinh non c nguy c xut huyt no rt cao gy tn thng cc t chc ang pht trin ca no.</li>\n 	<li>Cc bin chng trong qu trnh chuyn d v sinh n.</li>\n 	<li>Bnh bt ng nhm mu Rh: L s bt tng hp nhm mu gia m v bo thai c th gy tn thng no dn n bi no. Nhng bnh bt ng nhm mu Rh c th ngn nga trc c bng cch tim vo ngi m mang Rh-m (Rh-negative) mt sn phm mu c gi l Rh immune globulin vo tun th 28 trong thi k mang thai v tim nhc li mt ln na sau khi sinh cho a tr mang Rh-dng (Rh-positive).</li>\n 	<li>Nhng d tt bm sinh khc: Bt thng v cu trc no, bnh di truyn, nhim sc th bt thng, v nhng d tt c th khc cng lm tng nguy c mc bnh bi no.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\n<h3><b>Nhng ai c nguy c</b><strong>b bi no tr em?</strong></h3>\nTr d mc bnh bi no khi:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Trong thi k mang thai m b nhim trng hoc mc mt s bnh nh: Rubella; thy u; Cytomegalovirus (virus c bo); Toxoplasmosis; giang mai; bnh v tuyn gip, thiu nng tr tu hoc co git; tip xc vi cht c nh menthyl thy ngn.</li>\n 	<li>Tr mc bnh nh vim mng no do vi khun/ virus; vng da nng hoc vng da lu ngy khng c iu tr vo thi k s sinh.</li>\n</ul>\nBn c th lm gim kh nng mc bnh bng vic hn ch cc yu t nguy c.\n\nYu t lm tng nguy cbi no tr em, bao gm:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Sinh non.</li>\n 	<li>Tr c cn nng khi sinh thp.</li>\n 	<li>a thai.</li>\n 	<li>Tr b chn thng u hoc b nhim trng trong nhng nm u i.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn onbi no tr em</strong></h3>\nCc bc s chuyn khoa thng nhn bit c tr b bi no tm sau 6 thng tui, cha m cn lu  tnh trng ca tr v a tr i phc hi sm.\n\nDo hin nay cha c phng php no chn on chnh xc bnh bi no nn cc bc s phi quan st tr trong thi gian di v thc hin cc xt nghim nh siu m no qua thp, chp CT, o in no , v c bit chp cng hng t MRI cho bit c thng tin v tn thng no.\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr bi no tr em hiu qu</strong></h3>\nCc tn thng ca no mun c cha lnh hon ton dng nh l iu khng th, nhng chng ta c th gip tr nng cao kh nng tip xc vi th gii thng qua vic phc hi chc nng nh s h tr t gia nh v nhng ngi xung quanh.\n\nPhc hi chc nng gm:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Vn ng tr liu theo mc vn ng ca tr vi trnh t: Kim sot u c - ly - ngi - qu - b - ng - i - chy.</li>\n 	<li>Vt l tr liu gip tng sc co c,  linh hot cn bng trong vn ng.</li>\n 	<li>Luyn giao tip v ngn ng thng qua vic xy dng mi quan h vi ngi khc, bit chi a v giao tip bng c ch, c k nng x hi cn thit, ng thi ph huynh cng cn quan tm n con em mnh nhiu hn, cng ni chuyn vi tr, gip tr ci thin v sm ha nhp.</li>\n 	<li>Hun luyn cc k nng cn cho hot ng sng hng ngy nh dng hai tay, n ung, mc , i giy, v sinh c nhn,</li>\n 	<li>Ngoi ra tr cng c th c phu thut  gim s cng c v iu chnh bt thng ca xng do lit cng nh phu thut chnh hnh hoc phu thut ct dy thn kinh.</li>\n</ul>\nMc d y l bnh ko di sut i nhng cng khng din tin tng nng, cng khng lm suy gim tui th ca tr. iu quan trng nht l ph huynh cn lun  bn cnh tr, sn sng h tr v ng vin tr vt qua cc tr ngi. Nu iu tr tt, tr vn c kh nng hc tp v sinh hot vi cng ng.\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\n<h3><strong>Phng php phng ngahiu qu</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Khng kt hn cn huyt.</li>\n 	<li>B m trn 35 tui khng nn sinh thm con v s c nhiu yu t gy tn thng bo thai.</li>\n 	<li>Sn ph hn ch nguy c mc cc bnh nhim khun, ng thi khng nn dng cc cht gy nghin hoc kch thch nh ru, thuc l.</li>\n 	<li>B sung vitamin K gn ngy sinh  hn ch mt mu v phng xut huyt no.</li>\n 	<li>Quan st tnh hnh vng da ca tr  tr c iu tr sm nu c bt thng.</li>\n 	<li>Tr bi no cng cn b sung y  cc cht nh mi tr bnh thng khc.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 'Bi no tr em', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '781-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:06:55', '2021-01-30 15:06:55', '', 781, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/781-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
