(784, 1, '2021-01-30 22:14:03', '2021-01-30 15:14:03', '<h1>Sa st tr tu do mch mu no l g</h1>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Sa st tr tu do mch mu l bnh suy gim chc nng nhn thc bao gm kh nng t duy, ghi nh, ln k hoch, nh gi vn ,... do cc vn  ca mch mu nui no gy ra.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Sa st tr tu do mch mu no l bnh g?</strong></h3>\r\nSa st tr tu mch mu l bnh suy gim chc nng nhn thc bao gm kh nng t duy, ghi nh, ln k hoch, nh gi vn ,... do cc vn  ca mch mu nui no gy ra.\r\n\r\nMt s trng hp mch mu c th hon ton b chn, gy ra t qydn n sa st tr tu mch mu no. Tuy nhin khng phi t qu s dn n sa st tr tu do mch mu no. Ty vo mc  nghim trng ca t qu, v tr t qu v mt phn ca no ca b nh hng m mi c th nhn nh.\r\n\r\nMt nguyn nhn tc ng khc c th k n l mch mu trong no hp, gim s lng lu lng mu n cc phn ca no.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-next icon-next\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Next slide\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/33/2018/05/33-sa-sut-tri-tue-do-mach-mau-nao-3446-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"Sa st tr tu do mch mu no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/33/2018/05/33-sa-sut-tri-tue-do-mach-mau-nao-7042-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"Sa st tr tu do mch mu no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca bnh sa st tr tu do mch mu no</strong></h3>\r\nTy theo vng no b nh hng m ngi bnh c cc biu hin thng thy gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngn ng v tr nh b nh hng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt nh hng, i khng vng v d ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thay i tnh cch v tm trng.</li>\r\n 	<li>L ln, thng bn chn d kch ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gim tp trung.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thng i tiu t ngt.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nDu hiu bnh sa st tr tu do mch mu no rt d nhm ln vi mt s cn bnh khc nn khi ngi bnh c cc biu hin gim st kh nng t duy hoc hnh ng th nn n bnh vin  c bc s thm khm v chn on sm, trnh cc bin chng lu di. Chn on v iu tr sm s gim thiu nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n sa st tr tu do mch mu no</strong></h3>\r\nSa st tr tu do mch mu no c th xut pht t mt s nguyn nhn sau y:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mch mu no hp hoc tt hon ton.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tn thng no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tn thng mch mu no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Huyt p thp.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><b>Nhng ai c nguy c</b><strong>b sa st tr tu do mch mu no?</strong></h3>\r\nBnh thng xut hin   tui trn 65, ngi   tui cao hn s b nng hn.\r\n\r\nYu t lm tng nguy c sa st tr tu do mch mu no, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cao huyt p, cholesterol cao v ht thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tin s bt qu.</li>\r\n 	<li>X va ng mch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tiu ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ht thuc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn on sa st tr tu do mch mu no</strong></h3>\r\nCc bc s s da trn thng tin bnh s, tin s t qu hoc cc vn  tim v mch mu  chn on. ng thi thc hin cc xt nghim b sung nh: chp CT, chp MRI, chp cc lp pht x positron...  pht hin cc bt thng ca mch mu no hoc phn no khng hot ng bng hnh nh. Ngoi ra siu m Doppler gip xc nh on mch mu no b tc nghn hoc hp.\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr sa st tr tu do mch mu no hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nHin cha c bin php cha tr dt im, tuy nhin bnh nhn c th c iu tr gim bt cc triu chng. C th k n nh cc thuc iu tr bnh Alzheimer nh cht c ch cholinesterase (Donepezil, Galantamine, Rivastigmine), memantine (Namenda) cng rt c ch cho ngi b tnh trng ny.\r\n\r\nTy vo th trng v tnh trng bnh m bc s s k n thuc v p dng nhng phng php iu tr ph hp cho bnh nhn.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca bnh sa st tr tu do mch mu no</strong></h3>\r\n<em>Ch  sinh hot:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tun th theo cc hng dn ca bc s trong vic iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thm khm nh k  c theo di tnh trng sc khe, din tin ca bnh v  bc s tm hng iu tr ph hp trong thi gian tip theo nu bnh cha c du hiu thuyn gim.</li>\r\n 	<li>S ng vin ca ngi thn c th gip bnh nhn c li sng lc quan, tch cc hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>To mi trng sng trong sch, yn tnh, an ton  gip bnh nhn hn ch s lo lng v kch ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lin h ngay vi bc s khi c nhng c th c nhng bt thng trong qu trnh iu tr.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Ch  dinh dng:</em>\r\n\r\nDuy tr ch  n lnh mnh v  cht. n tri cy ti, rau v cung cp axit bo omega-3 (thng c trong c vng nc lnh nh c hi, cc trch, c mi,... v cc loi ht).\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng phng php phng bnh hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gi huyt p  mc bnh thng, n nh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngn nga, kim sotbnh tiu ngbng cch n ung v tp th dc hp l, nng cao sc khe. Nu bnh nhn mc tiu ng th nn kim sot lng ng trong mu n mc hp l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gi mc cholesterol bnh thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng ht thuc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Sa st tr tu do mch mu no', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sa-sut-tri-tue-do-mach-mau-nao-la-gi', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:14:03', '2021-01-30 15:14:03', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=784', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
