(786, 1, '2021-01-30 22:18:42', '2021-01-30 15:18:42', '<h2>Ung th tuyn nc bt l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Ung th tuyn nc bt l cn bnh tng i him gp, thuc khu vc u c. Cc tuyn nc bt c nhim v chnh l tit nc bt gip ming m v gip thc n d dng i xung thc qun vo d dy.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Ung th tuyn nc bt l g?</strong></h3>\r\nUng th tuyn nc bt l cn bnh tng i him gp, thuc khu vc u c. Cc tuyn nc bt c nhim v chnh l tit nc bt gip ming m v gip thc n d dng i xung thc qun vo d dy. Cc tuyn nc bt ln nht l:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tuyn di li - nm bn di li.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tuyn mang tai - hai bn ca ming ngay trc tai.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tuyn di xng hm di - nm di xng hm.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngoi ra cn c nhiu tuyn nh hn trong nim mc ming v c hng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nUng th tuyn nc bt l mt dng ung th c th bt u t bt c ni no ca tuyn nc bt nh  tuyn nc bt mang tai, tuyn nc bt di li, tuyn nc bt xng hm. Tuy nhin bnh thng xy ra  cc tuyn mang tai - pha trc ca tai.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/322/2018/06/322-ung-thu-tuyen-nuoc-bot-6318-5b18.jpg\" alt=\"Ung th tuyn nc bt\" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/322/2018/06/322-ung-thu-tuyen-nuoc-bot-7724-5b18.jpg\" alt=\"Ung th tuyn nc bt\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca ung th tuyn nc bt</strong></h3>\r\nNhng triu chng ban u ca ung th tuyn nc bt thng khng r rng. Cc du hiu v triu chng c th bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sng trn hoc gn hm hoc  c hoc ming;</li>\r\n 	<li>T mt phn ca khun mt;</li>\r\n 	<li>C bp yu  mt bn mt;</li>\r\n 	<li>au dai dng trong khu vc ca mt tuyn nc bt;</li>\r\n 	<li>Kh nut;</li>\r\n 	<li>Kh h to ming.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nHy n gp bc s ngay khi c cc triu chng k trn trong mt thi gian. Nu c mt ln sng hoc gn khu vc ca tuyn nc bt l mt du hiu ph bin ca mt khi u tuyn nc bt, nhng cn phn bit rng iu  khng c ngha l b ung th. Chn on v iu tr sm s gim thiu nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\r\n\r\nMi ngi mt c a khc nhau, bn cn tham kho  kin chuyn gia  c phng n iu tr thch hp. Vic t iu tr m khng c s hng dn ca bc s chuyn khoa c th dn n nhng tn thng nguy him khc.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n ung th tuyn nc bt</strong></h3>\r\nCc bc s hin nay vn khng r nguyn nhn gy bnh ung th tuyn nc bt l g. Tuy nhin bnh ung th tuyn nc bt xy ra khi c t bin ADN  cc t bo tuyn nc bt v pht trin ln mnh, xm ln, tiu dit cc t bo lnh tnh khc. Cc t bin cho php cc t bo pht trin v phn chia nhanh chng. Cc t bo t bin tip tc sng khi cc t bo khc s cht, n tch t thnh mt khi u c th xm nhp vo m ln cn. Cc t bo ung th c th v ra v ly lan ti cc vng xa ca c th.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy c b ung th tuyn nc bt?</strong></h3>\r\nBnh ung th tuyn nc bt c th nh hng mi ngi trong mi la tui. Tuy nhin bn c th kim sot c bng cch gim thiu cc yu t nguy c gy bnh.\r\n\r\nYu t lm tng nguy c mc bnh, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ung ru, ht thuc: nhng ngi ung ru, ht thuc c nguy c mc phi cao gp nhiu ln nhng ngi khng ung ru, ht thuc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tui tc: Bnh thng c chn on  ngi ln tui,  tui t 55  65.</li>\r\n 	<li>Phi nhim bc x, chng hn nh bc x c s dng  iu tr ung th u v c. Di bc x mnh, chng hn nh c s dng trong chn on X-quang, cng c th lm tng nguy c mc phi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ni lm vic tip xc vi cc cht nht nh nh cc hp kim niken v bi silica.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn on ung thtuyn nc bt</strong></h3>\r\nCc bc s c th chn on ung th tuyn nc bt bng cch:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chn on xc nh: Khai thc k tin s, c im v v tr ca u.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chn on phn bit vi u lnh tnh ca tuyn mang tai.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khm lm sng: Bc s s khm cc khi sng vng hm, c v hng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khm cn lm sng:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chp ng tuyn nc bt: S thy c hnh nh chn p i vi u lnh hoc ct ct i vi ung th.</li>\r\n 	<li>Siu m:  xc nh c u c hay u nang.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chp ct lp v cng hng t khi nghi ng u xm ln vo h chn bm hm hoc y vo thnh bn hng hay xm ln xng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chc t bo hc: Pht hin c u c hay u nang, c gi tr khi (+).</li>\r\n 	<li>Sinh thit: Ch sinh thit khi no u xm ln ra da hoc khng cn ch nh phu thut.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr ung thtuyn nc bt hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nVic iu tr ung th tuyn nc bt cn ph thuc vo kch c khi u, giai on pht hin ra bnh cng nh sc khe tng th v iu kin ca ngi bnh.\r\n\r\n<em>Phu thut ung th tuyn nc bt</em>\r\n\r\nGm cc phng php:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ct b mt phn ca tuyn nc bt b nh hng nu ung th nh v nm trong ti mt ch d dng truy cp.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ct b ton b cc tuyn nc bt nu mt khi u ln hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ct b cc hch bch huyt  c nu c bng chng cho thy ung th  lan n cc hch bch huyt  c.</li>\r\n 	<li>Phu thut ti to nu xng, da hoc dy thn kinh b loi b trong qu trnh phu thut. C th cn phi ghp m, da hoc dy thn kinh t cc b phn khc ca c th  xy dng li cc khu vc  c hng, ming hoc hm.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKhi phu thut cng cn phi ch  song song vic bo tn cc dy thn kinh  khu vc gn ni phu thut  trnh lm nh hng n nhng vng c th khc.\r\n\r\n<em>X tr ung th tuyn nc bt</em>\r\n\r\nS dng cung cp nng lng cao dm, nh X-quang,  tiu dit t bo ung th. Liu php bc x c th c s dng sau khi phu thut  git bt k t bo ung th c th vn cn.\r\n\r\n<em>Ha tr ung th tuyn nc bt</em>\r\n\r\niu tr bng thuc c s dng ha cht  tiu dit t bo ung th. y l mt la chn cho nhng ngi b bnh ung th tuyn nc bt  lan rng n cc vng xa ca c th.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca ung thtuyn nc bt</strong></h3>\r\nTun th theo cc hng dn ca bc s trong vic iu tr.\r\n\r\nThm khm nh k  c theo di tnh trng sc khe, din tin ca bnh v  bc s tm hng iu tr ph hp trong thi gian tip theo nu bnh c du hiu ti pht.\r\n\r\nDuy tr li sng tch cc, hn ch s cng thng.\r\n\r\nBnh nhn cn lc quan. Tm l c nh hng rt ln n iu tr, hy ni chuyn vi nhng ngi ng tin cy, chia s vi nhng thnh vin trong gia nh, nui th cng hay n gin l c sch, lm bt c th g khin bn thy thoi mi.\r\n\r\nNhng ngi tri qua x tr vng u v c thng b kh ming gy kh chu, c th dn n nhim trng thng xuyn trong ming, su rng, cc vn  v rng, kh n, kh nut v ni. Bn c th lm gim kh ming v cc bin chng khi:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>nh rng nhiu ln mi ngy. Nn s dng bn chi lng mn  chi rng nh nhng nhiu ln mi ngy v bo vi bc s nu ming tr nn qu nhy cm ngay c khi nh rng nh nhng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sc ming bng nc mui m sau ba n.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gi m ming bng nc hoc ko khng ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trnh cc loi thc phm v  ung c tnh acid hoc nhiu gia v.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trnh s dng  ung c cha caffeine v cn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chn thc phm m, trnh cc loi thc phm kh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng phng php phng bnh hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nNhng ngi lm vic trong mi trng phi nhim bc x, ngi thng xuyn tip xc vi cc cht nh niken, bi silica rt d b ung th tuyn nc bt. Nn vi nhng ngi c nguy c cao th cn kim tra sc khe nh k ti cc bnh vin c chuyn khoa ung bu,  pht hin sm u tuyn nc bt. Ngoi ra vi nhng ngi c thi quen xu nn t b thuc l v ru bia ng thi v sinh rng ming t nht 2 ln mi ngy.\r\n\r\nUng th l cn bnh nguy him nhng khng c ngha l bnh khng th iu tr c. iu quan trng nht trong vic chng li ung th chnh l ngi bnh cn c thi  lc quan v kin tr iu tr bnh. Thc t cho thy, nhng ngi c thi  sng tch cc kt hp vi phng php iu tr hp l  ko di c tui th v chng li c cn bnh ung th.\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Ung th tuyn nc bt', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ung-thu-tuyen-nuoc-bot', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:18:42', '2021-01-30 15:18:42', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=786', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
