(788, 1, '2021-01-30 22:22:59', '2021-01-30 15:22:59', '<h2>Phnh ng mch no l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Phnh ng mch no l hin tng mch mu trong no b phnh to, trng ging nh mt qu mng treo trn cy. ng mch no b v do phnh to l bnh l nguy him cn c cp cu kp thi. Tuy nhin khng phi ng mch no no b phnh cng s b v. iu ng tic l cc ti phnh nh khi cha v thng khng c triu chng nn rt kh nhn bit bnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phinh ng mach nao la gi?</strong></h3>\r\nPhnh ng mch no l hin tng mch mu trong no b phnh to, trng ging nh mt qu mng treo trn cy. Thng thng, ti phnh ng mch no thng nm  v tr gian gi hoc mng no. Phn thnh ng mch ch ti phnh b mng, d b r r hoc b v gy xut huyt no v e da n tnh mng.\r\n\r\nng mch no b v do phnh to l bnh l nguy him cn c cp cu kp thi. Tuy nhin khng phi ng mch no no b phnh cng s b v. iu ng tic l cc ti phnh nh khi cha v thng khng c triu chng nn rt kh nhn bit bnh.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/306/2018/12/306-phinh-dong-mach-nao-8389-5c05.jpg\" alt=\"Phnh ng mch no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/306/2018/12/306-phinh-dong-mach-nao-1169-5c05.jpg\" alt=\"Phnh ng mch no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/306/2018/12/306-phinh-dong-mach-nao-1641-5c05.jpg\" alt=\"Phnh ng mch no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu va triu chng cua phinh ng mch nao</strong></h3>\r\nTy thuc vo tng giai on m bnh c du hiu khc nhau.\r\n\r\n<em>1. Ti phnh v s c cc du hiu bao gm:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>t ngt au u d di, cn au thng din ra t ngt;</li>\r\n 	<li>Bun nn v nn;</li>\r\n 	<li>C cng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhn m hoc nhn i;</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhy cm vi nh sng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Co git;</li>\r\n 	<li>Sp mi;</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt  thc;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ln ln.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>2. Ti phnh r r:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>t ngt au u d di;</li>\r\n 	<li>Tnh trng v ti phnh lun nng hn sau khi b r r.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>3. Ti phnh cha v:</em>\r\n\r\nTi phnh cha v c th khng gy ra triu chng, c bit nu n nh. Tuy nhin ti phnh cha v ln c th gy ra cc triu chng nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>au  trn v pha sau mt;</li>\r\n 	<li>Gin ng t;</li>\r\n 	<li>Thay i th lc hoc nhn i;</li>\r\n 	<li>T, yu hoc lit mt bn mt;</li>\r\n 	<li>Sp mi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Bin chng co th gp do phinh ng mch nao</strong></h3>\r\nPhnh ng mch no c th gy ra cc bin chng nguy him nh:\r\n\r\n<em>Chy mu li:</em>Phnh ng mch  v hoc r r c nguy c chy mu mt ln na. Chy mu li c th gy thit hi thm cho cc t bo no.\r\n\r\n<em>Co tht mch:</em>Sau v do phnh ng mch no, mch mu trong no c th gian rng v hp tht thng. Tnh trng ny c th gii hn lu lng mu n cc t bo no (t qu thiu mu cc b) v gy thit hi t bo thm.\r\n\r\n<em>No ng thy:</em>Tnh trng ny c th dn n trn dch no, dch no ty lm tng p lc ln no v c th thit hi m nao.\r\n\r\n<em>Gim natri mu:</em>C th gy phu cc t bo no v tn thng vnh vin.\r\n<h3><strong>Khi nao cn gp bac si?</strong></h3>\r\nPhnh ng mch no l mt bnh l nguy him, trong trng hp ng mch b v do phnh th nguy c t vong s rt cao. V vy, khi bn thy cc triu chng trn xy ra, hoc khi cn nhc u ca bn xut hin ngy cng nhiu hay xut hin bt ng nhng rt d di, hy nh s tr gip ca nhng ngi xung quanh v n gp bc s  kim tra, trnh bin chng nguy him.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn nphinh ng mch nao</strong></h3>\r\nPhnh ng mch no hnh thnh do thnh ng mch mng hoc do thoi ha; thng xy ra  ng ba hay ch chia ca ng mch v nhng phn mch mu ny yu hn. Mc d chng phnh ng mch c th xut hin  bt c v tr no trong no nhng ph bin hn  khu vc y no.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy c bphinh ng mch nao?</strong></h3>\r\nBnh c th xut hin  mi la tui. Tuy nhin, tui cng cao nguy c mc bnh cng ln v ph n c t l mc bnh cao hn nam gii.\r\n\r\nCc yu t lm tng nguy c mc bnh bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gia nh tng c ngi mc bnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh ti phnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>X cng ng mch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lm dng thuc, nht l cocain.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chng tc: ngi M gc Phi c nhiu kh nng b xut huyt di mng nhn hn ngi da trng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Huyt p cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ht thuc l, ung nhiu ru.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chn thng u.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mc mt s ri lon lc mi sinh nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon di truyn m lin kt: lm suy yu mch mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh thn a nang: thng lm tng huyt p.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hp bt thng ng mch ch: hn ch dng mu giu oxy cung cp t tim n cc c quan trong c th.</li>\r\n 	<li>D tt ng tnh mch no: kt ni bt thng gia cc ng mch v tnh mch trong no lm gin on dng chy bnh thng ca mu</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNguy him nht l khi ch ng mch phnh b v, c khong 50% trng hp v ng mch dn n t vong. Mt s yu t gy v ti phnh bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tp th dc qu sc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng c ph hoc soda.</li>\r\n 	<li>Co tht rut.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gin d.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sc nng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Quan h tnh dc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng phap xet nghim va chn oanphinh ng mch nao</strong></h3>\r\nBc s chn on chng phnh ng mch no bng cch xem xt cc triu chng m bnh nhn gp phi, khm lm sng. Nu c cc du hiu ca phnh ng mch no, bc s s tin hnh mt s xt nghim  xc nh nguyn nhn v nhng tn thng no b.\r\n\r\nBc s chn on da vo mt s xt nghim sau:\r\n\r\n<em>Chp ct lp vi tnh (CT scan):</em>Vic ny thng lm u tin  xem c mu chy trong no hay khng. Nu c bc s s tin hnh cc xt nghim khc  xc nh nguyn nhn c phi do phnh ng mch no gy ra hay khng.\r\n\r\n<em>Kim tra dch no ty:</em>Xt nghim ny khng km phn quan trng so vi chp CT v c th mt s v tr CT khng th chp li c. Thng thng, nu phnh ng mch no s c xut huyt di mng nhn (chy mu vo khu vc khoang trng,  gia no v lp mng bao ph no). Khi chc dch bao quanh no v ty sng (dch no ty) s pht hin thy hng cu.\r\n\r\n<em>Chp cng hng t mch mu (MRI):</em>MRI s cung cp hnh nh r rng hn CT, c th lam ro net hnh nh ca mch mu v cc tn thng ca chng phnh ng mch v.\r\n\r\n<em>Chp mch no:</em>Nu cc xt nghim khc khng cung cp  thng tin, chp mch no c th c thc hin. Phng php ny tit l chi tit v cc vn  ca cc ng mch v tn thng ca chng phnh ng mch v. y cng l cch tt nht  xc nh v tr cc phnh mch nh hn 5mm.\r\n<h3><strong>Phng phap iu triphinh ng mch nao hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nTy vo tnh trng sc khe ca ngi bnh, kch thc, v tr v mc  nghim trng ca ti phnh  v hay r r cha, bc s s k n thuc v p dng nhng phng php iu tr ph hp.\r\n\r\nDo c rt nhiu ri ro khi tc ng n cc ng mch b phnh nn trong trng hp phnh ng mch no n nh, bc s s  ngh tip tc theo di tnh trng v din tin ca bnh ch khng yu cu phu thut ngay. Trng hp ng mch no c kch thc ln,  b v, gy au n d di hoc gy nhng triu chng khc, c th bn s c ch nh phu thut.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin caphinh ng mch nao</strong></h3>\r\nNu bn c ng mch no b phnh nhng cha v, bn c th gim nguy c v ca n bng cc phng php sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>B ht thuc hoc cc cht kch thch nh ru, ma ty. Nu bn khng th t b, hy tham kho  kin bc s v nhng chng trnh cai nghin.</li>\r\n 	<li>n mt ch  n nhiu tri cy, rau, ng cc nguyn ht, tht nc v cc sn phm t sa t cht bo. ng thi hn ch dng caffeine.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tp th dc thng xuyn nhng khng qu sc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Theo di huyt p cao hoc cholesterol cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hy thn trng khi s dng aspirin. Tt nht bn nn tham kho  kin bc s trc khi dng aspirin hay cc thuc gy c ch ng mu bi v c th lm tng mt mu khi phnh ng mch b v.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Phnh ng mch no', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'phinh-dong-mach-nao', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:22:59', '2021-01-30 15:22:59', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=788', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
