(790, 1, '2021-01-30 22:25:21', '2021-01-30 15:25:21', '<h2>Ri lon tun hon no l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Ri lon tun hon no hay cn gi l thiu nng tun hon no l tn gi chung  ch nhiu biu hin khc nhau nhng u do mt c ch sinh bnh l thiu mu nui no. Ri lon tun hon mu no xy ra khi lng mu lu thng n no khng  khin no b thiu oxy  hot ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Ri loan tun hoan nao la gi?</strong></h3>\r\nTun hon no l qu trnh lu thng ca mu ln no, gip cc t bo trong no hot ng n nh. Mc d nh nhng no l c quan quan trng, cn khong 15% mu t tim  c  oxy v glucose p ng cho cc chc nng ca no.\r\n\r\nRi lon tun hon no hay cn gi l thiu nng tun hon no l tn gi chung  ch nhiu biu hin khc nhau nhng u do mt c ch sinh bnh l thiu mu nui no. Ri lon tun hon mu no xy ra khi lng mu lu thng n no khng  khin no b thiu oxy  hot ng, dn n tnh trng cht m no hoc nhi mu no hay cn gi l t qu.\r\n\r\nBnh thng gp  la tui trung nin v ngi cao tui, ngi lao ng tr c. Bn cnh , t l mc bnh  nam gii cao hn n.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/602/2018/12/602-roi-loan-tuan-hoan-nao-7258-5c05.jpg\" alt=\"Ri lon tun hon no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-prev\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/602/2018/12/602-roi-loan-tuan-hoan-nao-3991-5c05.jpg\" alt=\"Ri lon tun hon no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/602/2018/12/602-roi-loan-tuan-hoan-nao-1546-5c05.jpg\" alt=\"Ri lon tun hon no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu va triu chng cua ri loan tun hoan nao</strong></h3>\r\nKhi h thng tun hon no b tn thng do mt s tc nhn no , mc oxy v glucose cung cp ln no s t hn lng cn thit. iu ny c th lm tn thng no v gy ra cc vn  v thn kinh. Di y l mt s tnh trng thng gp khi tun hon no b suy yu:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhn bn ngoi: km nhanh nhn; km theo c nho, nim mc kh, tc rng.</li>\r\n 	<li>au u: au lan ta, c tnh co tht hoc khu tr vng chm gy - trn. au tng khi cng thng thn kinh; cm gic nng n, u m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon cm gic: au tay chn v ton thn, au k lin sn, chut rt, ri lon thn kinh thc vt, cm gic kin b, t 1/2 ngi, tai  nh c ting ve ku, nng u.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thc th: run cc ngn tay khi a tay thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhng triu chng tiu biu:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon gic ng: mt ng, gim cht lng gic ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon s ch : gim s ch , hay ng tr hoc ch ch  n mt vic no  m khng cn ph hp vi hon cnh lc  na.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon tri gic: kh nng nghe gim hn, hp th trng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon tr nh: gim tr nh gn, kh nng sp xp li theo trnh t gim,  ngh ln xn, nhm.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon xc cm: d cu, d xc ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Bin chng co th gp do ri loan tun hoan nao</strong></h3>\r\nBnh ri lon tun hon no nu khng c iu tr sm s gy ra cc bin chng nng nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>t qu: Nu trong ng mch c huyt khi, n c th lm tc dng chy ca mu ln no dn n t qu, cc m no  cc khu vc b nh hng s cht. iu ny dn n mt s chc nng do cc m no  cht kim sot cng khng cn hot ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Xut huyt no: Khi b d dng mch mu, ri lon ng mu, chn thng u hay thnh ng mch b suy yu, sau  nt hoc v c th lm mu chy ra bn ngoi mch mu gy tnh trng chy mu bn trong khoang s. Xut huyt c th gia tng p lc ln khoang s v lm mt  thc ngi bnh. Nguy c t vong l rt ln.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ph no: Ph no xy ra khi cht dch trong khoang no gia tng, n cng gy p lc ln no v c nguy c lm tn thng hay ph hy ton b no.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi nao cn gp bac si?</strong></h3>\r\nNu c bt k triu chng no nu trn xy ra, bn nn lin h ngay vi bc s  c kim tra v t vn. Chn on v iu tr sm s gim nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><b>Nguyn nhn dn n ri lon tun hon no</b></h3>\r\nNguyn nhn gy ri lon tun hon no bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thiu mu hng cu hnh lim.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mch mu b  nn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhp nhanh tht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tc nghn ng mch do tch t mng x va.</li>\r\n 	<li>au tim.</li>\r\n 	<li>D tt tim bm sinh, d tt bm sinh  ng mch.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><b>Nhng ai c nguy c mc phiri lon tun hon no?</b></h3>\r\nCc ri lon tun hon no c th xy ra  bt c  tui no, tuy nhin ph n trn 50 tui c nguy c mc bnh cao hn.\r\n\r\nCc yu t lm tng nguy c mc bnh bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Huyt p cao;</li>\r\n 	<li>Cholesterol cao;</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh tim;</li>\r\n 	<li>X va ng mch;</li>\r\n 	<li>Tin s gia nh mc bnh tim;</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh i tho ng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Bo ph;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ht thuc l;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung ru.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng phap xet nghim va chn oan</strong><b>ri lon tun hon no</b></h3>\r\nBc s chn on da vo khm lm sng, tin s bnh l v thng qua cc xt nghim nh: xt nghim mu hoc mt s xt nghim hnh nh nh X-quang  quan st r hn nhng tn thng v bin i  tim v mch mu.\r\n<h3><b>Phng php iu tr ri lon tun hon no hiu qu</b></h3>\r\nCc phng php iu tr bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>S dng Alteplase (tpa) l mt trong nhng loi thuc c hiu qu i vi t qu thiu mu cc b cp.</li>\r\n 	<li>Duy tr huyt p  lu lng mu no c th phc hi v hn ch tnh trng thiu oxy v tng carbonic trong mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>K thuc chng co git cho bn  phng nga khi bn b ng kinh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch tng huyt p.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin cari lon tun hon no</strong></h3>\r\nCc bin php gip kim sot ri lon tun hon no bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>B thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tp th dc.</li>\r\n 	<li>iu tr cc tnh trng nh cao huyt p cao v i tho ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>n ch  n ung lnh mnh bao gm cc loi tri cy, rau v ng cc nguyn ht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nu bn c nguy c b ri lon tun hon mu, hy theo di tnh trng sc khe thng xuyn bng vic n gp bc s nh k.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Ri lon tun hon no', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'roi-loan-tuan-hoan-nao', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:25:21', '2021-01-30 15:25:21', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=790', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
