(792, 1, '2021-01-30 22:32:11', '2021-01-30 15:32:11', '<h2>U no l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">U no l khi u hnh thnh do s tng trng bt thng ca cc t bo bn trong no. Khi u  c th l lnh tnh hoc c tnh (ung th). D trong trng hp no th khi u vn c kh nng e da tnh mng ca bn nu khng c pht hin sm  iu tr. Triu chng ca bnh u no thng khng r rng, cc biu hin cng khc nhau  tng ngi v ty vo v tr, kch thc ca khi u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<strong>U no l g?</strong>\r\n\r\nU no l khi u hnh thnh do s tng trng bt thng ca cc t bo bn trong no. Khi u  c th l lnh tnh hoc c tnh (ung th). D trong trng hp no th khi u vn c kh nng e da tnh mng ca bn nu khng c pht hin sm  iu tr. Triu chng ca bnh u no thng khng r rng, cc biu hin cng khc nhau  tng ngi v ty vo v tr, kch thc ca khi u. Biu hin d dng nhn bit nht  l nhng thay i ca c th gn lin vi hot ng ca no nh nhc u, bun nn, suy gim nhn thc, th lc v thnh lc,... Dng phng php phu thut ct b khi u, x tr, ha tr c th ci thin tnh trng bnh nhng bn cnh  cn c s phi hp ca bnh nhn  kh nng phc hi cao hn.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-next icon-next\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Next slide\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/285/2018/12/285-u-nao-1817-5c22.jpg\" alt=\"U no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/285/2018/12/285-u-nao-9100-5c22.jpg\" alt=\"U no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/285/2018/12/285-u-nao-8469-5c22.jpg\" alt=\"U no\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca u no</strong></h3>\r\nTriu chng ca bnh u no thng khng r rng, cc biu hin cng khc nhau  tng ngi v ty vo v tr, kch thc ca khi u. Tuy nhin, cc triu chng in hnh ca bnh u no thng l:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>ng kinh, co git hay thm ch l b co tht cnh tay, bp chn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Suy gim nhn thc: Mt tr nh, kh tp trung suy ngh hay tc  x l ca no chm li. Bn canh o nhng cn nhc u cung la nguyn nhn gy nn tinh trang trn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Suy yu th lc v thnh gic: Gp gp trc trc vi tm nhn nh nhn thy nh n nhp nhy, m, v nhng ht li ti ni ln trc mt.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Bin chng c th gp khi mc u no</strong></h3>\r\nMt s bin chng t u no, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thot v no do p lc hp s tng cao; v sau  dn ti tim ngng p v p lc hp s  ln h tun hon mu. Trng hp ny dn n kh nng t vong rt cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gim th lc: Mc d bin chng ny t gp nhng vn khng phi l khng c. c bit l ngi ln tui, u no thng km theo cc nh hng v mt. Nu khng iu tr vn c nguy c m vnh vin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bi lit: Thi gian u c th lit nh, nhng sau c th dn n lit na ngi hoc ton thn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Xut huyt no: Thng khng c triu chng c bit nu xut huyt t. Nhng nu xut huyt nhiu c th km theo hin tng p lc ni s tng cao, khng th ni chuyn, lit, mt  thc v nghim trng nht l t vong t ngt.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nU no nh hng rt ln n tnh mng. V th, ngay khi bn pht hin bt k triu chng no bn trn th hy n gp bc s  c kim tra v xc nh bnh. Chn on v iu tr sm s gim thiu nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n u no</strong></h3>\r\nU no bt ngun t chnh bn thn no hoc trong cc m gn n, chng hn nh trong no - bao gm mng no, dy thn kinh s, tuyn yn hoc tuyn tng. U no tin pht bt u khi cc t bo bnh thng c cc li (t bin) trong DNA. Nhng t bin ny cho php t bo pht trin, phn chia  mc tng v tip tc sng khi t bo khe mnh cht. Kt qu l khi lng ca t bo bt thng to thnh mt khi u.\r\n\r\nU no tin pht t ph bin hn l u no th pht, trong  ung th bt u  ni khc v lan truyn n no.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy c mc u no?</strong></h3>\r\nBt c ai cng c th c nguy c mc bnh u no. Tuy nhin,  tui 70 l  tui hay gp u no nht.Yu t lm tng nguy c mc u no, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chng tc: Bnh thng gp  ngi da trng nhiu hn so vi nhng chng tc khc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tui tc: Nguy c mc bnh tng ln theo  tui, thng xy ra  ngi ln tui, c bit l  ngoi tui 70. Tuy nhin, u no c th xy ra  mi la tui</li>\r\n 	<li>Tin s gia nh: Nhng ngi c tin s gia nh c ngi mc bnh u no hoc tin s mc cc bnh ri lon di truyn nhim sc th.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tip xc vi bc x: Nhng ngi lm vic trong mi trng phng x, b phi nhim bc x gy ra bi bom nguyn t hay tr liu phng x  iu tr ung th, u c nguy c mc bnh cao hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thng xuyn tip xc vi ha cht: Nhng ngi lm vic trong mi trng cng nghip ha cht s lm tng nguy c mc bnh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn on u no</strong></h3>\r\nChp ct lp s no hoc cng hng t vi thuc i quang t gado - linium c th pht hin c tn thng cng nh v tr, hnh dng v kch thc ca khi u; s bin dng ca cu trc gii phu bnh thng; mc  ph no v hiu ng chon ch. Chp ct lp s no t c gi tr trong pht hin cc u h sau nhng cng hng t rt c gi tr trong pht hin u  v tr ny. Tnh cht ngm thuc cn quang ca u mng no c gi tr chn on, v d rih u  v tr in hnh (cnh ng dc gia v vng khe Sylvius, rnh khu, mo xng bm, c yn) khi u xut hin ng nht, tng t trng trn phim chp ct lp khng tim thuc cn quang v sau tim thuc th ngm thuc khng ng nht. y la mt trong nhng phng phap xet nghm, chun oan chinh xac nht.\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr u no hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nPhu thut ct b khi u. Tuy nhin, no l b phn quan trng v cc k nhy cm. Phu thut ct b ch c th tin hnh thun li khi khi u c ranh gii r rng v nm  v tr thun li  phu thut.\r\n\r\nX tr c th c p dng  tiu dit phn cn li ca khi u khng c ct b ht.\r\n\r\nNu khi u nm su trong no, bc s s dng tia gamma vi  tp trung cao  loi b chng.\r\n\r\nHa tr dng  iu tr trc hoc sau phu thut v x tr (trong trng hp khi u ln, kh phu thut,). Liu lng, cch s dng ha cht s cn tun theo phc  iu tr, ph hp vi bn cht m bnh hc v la tui.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin cau no</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tun th theo cc hng dn ca bc s trong vic iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thm khm nh k  c theo di tnh trng sc khe, din tin ca bnh v  bc s tm hng iu tr ph hp trong thi gian tip theo nu bnh c du hiu ti pht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Duy tr li sng tch cc, hn ch s cng thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh nhn cn lc quan. Tm l c nh hng rt ln n iu tr, hy ni chuyn vi nhng ngi ng tin cy, chia s vi nhng thnh vin trong gia nh, nui th cng hay n gin l c sch, lm bt c th g khin bn thy thoi mi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi bnh u nao nn co mt thc n n ung iu n va chinh xac nht t bac si  co mt sc khoe tt, cai thin tinh trang bnh. Sau y la mt s cht dinh dng ngi bnh cn b sung trong qua trinh dng bnh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Acid folic: Nu bn nhn c  axit folic trong ch  n ung ca bn, n s gip cho bnh u no ly lan chm hn. Mi ngy bnh nhn u no cn cung cp cho c th t nht 400mg acid folic. Ngoi vic b sung bng vitamin tng hp c th b sung bng cc loi thc phm nh: rau bina hoc ti hn mu xanh l cy, rau l xanh, cam, go, v u</li>\r\n 	<li>Cht chng oxy ha: Cc loi thc phm c mt s lng cao cht chng oxy ha, c bit n  chng li v ngn nga u no. Thc phm cha cht chng oxy ha cao nh: qu vit qut, du ty v nho, cam qut, to,... Cc loi tri cy cng ti, s dng ngay sau khi thu hoch s cha hm lng cht chng oxy ha cao nht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Omega-3: C th c tm thy trong c, omega-3 khng ch chng li bnh ung th bng cch gim tc  tng trng ca khi u, m cn c tc dng tng cng h thng min dch trong c th. Nu bn c th gip cho h thng min dch khe mnh c th bn c th chng li cc t bo ung th tt hn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php phng nga hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nBn nn tp cc thi quen tt, li sng lnh mnh nh l:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gi gn v sinh an ton thc phm  hn ch cc loi giun, sng c trong thc phm bn.</li>\r\n 	<li>B sung cc cht cn thit cho c th, tng cng n rau xanh v hn ch cc mn chin nhiu du m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng ung ru, bia, ht thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung  2 lt nc mi ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch ht phi cc kh c hi. Nu phi lm vic trong mi trng c ho cht c hi phi trang b cc dng c, trang phc bo h cn thit.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tng cng vn ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Quan trng hn l bn phi ng  8 ting mi ngy  c th c ngh ngi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'U no', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'u-nao', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:32:11', '2021-01-30 15:32:11', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=792', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
