(794, 1, '2021-01-30 22:35:04', '2021-01-30 15:35:04', '<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Bi lit l g</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"description\">Bi lit l mt bnh truyn nhim do virus Poliovirus gy nn.  dng nng nht ca n gy ra t lit, kh th v i khi mt mng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Bi lit l g?</strong></h3>\r\nBi lit l mt bnh truyn nhim do virus poliovirus gy nn.  dng nng nht ca n gy ra t lit, kh th v i khi mt mng.\r\n\r\nBnh bi lit c chia thnh 3 loi: khng in hnh, th khng lit v th lit. Bnh bi lit c th l mt dng bnh nh, nh dng bi lit khng lin quan n h thn kinh trung ng, nhng cng c th l dng bnh rt nghim trng, nh th lit. Hu ht cc bnh nhn b nhim bnh c th khng biu hin triu chng hoc triu chng khng c trng.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-prev\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/220/2018/06/220-bai-liet-3406-5b1a.jpg\" alt=\"Bi lit\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/220/2018/06/220-bai-liet-6523-5b1a.jpg\" alt=\"Bi lit\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca bi lit</strong></h3>\r\nTriu chng dng bi lit th nh:\r\n\r\nXut hin cc triu chng ging nh bnh cm, hoc nh cc bnh nhim trng do virus khc bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>au u;</li>\r\n 	<li>St;</li>\r\n 	<li>Rt c hng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Bun nn, nn ma;</li>\r\n 	<li>To bn hoc tiu chy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTriu chng  th khng lit:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>au u;</li>\r\n 	<li>Cng c;</li>\r\n 	<li>Thay i chc nng tm thn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTriu chng  th lit:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>St v sau  au u;</li>\r\n 	<li>Cng c v lng;</li>\r\n 	<li>To bn;</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhy cm khi b chm vo ngi;</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt cm gic v vn ng  phn di ca c th.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no bn cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nBnh bi lit l mt bnh kh nguy him mc d c nhiu triu chng khng c trng, d b nhm ln vi cc bnh khc. Nu c bt k triu chng no nu trn xy ra, bn nn lin h ngay vi bc s  c kim tra v t vn. Chn on v iu tr sm s gim nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n bi lit</strong></h3>\r\nBnh bi lit do virus polio gy ra. y l bnh nguy him v c sc lan truyn cao. Mt s con ng ph bin gy bnh l:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tip xc vi nc v thc n  b nhim phn ca ngi bnh. Tnh trng ny thng thy  nhng vng c h thng thot nc km.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi khe mnh tip xc vi ngi bnh bi lit hoc vi ngi va dng vc xin bi lit ng ung (y l loi vc xin c lm t virus sng).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy c mc bi lit?</strong></h3>\r\nBnh bi lit l bnh truyn nhim, kh ph bin nn mi i tng u c nguy c mc bnh. Bnh c bit d xy ra i vi tr em nu khng c tim chng vc-xin.\r\n\r\nYu t lm tng nguy c bi lit, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>i du lch  ni c virus bi lit hoc ang c dch bi lit.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sng vi ngi c mang virus bi lit trong ngi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi c h min dch suy gim nh l HIV/AIDS, b ct amian trc y, cha bnh bng x tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi b stress qu nhiu hoc hot ng cng  cao trong thi gian di ri tip xc vi virus bi lit khin sc  khng km.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mi trng sng lc hu,  nhim.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn on bi lit</strong></h3>\r\nBc s xem xt cc triu chng ca bnh nhn, khm lm sng v tin hnh ly mu dch t ty sng bng cch chc d ty sng v kim tra dch  tm ra du hiu nhim trng.\r\n\r\nBc s cng c th ly mu phn, dch t c hng, v mu  kim tra c virus hay khng.\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr bi lit hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nHin vn cha c phng php iu tr dt im bi lit. iu c th lm chnh l iu tr cc triu chng do bnh mang li bao gm dng thuc gim au, tp vt l tr liu v thit k li sng  ci thin tnh trng sc khe.\r\n\r\nS dng cc phng php iu tr bnh bi lit kp thi s gip bn phng chng nhng bin chng nguy him ng thi hn ch s tc ng tiu cc ca bnh n hot ng, sinh hot hng ngy.\r\n\r\nS dng ibuprofen hoc nhng loi thuc tng t  c kim sot cn au do bnh bi lit.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca bi lit</strong></h3>\r\nBn hon ton c th kim sot v hn ch c cc din bin xu ca bnh bng cch:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tun th theo hng dn ca bc s trong vic iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thng xuyn tp vt l tr liu kt hp vi xoa bp cc c  trnh b teo c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Duy tr li sng tch cc, hn ch s cng thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lin h ngay vi bc s khi c th c nhng bt thng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php phng nga hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nu c bt c biu hin nghi nhim bnh hoc mc bnh bi lit hy n bnh vin  c kim tra.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tim chng vc-xin nga bi lit trc khi i du lch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch tip xc chung ng cc vt dng nh khn, ly, ngun nc c nguy c nhim bnh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Bi lit', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bai-liet', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:35:04', '2021-01-30 15:35:04', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=794', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
(796, 1, '2021-01-30 22:37:07', '2021-01-30 15:37:07', '<h2>Lit na ngi l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Lit na ngi l tnh trng bnh nhn t ngt b mt vn ng ch ng na bn c th: tay chn cng mt bn, c th km theo na mt cng bn do tn thng vng no khi b t qu.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Lit na ngi l g?</strong></h3>\r\nLit na ngi l tnh trng bnh nhn t ngt b mt vn ng ch ng na bn c th: tay chn cng mt bn, c th km theo na mt cng bn do tn thng vng no khi b t qu. Ngi mc phi c kh nng c ng nh bn lit hoc hon ton khng th c ng. Lit na ngi thng l di chn hoc b nh hng bi cc cn bnh khc. Bnh c th gp  bt c ai v la tui no. Khi pht hin bnh, bn cn iu tr sm  mau chng phc hi cc chc nng v gim thiu nguy c b lit vnh vin.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-prev\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-next icon-next swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Next slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-prev\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/17/2018/05/17-liet-nua-nguoi-6384-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"Lit na ngi\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/17/2018/05/17-liet-nua-nguoi-7472-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"Lit na ngi\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca lit na ngi</strong></h3>\r\nCc triu chng thng gp  bnh nhn:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vng v, kh i li;</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt mi;</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc c co cng hoc mm nho;</li>\r\n 	<li>M mt r xung, mo ming;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ni kh, kh khn khi nghe hiu ngha t;</li>\r\n 	<li>B tiu;</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt cm gic na bn ngi;</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr nh suy gim.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nNu bn gp kh khn khi vn ng na bn c th v c cc biu hin nu trn th nn n bnh vin  khm v xt nghim sm trnh cc bin chng khng ng c. Mi ngi c mt c a khc nhau, bn cn tham kho  kin bc s  c phng n iu tr thch hp.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n lit na ngi</strong></h3>\r\n<em>Nguyn nhn c th phc hi hon ton:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Migraine.</li>\r\n 	<li>H ng huyt.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mu t di mng cng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lit Todd sau cn ng kinh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim ng mch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Huyt khi ang hnh thnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>D dng mch mu no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chn ng no.</li>\r\n 	<li>X no ty ri rc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon phn ly</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Nguyn nhn c th phc hi cn  li di chng:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhi mu no cp hon ton.</li>\r\n 	<li> mu t ni s.</li>\r\n 	<li>U thn kinh m no hoc cu no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh hng cu li lim.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lymphoma no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc d dng c bit ca v no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh Moyamoya</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><b>Nhng ai c nguy c</b><strong>b lit na ngi?</strong></h3>\r\nBnh xut hin  mi la tui v gii tnh. Cn lu  cc biu hin v sm iu tr  khng  bnh lm nh hng n cht lng cuc sng.\r\n\r\nLit na ngi thng l biu hin ca mt s cn bnh. V vy, ngi bnh c nguy c mc bnh cao khi c tin s:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tai bin mch mu no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhi mu no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Xut huyt trong no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khi u no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim trng thn kinh trung ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>p-xe.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chn thng s no.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mu t ngoi mng cng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn onlit na ngi</strong></h3>\r\nChn on bnh nhn thng qua thm khm v quan st triu chng. Ngoi ra bc s cng cn khm lm sng  xc nh dng yu c hoc lit  tm ra ni tn thng trong thn kinh.\r\n\r\nCc xt nghim cn thit:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Xt nghim cng thc mu ton b.</li>\r\n 	<li>Xt nghim sinh ha mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chp CT, MRI s no.</li>\r\n 	<li>in no .</li>\r\n 	<li>Chp mch mu no l cc xt nghim chn on hu ch nht  xc nh nguyn nhn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr lit na ngi hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nV lit phn ln l biu hin b tn thng gy ra bi nhiu cn bnh khc nhau nn km theo lit c th l mt s triu chng nguy him khc.iu tr lit u tin phi xc nh ng nguyn nhn v iu tr nguyn nhn bnh cng cc triu chng lin quan.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chm sc phn c th b lit.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lun t chi  t th sinh l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Xoa bp, tp vn ng sm.</li>\r\n 	<li> phng b lot, mc bng cch thay i t th nm lin tc (nm m nc hoc m khng kh c ngn).</li>\r\n 	<li> phng nhim khun th pht (ng h hp, tit niu...).</li>\r\n 	<li>Ch  dinh dng y .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTy vo th trng v tnh trng bnh m bc s s k n thuc v p dng nhng phng php iu tr ph hp cho bnh nhn.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca lit na ngi</strong></h3>\r\n<em>Ch  sinh hot:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tun th theo cc hng dn ca bc s trong vic iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thm khm nh k  c theo di tnh trng sc khe, din tin ca bnh v  bc s tm hng iu tr ph hp trong thi gian tip theo nu bnh c du hiu ti pht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Duy tr li sng tch cc, hn ch s cng thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi b lit thng b hn ch cc c ng v th rt kh khn trong vn  sinh hot. Ngi nh bnh nhn c th ng hnh hoc tm ngi gip  bnh nhn trong vn  ny.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi chm sc bnh nhn c th hc cc bi tp cho ngi b lit  h tr ngi bnh trong vic vn ng cc khp.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Ch  dinh dng:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nng lng m nn chim 20-25% v tinh bt chim 50%.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cn cung cp thc phm giu cht chng oxy ha, vitamin C (trong cam, bi, du), vitamin E (ht d, u phng).</li>\r\n 	<li>Nn dng dng thc n mm, d tiu: cho, sp, sa, nc hoa qu ti.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trnh thc n to, cng, nng dn n kh nut hoc d b hc, sc.</li>\r\n 	<li>King thc n cha nhiu cht bo v cht kch thch, caffeine (ru, bia, ch c, c ph).</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh nhn hn ch dng mui khi  n nh (7 - 14 ngy sau tai bin).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><b>Phng php phng nga hiu qu</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Kim sot nguyn nhn gy t qu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Kim sot huyt p, gi  mc khng cao qu 140/90 mmHg.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng  c th qu bo, tp th dc u n, n nhiu hoa qu, rau ti.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Lit na ngi', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'liet-nua-nguoi', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:37:07', '2021-01-30 15:37:07', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=796', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
