(798, 1, '2021-01-30 22:41:11', '2021-01-30 15:41:11', '<h2>L ln l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">L ln l triu chng khin ngi bnh mt phng hng, kh tp trung hay kh a ra quyt nh. y l bnh l thng xy ra  ngi gi, nhng hin nay cng xut hin rt nhiu  ngi tr do phong cch sng v tnh trng  nhim.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>L ln l g?</strong></h3>\r\nL ln l triu chng khin ngi bnh mt phng hng, kh tp trung hay kh a ra quyt nh. y l bnh l thng xy ra  ngi gi, nhng hin nay cng xut hin rt nhiu  ngi tr do phong cch sng v tnh trng  nhim. Triu chng ph bin nht l hay qun, hnh vi khng n nhp vi mi trng v cm xc khng n nh. Dng thuc kt hp vi vic thay i thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca l ln.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/21/2018/05/21-lu-lan-3498-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"L ln\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/21/2018/05/21-lu-lan-3156-5b0e.jpg\" alt=\"L ln\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca l ln</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bnh nhn mc phi thng c biu hin ng ngc v mt phng hng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh nhn thng phn x ngn ng chm, ni lp, hi i hi li mi tr li c. p ng v c khi khng tr li ng trng tm;</li>\r\n 	<li>Hnh vi thng khng n nhp vi mi trng, lc sng s im lng, lc th bn chn ht hong;</li>\r\n 	<li>Thay i cm xc t ngt;</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng bit mnh ang  u hay khng nhn bit c ngi quen;</li>\r\n 	<li>Hay nghi ng v cn c;</li>\r\n 	<li>Cm xc khng n nh;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ri lon  thc;</li>\r\n 	<li>Suy gim tr nh, thng hay qun.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><b>Khi no cn gp bc s?</b></h3>\r\nNu bn thn hoc ngi nh c du hiu l ln nh chng mt, th khng u, ln ln, thng mt  thc th bnh nhn nn n bnh vin  c iu tr cn nguyn. Mi ngi c mt c a khc nhau, bn cn tham kho  kin bc s  c phng n iu tr thch hp. Chn on v iu tr sm s gim nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n bnh l ln</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Do trm cm.</li>\r\n 	<li>No b hy hoi do nhiu tai bin no nh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt nc nh hng lng in gii v gy hi cho c th.</li>\r\n 	<li>Do di truyn, virus.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt chc nng no  ngi gi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thiu vitamin B12, niacin, thiamin.</li>\r\n 	<li>ng huyt thp.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n75% trng hp l ln din tin m thm mt thi gian kh lu trc khi c pht hin. Do bnh nhn lng trnh bnh ca mnh, tuy nhin cc triu chng s dn dn xut hin r rng v khng che y c na.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><b>Nhng ai c nguy c</b><strong>l ln?</strong></h3>\r\ny l bnh c th xy n vi tt c mi ngi, khng phn bit  tui hay gii tnh.\r\n\r\nBnh ph bin hn vi nhng ngi ln tui do chc nng trong c th  b lo ha. Tuy nhin hin nay, l ln ang c du hiu tr ha do ngi tr khng c li sng khoa hc.\r\n\r\nYu t lm tng nguy c l ln, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tui tc cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Phc hi sau phu thut.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lm dng ma ty.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nghin ru, ht nhiu thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh l no tim n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng phpxt nghim v chn onl ln</strong></h3>\r\nBc s s hi triu chng v khm sc khe bnh nhn  xc nh bnh v nguyn nhn gy nn. Cc xt nghim bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Xt nghim mu: Bch cu tng, mu lng tng l biu hin thng thy.</li>\r\n 	<li>o in no .</li>\r\n 	<li>Chp CT, MRI gip nhn bit bt thng trn phim.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr l ln hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nTy thuc vo nguyn nhn gy bnh m c nhng phng php iu tr khc nhau. Nu c chn on sm bnh nhn s c c hi gim bt cc triu chng v khng  li di chng.\r\n\r\nCc dc phm thng dng: Tacrine vi bit danh l cognex, aricept (donepezil), rivastigmine hoc exelon, galantamine (reminyl).\r\n\r\nC cc nghin cu cho rng sinh t E, estrogen, mt vi tho dc nh l bch qu cng c cng dng phn no.\r\n\r\nTy vo th trng v tnh trng bnh m bc s s k n thuc v p dng nhng phng php iu tr ph hp cho bnh nhn.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin cal ln</strong></h3>\r\n<em>Ch  sinh hot:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khuyn khch ngi bnh vn ng v sinh hot bui sng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tun th theo hng dn ca bc s trong vic iu tr.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thng xuyn tp luyn th dc th thao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch sinh hot  nhng ni c mi trng c hi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Th gin u c, hn ch cng thng thn kinh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Ch  dinh dng:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thc n cn xen k nhiu mn m bo dinh dng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cho bnh nhn n nhiu ba mi ngy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thc n n ung dinh dng cn bng, king  nhiu du m, ng v mui.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'L ln', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lu-lan', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:41:11', '2021-01-30 15:41:11', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=798', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
