(800, 1, '2021-01-30 22:46:24', '2021-01-30 15:46:24', '<h2>Mc rng l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Hin tng mc rng xy ra  tr t 6 thng tui v vo khong 3 tui th hai hm rng s mc hon thin, ty mi a tr c cung cp dinh dng th no m qu trnh mc rng din ra nhanh hay chm. Vo giai on ny, a tr s gp nhiu vn  v sc khe nn cc bc lm cha m cn ht sc ch  n b, khng  nhng vn  ny nh hng nghim trng n sc khe, thm ch tnh mng ca con mnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Mc rng l g?</strong></h3>\r\nRng l mt b phn nm trong khoang ming c chc nng x, nghin nt thc n trc khi xung thc qun vo d dy.\r\n\r\nHin tng mc rng xy ra  tr t 6 thng tui v vo khong 3 tui th hai hm rng s mc hon thin, ty mi a tr c cung cp dinh dng th no m qu trnh mc rng din ra nhanh hay chm. Vo giai on ny, a tr s gp nhiu vn  v sc khe nn cc bc lm cha m cn ht sc ch  n b, khng  nhng vn  ny nh hng nghim trng n sc khe, thm ch tnh mng ca con mnh.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-prev\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/324/2018/05/324-moc-rang-4343-5b05.jpg\" alt=\"Mc rng\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-next icon-next swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Next slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-prev\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/324/2018/05/324-moc-rang-8727-5b05.jpg\" alt=\"Mc rng\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca mc rng</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chy nc di: Thng vo thng th 4 qu trnh mc rng  tr s c biu hin chy nc di quanh ming, cha m ch cn dng khn mm lau sch cho tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nga nu rng, hay cn: Do rng c y ln trn, c xt vi nu nhiu hn khin nu rng kh nga, theo phn x tr s a tay hay  vt vo ming  cn.  gi v sinh ming v nu cho tr , cha m cn mua cho con nhng  chi gm nu chuyn dng. Trong giai on ny tr s hay cn khi b gy au ngi m, chnh v th m nn mua dng c tr ti.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ho, st: Do tit nhiu nc di nn tr s ho v st nh, ng qu lo lng v y l hin tng bnh thng, a tr n bc s l gii php tt nht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Quy khc: V kh kh chu nn tr s khc quy  chng t mnh ang c vn  cho cha m bit.</li>\r\n 	<li>B n: B n khin tr yu i v st cn nhanh chng. Nu vic b n ca tr ko di th cha m cn a tr n bc s  c gii php ng n.</li>\r\n 	<li>Kh ng: c bit vo ban m, hy ht ru, xoa lng hay v nh vo mng b,... b d ng, trnh tn hi sc khe.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Qu trnh mc rng ca tr</strong></h3>\r\n<em>T 5 - 10 thng:</em>Tr s mc nhng chic rng u tin v xut hin cc du hiu triu chng trn, cc bc lm cha m cn ch  n tr  rng mc u v khng nh hng nhiu n sc khe.\r\n\r\n<em>T 7 - 10 thng tui:</em>Tr mc 4 rng ca bn, vic tp nhai khi  c rng ca xut hin i vi cc b khng h n gin.\r\n\r\n<em>T 12 - 16 thng tui:</em>Tr mc rng hm, gip tr nhai thc n d dng hn. V kch thc v cu to rng hm khc vi rng ca nn khi mc tr rt au, cha m cn lu  n vn  dinh dng cho tr, c bit l lng canxi cn thit; thc n ch bin d nhai v tiu ha, khng tc ng nhiu vo phn hm ca con.\r\n\r\n<em>T 14 - 20 thng:</em>Tr mc 4 rng nanh. Trong giai on ny tr s hay quy khc, kh chu v tiu chy, mc  ty thuc vo mi a tr khc nhau. Nu con st trn 35  th n ngay bc s khm v mua thuc.\r\n\r\n<em>T 20 - 32 thng:</em>Tr mc 4 rng hm tip theo. y l giai on hon thin rng hm ln u ca tr. Nu pht trin theo ng tin  th rng tr s mc u, y  v n khong 6 tui th bt u qu trnh thay rng ln 2.\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nKhi tr xut hin cc du hiu triu chng trn  mc  cao hy tm n ngay cc bc s  c gii php ph hp. Tuyt i khng t  cho con ung thuc, v nh th khng nhng gim bt nhng kh chu  tr m cn nguy hi cho tnh mng.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Bm cn lm g khi con mc rng?</strong></h3>\r\nNu mun con c khe mnh vrng pht trin tt th b m cn phi:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cung cp y  ngun dinh dng lnh mnh ph hp trong tng giai on, c bit l canxi gip xng, rng ca con mau pht trin, cng cp.  lng canxi th tr no ca con cng pht trin mnh m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cho con ung nc nhiu hn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cho tr tm nng vo mi bui sng  hp thu lng vitamin D t t nhin.</li>\r\n 	<li>V sinh tht sch rng ming cho tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nu thy con c bt k du hiu bt thng nh st, quy khc, b n ko di th tm n ngay vi bc s chuyn khoa  khm v cho tr dng thuc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Mc rng', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'moc-rang', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:46:24', '2021-01-30 15:46:24', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=800', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
