(802, 1, '2021-01-30 22:50:05', '2021-01-30 15:50:05', '<h1>Tt li l g</h1>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Tnh trng li di chuyn v pha cung rng  l b mt chn rng c gi l bnh tt li, hay cn gi l tt nu rng. Bnh tt li l biu hin ca vic mt xi mng chn rng, mn c rng, l ng rng, gy tnh trng  but v mt v p thm m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Tt li l g?</strong></h3>\r\nTnh trng li di chuyn v pha cung rng  l b mt chn rng c gi l bnh tt li, hay cn gi l tt nu rng.\r\n\r\nTt li l biu hin ca vic mt xi mng chn rng, mn c rng, l ng rng, gy tnh trng  but v mt v p thm m.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/343/2018/05/343-tut-loi-2609-5b06.jpg\" alt=\"Tt li\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/343/2018/05/343-tut-loi-8832-5b06.jpg\" alt=\"Tt li\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca tt li</strong></h3>\r\nTt li ban u c cc triu chng nh: vim nu, sng  ty; khi chi rng hoc cn phi vt cng s chy mu chn rng. V lu di, bnh tt li gy chy mu thng xuyn, co ty rng, hi ming, tit nhiu nc bt, rng lung lay d rng i.\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nNhn thy s xut hin ca cc triu chng trn th tt nht nn n ngay phng khm nha khoa uy tn hay bnh vin  c kim tra, thm khm v iu tr ng phng php, ph hp tnh trng bnh ca tng bnh nhn.Chn on v iu tr sm s gim nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n tt li</strong></h3>\r\nBnh tt li c nhng nguyn nhn ph bin sau y:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vim li, vim quanh rng: c bit l nhng trng hp ko di  nhiu ngy. Bnh nhn mc bnh tt li trong trng hp ny thng xut hin tnh trng vim nu, chy mu nu rng, sng nu v c nguy c tt li c hai hm rng nu khng c pht hin sm.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sang chn khp cn: Do lp xng bn ngoi chn rng qu mng dn n sang chn, tng sinh biu m v gy vim nu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rng mc lch hm dn n c xt nhiu vi phanh mi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hu qu ca vic iu tr vng quanh rng hoc iu tr nn chnh rng cha ng k thut.</li>\r\n 	<li>S dng bn chi ch rng qu cng v chi khng ng cch.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy c mc tt li?</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhng ngi v sinh rng ming km, chi rng sai cch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi c tin s mc cc bnh v rng ming.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi c rng mc bt thng (mc lch, hoc tha rng).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn ontt li</strong></h3>\r\nTrc tin cc nha s s tin hnh iu tra bnh s v khm tng qut.  c c cc kt qu chnh xc, cc bc s s tin hnh cho bnh nhn chp X-quang, t  a ra cc chn on chun xc v gii php iu tr ph hp nht.\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr tt li hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\ni vi trng hp nh, bnh nhn c th iu tr bng cch thay i bn chi ch rng mm, si nh v thay i cch chi rng khoa hc nht. Nu c tnh trng  but xut hin, bnh nhn c th ngm gel fluor theo ch nh ca nha s.\r\n\r\nTrng hp c rng mn c th dng n cc liu php thm m.\r\n\r\nPhu thut ghp li phn li  che ph chn rng. Phng php phu thut ghp li mi nht c p dng  l phng php ti to m c hng dn vi mng sinh hc.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php phng nga hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>S dng bn chi mm vi cc si lng nh, chi rng ng cch; ng thi kt hp vi s dng nc sc ming khng khun, hm lng fluor t chun  khng nhng lm sch m cn cng c men rng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khm rng theo nh k 6 thng/ln  lm sch cao rng, pht hin cc bnh v rng ming.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tham kho cc chuyn gia dinh dng v ch  n y  dinh dng cn thit  rng c chc khe.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Tt li', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tut-loi', '', '', '2021-01-30 22:50:05', '2021-01-30 15:50:05', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=802', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
