(804, 1, '2021-01-30 23:16:31', '2021-01-30 16:16:31', '<h2>Basedow l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Bnh Basedow (c tn gi khc l bnh Graves, bnh Parry) c hiu l mt dng bu c, nhng l bu gip c lan ta hoc cng gip t min, gy ri lon min dch v nh hng trc tip n tuyn gip. Tuyn gip l mt tuyn ni tit quan trng c chc nng tit hormone thyroid kim sot hot ng c th. Tuyn gip b tc ng dn n hot ng qu mc, tit nhiu hormone vt mc v gy ra bnh cng gip.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Basedow l g?</strong></h3>\r\nBnh Basedow (c tn gi khc l bnh Graves, bnh Parry) c hiu l mt dng bu c, nhng l bu gip c lan ta hoc cng gip t min, gy ri lon min dch v nh hng trc tip n tuyn gip. Tuyn gip l mt tuyn ni tit quan trng c chc nng tit hormone thyroid kim sot hot ng c th. Tuyn gip b tc ng dn n hot ng qu mc, tit nhiu hormone vt mc v gy ra bnh cng gip.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/288/2018/05/288-basedow-5691-5b03.jpg\" alt=\"Basedow\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/288/2018/05/288-basedow-3790-5b03.jpeg\" alt=\"Basedow\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca Basedow</strong></h3>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nQuan st  nhng ngi mc bnh Basedow, d nhn thy:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nhn cu li ra hn ngi bnh thng;</li>\r\n 	<li>C bu  c;</li>\r\n 	<li>Thm n, n nhiu;</li>\r\n 	<li>i tiu thng xuyn;</li>\r\n 	<li>To cc u ngn tay, chn;</li>\r\n 	<li>Hay mt tp trung, hay run ry.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n bn thn ngi bnh s cm thy mnh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cm gic bn chn, nn nao, lo lng bt thng, c th mt mi;</li>\r\n 	<li>Gp cc vn  v mt nh m hay phn nh (cng mt vt nhng n hai hay nhiu hnh nh);</li>\r\n 	<li>Tit nhiu m hi;</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhp tim bt thng, thng l nhanh hn bnh thng nn lun c cm gic lo lng, bn chn;</li>\r\n 	<li>Chu k kinh nguyt khng u;</li>\r\n 	<li>Cm thy ngc ln bt thng (xut hin  nam gii);</li>\r\n 	<li>Gim cn bt thng (xut hin  mt b phn ngi mc bnh).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nKhi bin chng, bnh Basedow c kh nng gy bnh c tim nhim c gip (gm ri lon nhp tim v suy tim cng gip), c cng gip cp. V vy, khi nhn bit c s xut hin ca cc du hiu trn hy n ngay bnh vin  bc s lm cc xt nghim, chn on, a ra gii php iu tr ph hp.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Lu : Tnh trng bnh v th trng mi ngi l khc nhau, hy lng nghe nhng li khuyn ca bc s  vic iu tr bnh tin trin tt nht.</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n</strong><strong>Basedow</strong></h3>\r\nBnh Basedow hnh thnh do s ri lon hot ng ca h min dch, lc ny h min dch s quay ngc li tn cng cc t bo m trong c th, nh hng trc tip n hot ng ca tuyn gip. Chnh s tc ng ny, tuyn gip sn xut hormone nhiu hn bnh thng.\r\n\r\nBnh ny c th di truyn t m sang con (c bit l con gi chim t l cao hn con trai), khng ly t ngi ny sang ngi khc.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy c mc</strong><strong>Basedow?</strong></h3>\r\nNhng yu t c th lm gia tng kh nng mc bnh Basedow:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Yu t di truyn: Nu gia nh c ngi thn mc bnh Basedow th nguy c th h sau mc bnh cao hn, c bit m mc bnh th t l con gi sinh ra di truyn rt cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gii tnh: N gii c kh nng mc bnh ny cao hn nam gii.</li>\r\n 	<li> tui: Xut hin  ngi di 40 tui (nht l  20 - 40 tui).</li>\r\n 	<li>Ht thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tinh thn, u c lun trong trng thi cng thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc ri lon khc trong c th nh ri lon do mcbnh tiu ngloi 1, vim khp,</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn on</strong><strong>Basedow</strong></h3>\r\nKhi n bnh vin, ngi mc bnh s c thm hi v nhng biu hin bn ngoi c th v thc hin vic xt nghim mu; chp X-quang, CT  c cc thng tin bnh. Bc s da vo cc kt qu xt nghim, tin s nhn thn v cc du hiu ca bnh nhn m c cc hng iu tr ph hp.\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr</strong><strong>Basedow hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\n lm gim lng hormone do tuyn gip sn xut ra gy nn cm gic hi hp lo lng, tng tit m hi v nhp tim nhanh bt thng, bc s cho bnh nhn dng thuc c ch beta. Cn trng hp iu tr bng tia phng xa hay phu thut th buc phi dng hormone thyroid thay th sut qung i.\r\n\r\nBasedow ko theo s suy gim chc nng mt, mang n mt s bnh v mt. Cc bc s c th s dng phng php phng x i-t, phu thut hay ch dng thuc.  gim bt tnh trng kch ng, sng mt, bc s cho bnh nhn dng thuc steroid c ch h thng min dch, mt s loi thuc nh mt trong danh mc. Phng php phng x i-t ngy cng t c s dng v hiu qu mang li khng cao ng thi em n nhng tn thng khc cho mt.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin caBasedow</strong></h3>\r\n bnh c iu tr thun li nht, cc bnh nhn Basedow cn thc hin nhng iu sau y:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Luyn tp th dc th thao, nhng bi tp c cc bc s khuyn hoc cho php tp.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung thuc ng liu ng gi, vic qun ung hoc ung khng ng liu s khin qu trnh iu tr v hiu.</li>\r\n 	<li>i khm mt t nht 1 ln/nm hoc nhiu hn theo ch nh ca bc s.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ni khng vi ru, bia, cc cht kch thch v thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ch  n ung: Cn tham kho k cc li khuyn ca bc s nhng thc phm nn n nhiu v nhng thc phm nn hn ch  qu trnh iu tr tt nht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lin h ngay vi bc s khi c th c nhng bt thng trong qu trnh iu tr.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Basedow', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'basedow', '', '', '2021-01-30 23:16:31', '2021-01-30 16:16:31', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=804', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
