(806, 1, '2021-01-30 23:33:36', '2021-01-30 16:33:36', '<h2>Suy cn gip l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Hormone parathyroid ca tuyn cn gip c chc nng iu chnh lng canxi v photpho trong xng v mu. Tnh trng tuyn cn gip khng sn xut  hormone parathyroid khin mt cn bng lng photpho tng trong khi canxi trong mu li gim, gy nn bnh suy cn gip. Suy cn gip dn n nhiu bnh l khc nh: thn kinh, c, da, xng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Suy cn gip l g?</strong></h3>\r\nHormone parathyroid ca tuyn cn gip c chc nng iu chnh lng canxi v photpho trong xng v mu. Tnh trng tuyn cn gip khng sn xut  hormone parathyroid khin mt cn bng trong khi lng photpho tng thcanxi trong mu li gim, gy nn bnh suy cn gip.\r\n\r\nSuy cn gip dn n nhiu bnh l khc nh: thn kinh, c, da, xng...\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/297/2018/05/297-suy-can-giap-3947-5b03.jpg\" alt=\"Suy cn gip\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/297/2018/05/297-suy-can-giap-3250-5b03.jpg\" alt=\"Suy cn gip\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca suy cn gip</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cm gic t cng  cc u ngn tay, chn v c mi, li;</li>\r\n 	<li>C yu, au cc vng c  tay, chn, thm ch cc vng khc trn c th;</li>\r\n 	<li>au bng d di khi ti chu k kinh nguyt;</li>\r\n 	<li>Co tht thanh qun gy kh th, trng hp nng phi cp cu;</li>\r\n 	<li>Kh da, mng tay gin, d gy, bin dng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Rng nhiu tc, lng my tha tht;</li>\r\n 	<li>Thn kinh lun cng thng, mt mi, au u;</li>\r\n 	<li>Xut hin tnh trng ng kinh, trm cm  mt s bnh nhn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nKhi nhng du hiu, triu chng trn xut hin cn n ngay bnh vin  lm cc xt nghim, thm khm, t  bc s c c s a ra nhng chn on chnh xc nht, hng dn iu tr bng cc gii php ph hp vi tnh trng mi bnh nhn.\r\n\r\nTuyt i khng th  vi cc bt thng xy ra  c th v vic cha tr mun mng thng kh em li kt qu cao.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n suy cn gip</strong></h3>\r\n<em>Suy cn gip mc phi:</em>Thng xut hin sau cc cuc phu thut hay chn thng tuyn cn gip (c bit l phu thut ct tuyn gip hoc iu tr u tuyn cn gip). Trnh  khoa hc k thut ngy cng cao nn cc cuc phu thut c thc hin bi nhng bc s c trnh  v tay ngh cao, s trng hp gp tai bin ngy cng t.\r\n\r\n<em>Suy cn gip di truyn:</em>a tr sinh ra hoc l khng c tuyn cn gip hoc tuyn cn gip c nhng hot ng rt km. Suy cn gip di truyn l bnh di truyn theo gen ln, nu c cha v m u mang gen ny th nguy c con mc bnh n 25%. Cc triu chng ca bnh s xut hin vo trc nm tr 10 tui, nht l lc tr 2 tui.\r\n\r\n<em>Hu qu ca bnh t min:</em>Khng th sinh ra v quay li tn cng loi b tuyn cn gip, dn n suy cn gip. Cng c khi, bnh nhn cn mc thm cc bnh t min khc na, thng nht l bnh Addison.\r\n\r\n<em>Nguyn nhn khc:</em> Vic iu tr ung th  vng c d dn n tn thng v ph hy tuyn cn gip.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><b>Nhng ai c nguy c mc phi</b><strong>suy cn gip?</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi c tin s iu tr cc bnh tuyn gip, c bit  tng phu thut hay iu tr ung th vng c.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tin s gia nh: Cha v m mang gen ln bnh suy tuyn cn gip th nguy c con mc bnh cng cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi mc cc bnh t min.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi c ch  n ung ngho canxi th nguy c mc cc bnh v tuyn ni tit cng cao, trong  c bnh suy tuyn cn gip.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn on suy cn gip</strong></h3>\r\nBnh nhn mc suy tuyn cn gip khi n bnh vin s c lm cc xt nghim mu, nc tiu  kim tra nng  canxi v photpho, nng  hormone parathyroid trong mu; chp X-quang  kim tra nng  canxi trong xng; lm in tm   kim tra nhp tim.\r\n\r\nCc bc s s kt hp vi vic iu tra tin s gia nh, tin s bnh ca bnh nhn ri t  mi a ra cc chn on v gii php iu tr ph hp.\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr suy cn gip hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nCh yu bnh suy tuyn cn gip c iu tr bng thuc, mc ch l  cn bng nng  canxi v photpho trong mu lun  mc cn bng. Qu trnh iu tr din ra nh th no ph thuc vo nhiu yu t nh: sc khe, mc  bnh, cc du hiu v triu chng bnh,... ca tng bnh nhn.\r\n\r\nC th cc bc s s cho bnh nhn ung calcium carbonate dng vin  iu tr bnh. Tuy nhin thuc cng c tc dng ph nh to bn, si thn nu s dng liu cao.\r\n\r\nVi trng hp canxi trong mu qu thp, triu chng bnh nng th phi nhp vin v c cc bc s chuyn khoa tim canxi vo tnh mch. Sau khi c v nh, cc bnh nhn phi dng canxi v vitamin D ng ung. y l mt bnh mn tnh nn vic iu tr c th ko di sut i ca bnh nhn.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><b>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca</b><strong>suy cn gip</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ch  n giu canxi nh rau xanh, sa, cc ch phm t sa, ng cc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khng ht thuc l, dng cc cht kch thch, ung cc loi nc ngt, c bit cc loi nc c cha acid phosphoric.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tng cng vn ng thn th. Ng  gic, ung  nc  ci thin sc khe.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tun th theo hng dn ca bc s trong vic iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lin h ngay vi bc s khi c th c nhng bt thng trong qu trnh iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thm khm nh k  c theo di tnh trng sc khe, din tin 