(812, 1, '2021-01-30 23:36:06', '2021-01-30 16:36:06', '<h2>Chn thng thanh qun l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Chn thng thanh qun l mt loi chn thng thng gp trong chn thng tai, mi, hng i km chung vi chn thng s no gy tc nghn ng th v nguy c t vong cho bnh nhn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Chn thng thanh qun l g?</strong></h3>\r\nChn thng thanh qun l mt loi chn thng thng gp trong chn thng tai, mi, hng i km chung vi chn thng s no gy tc nghn ng th v nguy c t vong cho bnh nhn.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/456/2018/05/456-chan-thuong-thanh-quan-5606-5b0c.jpg\" alt=\"Chn thng thanh qun\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/456/2018/05/456-chan-thuong-thanh-quan-6519-5b0c.jpg\" alt=\"Chn thng thanh qun\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca bnh chn thng thanh qun</strong></h3>\r\nChn thng thanh qun c nhiu triu chng t bnh thng n phc tp. Ngi bnh s mc mt s triu chng ph bin sau y:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Kh khn khi ni hoc to ra ting;</li>\r\n 	<li>Thay i trong ging ni (khn ting);</li>\r\n 	<li>Th n o (th rt);</li>\r\n 	<li>Suy h hp;</li>\r\n 	<li>au  c khi nut hoc ho;</li>\r\n 	<li>B bm dp  trn c;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ho ra mu;</li>\r\n 	<li>Sng c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Bin chng c th gp khi chn thng thanh qun</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bin chng tc thi:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNgat th: sc, chay mau xung khi quan tng va  ong xut tit m, di vt theo vt thng bit lp ng th, sc oi hoi phai c m khi quan cp cu.\r\n\r\nChay mau do chn thng mach, do thay i t th c lm mch mu bc  c nn c cm mau chu ao ngay.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bin chng th phat:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nVim ty lan toa: nu chm sc vng c long leo, vim ty kha nhanh chong lan ra c, mt gy au n.\r\n\r\nVim ty co th lan xung gy vim trung tht thng gp khi kem theo chn thng vung ha hong, thanh quan.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vim khp nhn phu:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDi chng nh hng n i sng, sinh hot, thm m nh ri lon v pht m, thay i ging ni, thn kinh qut ngc.\r\n\r\nTh: kho th, mc  tuy theo tinh trang tn thng, vi tri, hinh thai cua seo.\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nHy n gp bc s ngay  c thm khm v iu tr kp thi khi thy nhng du hiu sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Kh th nhiu, c bit kh th trong thanh qun, kh th c th n mun sau vi gi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khn ting qu lu l du hiu quan trng cn lu .</li>\r\n 	<li>Ho nhiu, ting thay i, khc m ra mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nut au l du hiu lch khp ca sn thanh nhit, ng dp v sn phu, c th gy au ch  h hng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBnh nhn nn c chm sc, iu tr kp thi ca bc s nhm ngn chn v gim thiu nhng bin chng bnh gy nh hng n sc khe v i sng sinh hot.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n chn thng thanh qun</strong></h3>\r\nChn thng thanh qun c chia lm 2 loi chn thng:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chn thng thanh qun ngoi: do ng, nh, ct gy tn thng trc tip n thanh qun t ngoi vo.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chn thng thanh qun trong: do t ng ni kh qun, soi thanh kh qun, x tr cc khi u, gy tn thng bn trong thanh qun.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy c chn thng thanh qun?</strong></h3>\r\nNguy c mc chn thng thanh qun l  nhiu i tng,  tui, gii tnh, ngnh ngh nn hy phng nga v bo v sc khe cho bn thn.\r\n\r\nYu t lm tng nguy c chn thng thanh qun, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ht thuc nhiu hoc tip xc vi nhiu khi thuc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi s dng nhiu cht kch thch nh ru bia, cht cha caffeine.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ung t nc, tip xc nc lnh nhiu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tc ng thanh qun nhiu nh thi quen khc, khc ln gy ph n, au hng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn on chn thng thanh qun</strong></h3>\r\n<em>Chn thng h:</em>\r\n\r\nChn thng trong tnh trng cp cu nh ngt, sc do chn thng s no, v, gy xng hm hay dao m, n bn. Nhng chn thng h khng phi lc no cng chn on ng m cn c s kim tra, xt nghim.\r\n\r\nLu  cc triu chng:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Pht m thu tho, ni kh khn; ri lon h hp nh kh th, th ra bt mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ho hoc ho ln mau bn, trao theo nhip th ra, khi ho hoc c noi. c bit nn lu  b ct hoc m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Chn thng kin:</em>\r\n\r\nKh chn on khi cc triu chng xut hin chm.\r\n\r\nLu  cc triu chng:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Kho th: thanh quan, kh th sau nhiu ln.</li>\r\n 	<li>Khan ting: du hiu quan trng nhng thng b b qua.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nut au, ho ting thay i, khc m ra mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ho: ting ho thay i, khac m co ln mau cung cn lu y, co th xut hin mun.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTrng hp ny nn soi thanh qun :\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bit c hnh thi v gii phu cc b phn thanh qun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bit c hot ng thanh qun nh lit, hn ch hay nhng bt thng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nChup X-quang: T th c nghing, c thng, ct lp giup cho xac inh tn thng (i vi vng sng, ph n th kh cho kt qu chnh xc).\r\n<h3><b>Phng php iu tr chn thng thanh qun hiu qu</b></h3>\r\nCn xc nh mc  thit hi n thanh qun  a ra hng iu tr ph hp.\r\n\r\nNu an ton, bn s c t ni kh qun.\r\n\r\nTrong nhng tnh hung khn cp, phu thut m kh qun c th c thc hin  gip ng th an ton trong khi cha lnh cc tn thng  kh qun. Phu thut m, lm lnh cc vt nt hoc vt rch ni b cn c thc hin cng sm cng tt.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca bnh chn thng thanh qun</strong></h3>\r\nMt s cch phng nga:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khng ht thuc v trnh ht phi khi thuc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung nc   gi thanh qun trn, sch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch s dng cht kch thch, ru bia, caffeine.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch thi quen khc nh gy tn thng thanh qun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bo v thanh qun trc vt nhn, st, nguy him.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Chn thng thanh qun', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'chan-thuong-thanh-quan', '', '', '2021-01-30 23:36:06', '2021-01-30 16:36:06', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=812', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
