(814, 1, '2021-01-30 23:41:07', '2021-01-30 16:41:07', '<h2>Vim hng cp l g</h2>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Vim hng cp l trng thi vim nim mc hng cp tnh. Bnh thng gp  ma lnh. Xut hin  c ngi ln v tr em, kh nguy him i vi tr em. Bnh nu khng c c iu tr sm, vim hng cp s c nguy c dn n vim hng mn tnh v bin chng bnh thp tim.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3><strong>Vim hng cp l g?</strong></h3>\r\n<div>Vim hng cp l trng thi vim nim mc hng cp tnh. Bnh thng gp  ma lnh. Xut hin  c ngi ln v tr em, kh nguy him i vi tr em. Bnh nu khng c c iu tr sm, vim hng cp s c nguy c dn n vim hng mn tnh v bin chng bnh thp tim.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/469/2018/05/469-viem-hong-cap-4295-5b0d.jpg\" alt=\"Vim hng cp\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/469/2018/05/469-viem-hong-cap-9521-5b0d.JPG\" alt=\"Vim hng cp\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-next icon-next\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Next slide\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/469/2018/05/469-viem-hong-cap-4295-5b0d.jpg\" alt=\"Vim hng cp\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/469/2018/05/469-viem-hong-cap-9521-5b0d.JPG\" alt=\"Vim hng cp\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<div><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca vim hng cp</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nBnh vim hng cp c nhng triu chng nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ngi bnh st cao 39 - 40  C;</li>\r\n 	<li>au hng, rt hng, kh nng hng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi bnh s thy hng kh nng, t t thnh cm gic au rt, au tng ln khi nut, khi ni, ho;</li>\r\n 	<li>Tc, nght mi, st st, chy nc mi, khn ging;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ho khan, ho ko di;</li>\r\n 	<li>Amidan b vim to, trn b mt amidan c cht nhy trong, hch c b sng;</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim hng cp thng ko di t 7 - 10 ngy nu khng c iu tr ng cch.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nVim hng cp l bnh thng thng, ph bin nhng khng v vy m chng ta l l trong vic iu tr. Bnh c th gy ra nhiu bin chng nguy him nh: vim tai, vim amidan, vim xoang, vim ph qun, vim thanh qun, c bit nguy him i vi tr nh.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, bnh vim hng cp cn l nguyn nhn gy ra vim cu thn thp, thp tim.\r\n\r\nVy nn, bn nn theo di tnh trng bnh v n gp bc s khi tnh trng khng thuyn gim sau khi t iu tr ti nh. Bc s s cho bn li khuyn v hng dn iu tr kp thi, ngn nga bin chng nguy him v tnh trng chuyn sang vim hng mn tnh.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n vim hng cp</strong></h3>\r\nBnh vim hng cp c nhiu nguyn nhn:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bnh thng i km cc bnh VA, vim amidan.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh do vi khun (ph cu, lin cu hoc cc vi khun khc sn c  hng) hay virus (cm, si,...) gy ra.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy c vim hng cp?</strong></h3>\r\nBnh xy ra  c ngi ln v tr em, c bit nguy him  tr em. Bnh d pht trin khi thi tit thay i t ngt, thay i mi trng sinh hot.\r\n\r\nYu t lm tng nguy c vim hng cp, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tip xc vi mm bnh, b ly nhim t ngi khc.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gi m c th khng tt khi thay i thi tit.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tip xc vi nc  lnh, bi bn khng kh, thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tm nc lnh vo ban m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sc khe yu khin cho sc  khng chng bnh km.</li>\r\n 	<li>B vim amidan.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cm lnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>nh hng ca ru, ha cht.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn on vim hng cp</strong></h3>\r\nVim hng cp c bc s chn on xc nh bng cc biu hin, triu chng ca ngi bnh nh trng thi st cao, au rt hng; khm, quan st nim mc thy tnh trng nim mc hng  rc, man hu, tru trc, tru sau va thanh sau hong phu n, o, vim amidan,\r\n\r\nXt nghim bch cu  kim tra bnh do virus  c hng iu tr ph hp.\r\n\r\nBn cnh , khi bnh nhn khng c du hiu st, nim mc hng  th tin hnh chn on phn bit, s dng xt nghim BW (+), kim tra d ng thuc v k toa iu tr.\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr vim hng cp hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thc hin ch  ngh ngi, gi m c th, nht l c, ngc, bn chn.</li>\r\n 	<li>S dng thuc theo toa bc s, c th s dng thuc h st paracetamol, efferalgan...</li>\r\n 	<li>Tr em bi hng bng glyxerin borat 5%, nh mi bng thuc argyrol 1%.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng khng sinh khi c bin chng nh vim thn, vim khp, vim ph qun, vim tai gia.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nu b vim hng cp ti pht nhiu ln km theo c anbumin trong nc tiu, nn ct amian.</li>\r\n 	<li>S dng thuc khang sinh toan thn khi c th c du hiu bi nhim hoc nguyn nhn do vi khun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sc ming bng nc mui long m (lu  lm thng xuyn hn vo ma lnh). Khi sc ming nn nga c ra pha sau  lm sch hng; sc ming trc v sau khi ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca vim hng cp</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Gi thi quen sinh hot khoa hc, tp th dc thng xuyn, v sinh rng ming, nhm tng sc  khng cho c th.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gi m c th, hn ch tip xc vi nc  lnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thc hin ch  n ung  cht, b sung vitamin C.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tp thi quen sinh hot khoa hc cho tr, nh rng trc v sau ng dy.</li>\r\n 	<li>S dng nc m vo mu lnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>To thi quen tm xong phi lau ngi kh trc khi mc qun o d vo bt c ma no.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Vim hng cp', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'viem-hong-cap', '', '', '2021-01-30 23:41:07', '2021-01-30 16:41:07', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=814', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
