(816, 1, '2021-01-30 23:59:53', '2021-01-30 16:59:53', '<h1>Vim hng mn tnh l g</h1>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Vim hng mn tnh la vim man tinh nim mac hong gy cm gic vng vu, nga rt trong hng, ho v khc m (qunh dnh hoc trng nhy) thng xuyn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Vim hng mn tnh l g?</strong></h3>\r\nVim hng mn tnh la vim man tinh nim mac hong gy cm gic vng vu, nga rt trong hng, ho v khc m (qunh dnh hoc trng nhy) thng xuyn.\r\n\r\nVim hng mn tnh thng chung vi bnh vim mui, xoang man tinh, vim thanh, khi ph quan man tinh. Bnh th hin  3 hinh thc: xut tit, qua phat va teo.\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev swiper-button-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"true\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/471/2018/05/471-viem-hong-man-tinh-2069-5b0d.jpg\" alt=\"Vim hng mn tnh\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/471/2018/05/471-viem-hong-man-tinh-9482-5b0d.jpg\" alt=\"Vim hng mn tnh\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca vim hng mn tnh</strong></h3>\r\nNgi mc bnh vim hng mn tnh c nhng du hiu c nng nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cam thy kh hong, nong rat trong hong hoc co cam giac nga hong;</li>\r\n 	<li>Khi ngu dy c cm gic vng hng, phai c khac m, ng hng  lam long m; m deo va c thng tng ln khi nut;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ho nhiu vo m, nut hi nghn, ting d b khn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBnh vim hng mn tnh gm 4 th, mi th bnh c mt triu chng khc nhau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vim hng mn tnh sung huyt n thun:Ngi bnh c du hiu nim mc hng , ni nhiu tia mao mch mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim hng mn tnh xut tit:Thnh sau hng tng xut tit nhy, trong, hi dnh vo nim mc, chy t vm xung h hng, tm mt i khi bnh nhn nut. Nim mc hng  v ni nhiu tia mao mch mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vim hng mn tnh qu pht:Nim mc hng  v dy ln. T chc bch huyt  thnh sau hng pht trin mnh, qu pht thnh tng m to nh khng u, c mu hng hoc . C khi tp trung thnh mt di g ln  pha sau v dc theo tr sau ca amidan trng nh mt tr sau th hai gi l tr gi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n vim hng mn tnh</strong></h3>\r\nBnh vim hng mn tnh do nhng nguyn nhn sau:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Do nhim khun ti pht i ti pht li ca vng mi hng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tip xc trc tip vi  nhim mi trng, khi bi, khi cng nghip, khi thuc l, trong thi gian di.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi c tin s bnh vim amidan mn tnh v nhim trng rng li gy au hng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thi quen th bng ming khin cho khng kh khng c lc sch bi, vi khun i trc tip vo khoang ming d khin hng b nhim khun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sc  khng, min dch km, yu t c a, d ng, suy gan, tiu ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy c vim hng mn tnh?</strong></h3>\r\nBnh vim hng mn tnh xy ra i vi nhiu ngi, nhiu la tui c bit i vi ngi c sc  khng yu, thng xuyn tip xc vi khi bi, bi bn,  nhim, ngi c tin s vim amidan mn tnh, bnh v tiu ng, suy gan,\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php xt nghim v chn on vim hng mn tnh</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chn on qua cc triu chng, biu hin bnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Xt nghim cn lm sng qua mu, chp X-quang.</li>\r\n 	<li>Xc nh hi chng tro ngc: ni soi thc qun d dy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chn on phn bit  so snh, trnh nhm ln vi bnh khc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr vim hng mn tnh hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\niu tri bnh vim hng mn tnh bng nhiu cch:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>iu tr nguyn nhn gy bnh: Gii quyt cac  vim tim tang  mui, xoang (vim xoang sau), vim amidan.</li>\r\n 	<li>Gip lu thng mui do di hinh vach ngn, polyp mui, thoai hoa cun mui di...</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngn chn, trnh s dng cht kch thch nh thuc l, ru, bia, trnh tip xc vi lung khng kh  nhim nh bui, hoa cht, khi,</li>\r\n 	<li>Gii quyt yu t c a, tng sc  khng, chm sc sc khe tt.</li>\r\n 	<li>iu tri bnh ti ch:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Giai oan xut tit:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Suc ming, hong bng dung dich kim nh: BBM, nc mui nhat.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bi va chm hong bng glycerin borat 3% (theo ch nh ca bc s).</li>\r\n 	<li>Kh dung hng: Hydrocortison v khng sinh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nu hng c nhiu nhy dinh  thanh sau hong thi ra bng dung dich Borat natri 1% choht vy, bi hong va khi dung.</li>\r\n 	<li>Giai oan qua phat: iu tr bng t in nong, cao tn hoc t bng nit long hay laser CO2.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Giai oan teo:</em>Bi glycerin i-t 0,5% hoc m thuy ngn 1%.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"active\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca vim hng mn tnh</strong></h3>\r\nBn nn c mt k hoch phng bnh khoa hc  trnh s xm nhp ca ngun bnh nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Trnh tip xc bui va hoa cht bng cch eo khu trang bao h.</li>\r\n 	<li>V sinh hng bng nc mui m hay dung dch kim m.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ch  n ung iu ,  cht, b sung cac vitamin A, D,ung nc sui, nc khoang.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tng sc  khng cho c th bng ch  hot ng khoa hc, tp th dc thng xuyn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trnh tip xc vi mm bnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch s dng thuc l, bia ru.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Vim hng mn tnh', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'close