(835, 1, '2021-01-31 00:07:28', '2021-01-30 17:07:28', '<h1>Ung th thanh qun l g</h1>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"description\">Ung th thanh qun l cn bnh ph bin v c bit nguy him, ng th 2 trong cc bnh ung th vng u - c  nc ta (xp sau ung th vm hng). Ung th thanh qun l thut ng dng  ch n khi u nm trong long thanh quan (gm mt di thanh nhit, bng thanh tht, thanh tht Morgagni, dy thanh va ha thanh mn), cac khi u khac vt ngoai pham vi cac vi tri trn l ung th ha hong.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cs-base-custom cs-benh-content\">\r\n<h2 id=\"section-1\" class=\"\">Tm hiu chung</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Ung th thanh qun l g?</strong></h3>\r\nUng th thanh qun l cn bnh ph bin v c bit nguy him, ng th 2 trong cc bnh ung th vng u - c  nc ta (xp sau ung th vm hng). Ung th thanh qun l thut ng dng  ch n khi u nm trong long thanh quan (gm mt di thanh nhit, bng thanh tht, thanh tht Morgagni, dy thanh va ha thanh mn), cac khi u khac vt ngoai pham vi cac vi tri trn l ung th ha hong. c bit  Vit Nam ngy cng gp nhiu th ung th thanh qun n thun hn ung th h hng.\r\n\r\nHu ht cc loi ung th thanh qun l ung th t bo gai, mng, cc t bo dt t lt trong thanh qun. Thanh qun gm c 3 phn:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thng thanh mn: Phn trn ca thanh qun pha trn dy thanh, bao gm c np thanh thit.</li>\r\n 	<li>Thanh mn: Phn gia ca thanh qun ni c 2 dy thanh.</li>\r\n 	<li>H thanh mn: Phn di ca thanh qun gia hai dy thanh v kh qun.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"post-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-top slide-benh-top swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-button-prev icon-prev\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container gallery-thumbs slide-benh-thumb swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-prev\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/316/2018/06/316-ung-thu-thanh-quan-4223-5b16.jpg\" alt=\"Ung th thanh qun\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide-item\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://nhathuoclongchau.com/upload/images/benh/316/2018/06/316-ung-thu-thanh-quan-1575-5b16.jpg\" alt=\"Ung th thanh qun\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-2\" class=\"\">Triu chng thng gp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng du hiu v triu chng ca ung th thanh qun</strong></h3>\r\nTriu chng ca bnh lin quan n giai on bnh v v tr khi u:\r\n\r\n<em>Theo giai on bnh:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Giai on u c cc du hiu:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khn ting chm v tng dn theo thi gian;</li>\r\n 	<li>Nut vng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Giai on ton pht bnh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Kh th tng dn;</li>\r\n 	<li>Kh nut, nut c cm gic au, thng gy au lan ln tai;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ho dai dng, khc ra mu;</li>\r\n 	<li>Hi th hi do bi nhim;</li>\r\n 	<li>Hch c xut hin mt bn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Theo v tr khi u:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ung th tng trn thanh qun:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khn ting nh;</li>\r\n 	<li>Nut vng;</li>\r\n 	<li>C th cm thy kh th khi u ln ln vo thanh mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung th thanh tht Morgagni: Cc triu chng xut hin mun nh nut au, do v tr ung th  trong lng thanh tht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung th dy thanh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khn ting v ngy cng nng v khng th khi;</li>\r\n 	<li>Ho, kh th tng cn khi u lan ra n mp trc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Ung th h thanh mn: Thng pht hin  giai on mun. Triu chng ch yu l kh th tng dn, khn ting nh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Khi no cn gp bc s?</strong></h3>\r\nKhi cm nhn c s thay i  c hng bao gm khan ting hoc thay i ging ni, au c m khng dt th bn nn n bnh vin  nhn c t vn. Nu bc s cm thy c nguy c th bn s c xt nghim v chn on lm sng. Chn on v iu tr sm s gim thiu nguy c tng nng ca bnh v gip bn mau chng hi phc sc khe.\r\n\r\nMi ngi mt c a khc nhau, bn cn tham kho  kin chuyn gia  c phng n iu tr thch hp. Vic t iu tr m khng c s hng dn ca bc s chuyn khoa c th dn n nhng tn thng nguy him khc.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-3\" class=\"\">Nguyn nhn gy bnh</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nguyn nhn dn n ung th thanh qun</strong></h3>\r\nHin ti theo cc nh khoa hc vn cha c nguyn nhn chnh xc gy ra bnh. Trong tt c cc loi bnh ung th th u lin quan n ADN b thay i, lm c th khng kim sot c s ti to t bo. Hu qu l lm cho cc m tng sinh t bin dn n bu hay c gi l khi u.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-4\" class=\"\">Nguy c mc phi</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng ai c nguy cb ung th thanh qun?</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ung th thanh qun hay gp  la tui 50 - 70, bnh tng i him  nhng ngi   tui di 40.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nam gii c nguy c b ung th thanh qun cao gp 4 ln so vi ph n.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi ta nghi ng vic mc ung th thanh qun c lin quan n ht thuc l, nhng ngi tip xc vi niken, amiang, crom hay c tin s chy tia x tuyn gip, ng n v ng th.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYu t lm tng nguy c mc bnh, bao gm:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ht thuc l kt hp vi s dng ru, bia.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh nhn c tin s mc cc bnh lin quan n vng u c.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngi phi thng xuyn tip xc vi acid sulfuric hoc niken c nguy c cao b ung th thanh qun.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nhim virus, tro ngc d dy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"section-5\" class=\"\">iu tr hiu qu</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php dng  xt nghim v chn on ung th thanh qun</strong></h3>\r\nBc s s da trn bnh s v tin hnh mt s xt nghim  chn on bnh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thm khm thc th hng v c: Du hiu c hch sng  c v quan st qua gng  nh gi cc bt thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ni soi thanh qun vi gng hoc vi optic soi thanh qun. Ni soi gip bc s c th nh gi hot ng ca thanh qun v bt thng ca cc vng trong thanh qun, qua  c th bm sinh thit ch nghi ng.</li>\r\n 	<li>CT scan (CAT scan): Hnh nh chi tit  nh gi cc vng bn trong c th vi nhiu gc .</li>\r\n 	<li>MRI: Chui cc hnh nh chi tit nh gi cc vng trong c th.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sinh thit: Ly cc m hoc cc t bo  quan st di knh hin vi tm t bo c tnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Chp nhum ng tiu ha trn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Phng php iu tr ung th thanh qun hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nTy theo giai on bnh, v tr v kch thc khi u, bnh ti pht m bc s s ch nh phng php iu tr. Mc ch chnh l gip bnh nhn gi c kh nng ni, n v th nh bnh thng  mc c th. Cc phng php iu tr chnh cho ung th thanh qun bao gm phu thut, x tr, ha tr hoc kt hp cc phng php trn.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>X tr: S dng nhng tia c nng lng cao  tiu dit t bo ung th v ngn chn chng pht trin. X tr n thun trong iu tr ung th dy thanh c hiu qu cao.</li>\r\n 	<li>Phu thut: Ct b mt phn khi u thanh qun khi khi u cn khu tr cha c di cn. y l phu thut bo tn, sau m bnh nhn cn bo tn cc chc nng pht m, th qua ng mi.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ha tr: S dng thuc cc loi thuc lm ngng s pht trin ca t bo ung th, thng c tim vo mch mu.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTy vo th trng v tnh trng bnh m bc s s k n thuc v p dng nhng phng php iu tr ph hp cho bnh nhn.\r\n<h2 id=\"section-6\" class=\"\">Ch  sinh hot ph hp</h2>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng thi quen sinh hot c th gip bn hn ch din tin ca ung th thanh qun</strong></h3>\r\n<em>Ch  sinh hot:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tun th theo cc hng dn ca bc s trong vic iu tr.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vn ng v tp luyn th thao iu .</li>\r\n 	<li>Khi co ru, bnh nhn nn s dng dao co ru nha  trnh lm tn thng da sau phu thut.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thm khm nh k  c theo di tnh trng sc khe, din tin ca bnh v  bc s tm hng iu tr ph hp trong thi gian tip theo nu bnh c du hiu ti pht.</li>\r\n 	<li>Duy tr li sng tch cc, hn ch s cng thng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bnh nhn cn lc quan. Tm l c nh hng rt ln n iu tr, hy ni chuyn vi nhng ngi ng tin cy, chia s vi nhng thnh vin trong gia nh, nui th cng hay n gin l c sch, lm bt c th g khin bn thy thoi mi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Ch  dinh dng:</em>\r\n\r\nBnh nhn mc ung th thanh qun cn c ch  dinh dng lnh mnh, kt hp cng vi liu php iu tr  bnh din bin tt hn:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cn m bo dinh dng y  nng lng v protein  gip bnh nhn khng b st cn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nn n thc n lng, m nh nc st, cho, sp gip d nut.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch n  cng kh nhai nut, thc phm cay nng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Nhng phng php phng bnh hiu qu</strong></h3>\r\nBnh c th phng nga bng cch gim thiu cc yu t nguy c\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khng ht, nghin thuc l.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hn ch ung ru.</li>\r\n 	<li>Duy tr ch  n ung lnh mnh,  cht v khoa hc. n nhiu rau xanh, cht x, hoa qu, ung nhiu nc. Trnh n qu nhiu cc  n nng, cay,  nng, chin,</li>\r\n 	<li>Khm sc khe nh k  kp thi pht hin nhng bt thng trong c th.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Ung th l cn bnh nguy him nhng khng c ngha l bnh khng th iu tr c. iu quan trng nht trong vic chng li ung th chnh l ngi bnh cn c thi  lc quan v kin tr iu tr bnh. Thc t cho thy, nhng ngi c thi  sng tch cc kt hp vi phng php iu tr hp l  ko di c tui th v chng li c cn bnh ung th.</em>\r\n<ul class=\"block-note\">\r\n 	<li>Mi thng tin trn y ch mang tnh cht tham kho. Vic s dng thuc phi tun theo hng dn ca bc s chuyn mn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Ung th thanh qun', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ung-thu-thanh-quan', '', '', '2021-01-31 00:07:28', '2021-01-30 17:07:28', '', 0, 'https://i-pharmacy.vn/?post_type=benh&#038;p=835', 0, 'benh', '', 0),
